        if (SortOption1 == "全部") { return data; }
        if (SortOption1 == "机柜号" && SortType1 == "升序") { result = data.OrderBy(x => x.CabinetNumber); } else if (SortOption1 == "机柜号" && SortType1 == "降序") { result = data.OrderByDescending(x => x.CabinetNumber); } else if (SortOption1 == "机架" && SortType1 == "升序") { result = data.OrderBy(x => x.Cage); } else if (SortOption1 == "机架" && SortType1 == "降序") { result = data.OrderByDescending(x => x.Cage); } else if (SortOption1 == "插槽" && SortType1 == "升序") { result = data.OrderBy(x => x.Slot); } else if (SortOption1 == "插槽" && SortType1 == "降序") { result = data.OrderByDescending(x => x.Slot); } else if (SortOption1 == "通道" && SortType1 == "升序") { result = data.OrderBy(x => x.Channel); } else if (SortOption1 == "通道" && SortType1 == "降序") { result = data.OrderByDescending(x => x.Channel); } else if (SortOption1 == "FF/DP端子通道" && SortType1 == "升序") { result = data.OrderBy(x => x.FFDPTerminalChannel); } else if (SortOption1 == "FF/DP端子通道" && SortType1 == "降序") { result = data.OrderByDescending(x => x.FFDPTerminalChannel); } else { throw new("开发人员注意"); }
        if (SortOption2 == "全部") { return result; }
        if (SortOption2 == "机柜号" && SortType2 == "升序") { result = result.ThenBy(x => x.CabinetNumber); } else if (SortOption2 == "机柜号" && SortType2 == "降序") { result = result.ThenByDescending(x => x.CabinetNumber); } else if (SortOption2 == "机架" && SortType2 == "升序") { result = result.ThenBy(x => x.Cage); } else if (SortOption2 == "机架" && SortType2 == "降序") { result = result.ThenByDescending(x => x.Cage); } else if (SortOption2 == "插槽" && SortType2 == "升序") { result = result.ThenBy(x => x.Slot); } else if (SortOption2 == "插槽" && SortType2 == "降序") { result = result.ThenByDescending(x => x.Slot); } else if (SortOption2 == "通道" && SortType2 == "升序") { result = result.ThenBy(x => x.Channel); } else if (SortOption2 == "通道" && SortType2 == "降序") { result = result.ThenByDescending(x => x.Channel); } else if (SortOption2 == "FF/DP端子通道" && SortType2 == "升序") { result = result.ThenBy(x => x.FFDPTerminalChannel); } else if (SortOption2 == "FF/DP端子通道" && SortType2 == "降序") { result = result.ThenByDescending(x => x.FFDPTerminalChannel); } else { throw new("开发人员注意"); }
        if (SortOption3 == "全部") { return result; }
        if (SortOption3 == "机柜号" && SortType3 == "升序") { result = result.ThenBy(x => x.CabinetNumber); } else if (SortOption3 == "机柜号" && SortType3 == "降序") { result = result.ThenByDescending(x => x.CabinetNumber); } else if (SortOption3 == "机架" && SortType3 == "升序") { result = result.ThenBy(x => x.Cage); } else if (SortOption3 == "机架" && SortType3 == "降序") { result = result.ThenByDescending(x => x.Cage); } else if (SortOption3 == "插槽" && SortType3 == "升序") { result = result.ThenBy(x => x.Slot); } else if (SortOption3 == "插槽" && SortType3 == "降序") { result = result.ThenByDescending(x => x.Slot); } else if (SortOption3 == "通道" && SortType3 == "升序") { result = result.ThenBy(x => x.Channel); } else if (SortOption3 == "通道" && SortType3 == "降序") { result = result.ThenByDescending(x => x.Channel); } else if (SortOption3 == "FF/DP端子通道" && SortType3 == "升序") { result = result.ThenBy(x => x.FFDPTerminalChannel); } else if (SortOption3 == "FF/DP端子通道" && SortType3 == "降序") { result = result.ThenByDescending(x => x.FFDPTerminalChannel); } else { throw new("开发人员注意"); }
        if (SortOption4 == "全部") { return result; }
        if (SortOption4 == "机柜号" && SortType4 == "升序") { result = result.ThenBy(x => x.CabinetNumber); } else if (SortOption4 == "机柜号" && SortType4 == "降序") { result = result.ThenByDescending(x => x.CabinetNumber); } else if (SortOption4 == "机架" && SortType4 == "升序") { result = result.ThenBy(x => x.Cage); } else if (SortOption4 == "机架" && SortType4 == "降序") { result = result.ThenByDescending(x => x.Cage); } else if (SortOption4 == "插槽" && SortType4 == "升序") { result = result.ThenBy(x => x.Slot); } else if (SortOption4 == "插槽" && SortType4 == "降序") { result = result.ThenByDescending(x => x.Slot); } else if (SortOption4 == "通道" && SortType4 == "升序") { result = result.ThenBy(x => x.Channel); } else if (SortOption4 == "通道" && SortType4 == "降序") { result = result.ThenByDescending(x => x.Channel); } else if (SortOption4 == "FF/DP端子通道" && SortType4 == "升序") { result = result.ThenBy(x => x.FFDPTerminalChannel); } else if (SortOption4 == "FF/DP端子通道" && SortType4 == "降序") { result = result.ThenByDescending(x => x.FFDPTerminalChannel); } else { throw new("开发人员注意"); }
        if (SortOption5 == "全部") { return result; }
        if (SortOption5 == "机柜号" && SortType5 == "升序") { result = result.ThenBy(x => x.CabinetNumber); } else if (SortOption5 == "机柜号" && SortType5 == "降序") { result = result.ThenByDescending(x => x.CabinetNumber); } else if (SortOption5 == "机架" && SortType5 == "升序") { result = result.ThenBy(x => x.Cage); } else if (SortOption5 == "机架" && SortType5 == "降序") { result = result.ThenByDescending(x => x.Cage); } else if (SortOption5 == "插槽" && SortType5 == "升序") { result = result.ThenBy(x => x.Slot); } else if (SortOption5 == "插槽" && SortType5 == "降序") { result = result.ThenByDescending(x => x.Slot); } else if (SortOption5 == "通道" && SortType5 == "升序") { result = result.ThenBy(x => x.Channel); } else if (SortOption5 == "通道" && SortType5 == "降序") { result = result.ThenByDescending(x => x.Channel); } else if (SortOption5 == "FF/DP端子通道" && SortType5 == "升序") { result = result.ThenBy(x => x.FFDPTerminalChannel); } else if (SortOption5 == "FF/DP端子通道" && SortType5 == "降序") { result = result.ThenByDescending(x => x.FFDPTerminalChannel); } else { throw new("开发人员注意"); }
        return result;
    }
    public ObservableCollection<string> SortTypes { get; } = ["升序", "降序"];
    [ObservableProperty] private string sortType1 = "升序";
    [ObservableProperty] private string sortType2 = "升序";
    [ObservableProperty] private string sortType3 = "升序";
    [ObservableProperty] private string sortType4 = "升序";
    [ObservableProperty] private string sortType5 = "升序";
    [ObservableProperty]
    private ObservableCollection<string> sortOptions1 = ["全部", "机柜号", "机架", "插槽", "通道", "FF/DP端子通道"];
    [ObservableProperty]
    private string sortOption1 = "全部";
    [ObservableProperty]
    private ObservableCollection<string> sortOptions2 = ["全部"];
    [ObservableProperty]
    private string sortOption2 = "全部";
    [ObservableProperty]
    private ObservableCollection<string> sortOptions3 = ["全部"];
    [ObservableProperty]
    private string sortOption3 = "全部";
    [ObservableProperty]
    private ObservableCollection<string> sortOptions4 = ["全部"];
    [ObservableProperty]
    private string sortOption4 = "全部";
    [ObservableProperty]
    private ObservableCollection<string> sortOptions5 = ["全部"];
    [ObservableProperty]
    private string sortOption5 = "全部";
    private ImmutableList<string> allSortOptions = ["机柜号", "机架", "插槽", "通道", "FF/DP端子通道"];
    partial void OnSortOption1Changed(string value) {
        var option2Old = SortOption2;
        SortOption2 = "全部";
        if (SortOption1 == "全部") {
            SortOptions2 = ["全部"];
        } else {
            SortOptions2 = ["全部", .. allSortOptions.Except([SortOption1])];
        }
        if (option2Old == "全部") { OnSortOption2Changed("全部"); }
    }
    partial void OnSortOption2Changed(string value) {
        var option3Old = SortOption3;
        SortOption3 = "全部";
        if (SortOption2 == "全部") {
            SortOptions3 = ["全部"];
        } else {
            SortOptions3 = ["全部", .. allSortOptions.Except([SortOption1, SortOption2])];
        }
        if (option3Old == "全部") { OnSortOption3Changed("全部"); }
    }
    partial void OnSortOption3Changed(string value) {
        var option4Old = SortOption4;
        SortOption4 = "全部";
        if (SortOption3 == "全部") {
            SortOptions4 = ["全部"];
        } else {
            SortOptions4 = ["全部", .. allSortOptions.Except([SortOption1, SortOption2, SortOption3])];
        }
        if (option4Old == "全部") { OnSortOption4Changed("全部"); }
    }
    partial void OnSortOption4Changed(string value) {
        var option5Old = SortOption5;
        SortOption5 = "全部";
        if (SortOption4 == "全部") {
            SortOptions5 = ["全部"];
        } else {
            SortOptions5 = ["全部", .. allSortOptions.Except([SortOption1, SortOption2, SortOption3, SortOption4])];
        }
        if (option5Old == "全部") { OnSortOption5Changed("全部"); }
    }
    partial void OnSortOption5Changed(string value) {
        FilterAndSort();
    }
}
#pragma warning disable CA1822 
using System.Data;
using System.IO;
using IODataPlatform.Models.DBModels;
using IODataPlatform.Models.ExcelModels;
using IODataPlatform.Utilities;
using Microsoft.Xaml.Behaviors.Layout;
namespace IODataPlatform.Views.Pages;
partial class DepXT2ViewModel {
    [RelayCommand]
    private async Task Export(string param) {
        if (AllData == null) { throw new("没有可导出的数据"); }
        if (picker.SaveFile("Excel 文件(*.xlsx)|*.xlsx", param) is not string file) { return; }
        if (File.Exists(file)) { File.Delete(file); }
        model.Status.Busy($"正在{param}数据……");
        if (param == "导出IO分站清单") {
            await ExportIOSubStation(AllData.ToList(), file);
        }
        else if (param == "导出主系统板卡清单")
        {
            await ExportMainSystemBoardList(AllData.ToList(), file);
        }
        else if (param == "导出板卡统计信息")
        {
            await ExportBoardStatisticsInfo(AllData.ToList(), file);
        }
        else if (param == "导出龙鳍数据库")
        {
            await ExportDatabase(AllData.ToList(), file);
        }
        else if (param == "导出端接清单")
        {
            await ExportDuanjie(AllData.ToList(), file);
        }
        model.Status.Success($"已成功{param}数据：{file}");
    }
    private async Task ExportIOSubStation(List<Xt2Cabinet> cabinets, string filePath) {      
        var data = CabinetCalc.CabinetStructureToPoint(cabinets);       
        await Recalc();       
        model.Status.Reset();
        using var dataTable = await data.ToTableByDisplayAttributeAsync();
        await excel.FastExportSheetAsync(dataTable, filePath, "IO分站清单");
    }
    private async Task ExportMainSystemBoardList(List<Xt2Cabinet> cabinets, string filePath)
    {       
        var groupedData = Getxtes_mainsystemboard_list(cabinets);
        using var dataTable = await groupedData.ToTableByPropertyNameAsync();
        await excel.FastExportSheetAsync(dataTable, filePath, "主系统板卡");
    }
    public List<xtes_mainsystemboard_list> Getxtes_mainsystemboard_list(List<Xt2Cabinet> cabinets)
    {
        var groupedData = new List<xtes_mainsystemboard_list>();
        int addressStartIndex = 2;
        foreach (var cabinet in cabinets)
        {
            AddControllerAndPowerBoards(groupedData, cabinet, ref addressStartIndex);
            foreach (var cage in cabinet.Cages)
            {
                foreach (var slot in cage.Slots)
                {
                    if (slot.Board != null) 
                    {
                        var tagFirst = slot.Board.Channels.Select(c => c.Point).FirstOrDefault(c => c != null);
                        groupedData.Add(CreateBoardListItem(cabinet.Name, cage.Index, slot.Index, slot.Board, tagFirst));
                    }
                }
            }
            CompleteUnusedSlots(groupedData, cabinet);
        }
        return groupedData.OrderBy(g => g.机柜编号).ThenBy(g => g.机架号).ThenBy(g => g.插槽).ToList();
    }
    private void AddControllerAndPowerBoards(List<xtes_mainsystemboard_list> list, Xt2Cabinet cabinet, ref int addressIndex)
    {
        list.AddRange(new[]
        {
        new xtes_mainsystemboard_list
        {
            机柜编号 = cabinet.Name,
            机架号 = 1,
            插槽 = 1,
            地址 = addressIndex++.ToString(),
            板卡类型 = "NP204",
            板卡编号 = $"{cabinet.Name}101UC",
            描述 = "控制器",
        },
        new xtes_mainsystemboard_list
        {
            机柜编号 = cabinet.Name,
            机架号 = 1,
            插槽 = 2,
            地址 = (addressIndex + 127).ToString(),
            板卡类型 = "NP204",
            板卡编号 = $"{cabinet.Name}102UC",
            描述 = "控制器",
        }
    });
        for (int i = 0; i < 3; i++)
        {
            list.Add(new xtes_mainsystemboard_list
            {
                机柜编号 = cabinet.Name,
                机架号 = i + 1,
                插槽 = 11,
                地址 = "0B",
                板卡类型 = "PM211",
                描述 = "DC24V电源板卡",
            });
            list.Add(new xtes_mainsystemboard_list
            {
                机柜编号 = cabinet.Name,
                机架号 = i + 1,
                插槽 = 12,
                地址 = "0C",
                板卡类型 = "PM211",
                描述 = "DC24V电源板卡",
            });
        }
    }
    private xtes_mainsystemboard_list CreateBoardListItem(string cabinetName, int cageIndex, int slotIndex, Xt2Board board,Xt2Point? tag)
    {
        return new xtes_mainsystemboard_list
        {
            机柜编号 = cabinetName,
            机架号 = cageIndex,
            插槽 = slotIndex,
            地址 = GetAddress(cageIndex, slotIndex),
            板卡类型 = GetCardType(cageIndex, slotIndex, board.Type),
            板卡编号 = GetCardNumber(cabinetName, cageIndex, slotIndex, board.Type),
            端子板类型 = GetTerminalBoardType(board.Type, slotIndex, tag),
            端子板编号 = GetTerminalBoardNumber(cageIndex, slotIndex, tag),
            描述 = GetDescription(board.Type),
        };
    }
    private void CompleteUnusedSlots(List<xtes_mainsystemboard_list> list, Xt2Cabinet cabinet)
    {
        var slotsUsed = list.Where(g => g.机柜编号 == cabinet.Name).Select(g => (g.机架号, g.插槽)).ToList();
        for (int rack = 1; rack <= 12; rack++)
        {
            for (int slot = 1; slot <= 12; slot++)
            {
                if (!slotsUsed.Contains((rack, slot)))
                {
                    list.Add(new xtes_mainsystemboard_list
                    {
                        机柜编号 = cabinet.Name,
                        机架号 = rack,
                        插槽 = slot,
                        地址 = GetAddress(rack, slot),
                        板卡类型 = "备用",
                        描述 = "空插槽",
                    });
                }
            }
        }
    }
    private async Task ExportBoardStatisticsInfo(List<Xt2Cabinet> cabinets, string filePath)
    {
        var data = CabinetCalc.CabinetStructureToPoint(cabinets);
        var list = Getxtes_mainsystemboard_list(cabinets);
        var aggregatedStatistics = list.GroupBy(board => new { board.板卡类型, board.端子板类型 })
                                          .Select((group, index) => new xtes_board_statistics
                                          {
                                              序号 = index + 1,
                                              板卡 = group.Key.板卡类型,
                                              板卡数量 = group.Count(),
                                              端子板 = group.Key.端子板类型,
                                              端子板数量 = group.Count()
                                          }).ToList();
        using var dataTable = await aggregatedStatistics.ToTableByPropertyNameAsync();
        await excel.FastExportSheetAsync(dataTable, filePath, "板卡统计");
    }
    private string GetAddress(int cage, int slot) {
        return (cage, slot) switch {
            (1, < 3) => "", 
            (_, < 11) => ((cage - 1) * 10 + slot).ToString(),
            _ => "--",
        };
    }
    private string GetCardType(int cage, int slot, string cardType) {
        return (cage, slot) switch {
            (1, 1 or 2) => "NP204",  
            (_, 11 or 12) => "PM211",  
            _ => cardType, 
        };
    }
    private string GetCardNumber(string cabinetNumber, int cage, int slot, string cardType) {
        string cardNumber = cabinetNumber + GetCardInCabinetNumber(cage, slot, cardType);
        return (cage, slot) switch {
            (1, 1 or 2) => $"{cabinetNumber}{cage}{slot:00}UC",
            (_, 11 or 12) => "--",
            (_, 13 or 14) => $"{cabinetNumber}{cage}{slot:00}PM",
            _ => cardNumber,
        };
    }
    private string GetTerminalBoardType(string cardType, int slot, Xt2Point? tag) =>
    cardType switch
    {
        "MD211" => "TB244",
        "NP204" or "MD212" or "MD216" => "--",
        _ when slot is 11 or 12 or 13 or 14 => "--",
        _ => tag?.TerminalBoardModel ?? "--"
    };
    private string GetTerminalBoardNumber(int cage, int slot, Xt2Point? tag) =>
      (cage, slot) switch
      {
          (1, 1 or 2) => "--",                  
          (_, 11 or 12 or 13 or 14) => "--",    
          _ => tag?.TerminalBoardNumber ?? "--" 
      };
    private string GetDescription(string cardType) {
        return cardType switch {
            "AI212" => "8通道模拟量输入模块",
            "FF211" => "FF H1网关通信模块",
            "DP211" => "PROFIBUS-DP",
            "AI216" => "8通道带HART功能模拟量输入模块",
            "AI221" => "8通道热电偶模块",
            "AI231" => "8通道热电阻模块",
            "AO211" => "8通道模拟量输出模块",
            "AO212" => "8通道模拟量输出模块",
            "DI211" => "16通道开关量输入模块",
            "DO211" => "16通道开关量输出模块",
            "NP204" => "控制器",
            "PM211" => "DC24V电源板卡",
            "备用" => "",
            "--" => "总线扩展连接模块",
            "MD212" => "MODBUS TCP通讯板卡",
            "MD211" => "Modbus RTU通讯板卡",
            "PI211" => "脉冲量输入模块",
            _ => "Unknown"
        };
    }
    private async Task ExportDuanjie(List<Xt2Cabinet> cabinets, string filePath)
    {
        var data = CabinetCalc.CabinetStructureToPoint(cabinets);
        var terminations = data.Select(x => x.toduanjieData()).ToList();
        using var dataTable = await terminations.ToTableByDisplayAttributeAsync();
        await excel.FastExportSheetAsync(dataTable, filePath, "系统二室端接清单");
    }
    private async Task ExportDatabase(IList<Xt2Cabinet> cabinets, string filePath) {
        var data = CabinetCalc.CabinetStructureToPoint(cabinets);
        var (am_ffTask, aviTask, avoTask, dviTask, dvoTask, gbpTask, gcpTask) = (
            new FormularHelper().ConvertToAmffList(data).ToTableByDisplayAttributeAsync(),
            new FormularHelper().ConvertToAviList(data).ToTableByDisplayAttributeAsync(),
            new FormularHelper().ConvertToAvoList(data).ToTableByDisplayAttributeAsync(),
            new FormularHelper().ConvertToDviList(data).ToTableByDisplayAttributeAsync(),
            new FormularHelper().ConvertToDvoList(data).ToTableByDisplayAttributeAsync(),
            new FormularHelper().ConvertToGbpList(data).ToTableByDisplayAttributeAsync(),
            new FormularHelper().ConvertToGcpList(data).ToTableByDisplayAttributeAsync()
        );
        var (am_ff, avi, avo, dvi, dvo, gbp, gcp) = (await am_ffTask, await aviTask, await avoTask, await dviTask, await dvoTask, await gbpTask, await gcpTask);
        await Task.Run(() => {
            var wb = excel.GetWorkbook();
            void writeData(DataTable dataTable, string name) {
                var ws = wb.Worksheets.Add(name);
                var cells = ws.Cells;
                cells.ImportData(dataTable, 0, 0, new() { IsFieldNameShown = true });
                dataTable.Dispose();
            }
            writeData(am_ff, nameof(am_ff).ToUpper());
            writeData(avi, nameof(avi).ToUpper());
            writeData(avo, nameof(avo).ToUpper());
            writeData(dvi, nameof(dvi).ToUpper());
            writeData(dvo, nameof(dvo).ToUpper());
            writeData(gbp, nameof(gbp).ToUpper());
            writeData(gcp, nameof(gcp).ToUpper());
            wb.Save(filePath);
        });
    }
}
using IODataPlatform.Models.DBModels;
using IODataPlatform.Models.ExcelModels;
using IODataPlatform.Views.SubPages.XT2;
using LYSoft.Libs.Editor;
using LYSoft.Libs.Wpf.WpfUI;
using System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations;
using System.Diagnostics;
using System.Reflection;
namespace IODataPlatform.Views.Pages;
partial class DepXT2ViewModel {
    [RelayCommand]
    private async Task Add() {
        if (SubProject is null) { return; }
        if (AllPoints is null) { return; }
        var data = new Xt2Point();
        if (!EditData(data, "添加")) { return; }
        AllPoints = [.. AllPoints.Append(data)];
        AllData = CabinetCalc.BuildCabinetStructure([.. AllPoints], await context.Db.Queryable<config_card_type_judge>().ToListAsync());
        await SaveAndUploadFileAsync();
        RefreshFilterOptions();
        FilterAndSort();
    }
    [RelayCommand]
    private async Task Clear() {
        if (!await message.ConfirmAsync("确认清空")) { return; }
        AllData = [];
        await SaveAndUploadFileAsync();
    }
    [RelayCommand]
    private async Task Edit(Xt2Point data) {
        var objToEdit = new Xt2Point().CopyPropertiesFrom(data);
        if (!EditData(objToEdit, "编辑")) { return; }
        data.CopyPropertiesFrom(objToEdit);
        DisplayPoints = [.. DisplayPoints];
        await SaveAndUploadFileAsync();
    }
    [RelayCommand]
    private async Task Delete(Xt2Point data) {
        _ = AllData ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        if (!await message.ConfirmAsync("是否删除")) { return; }
        var allPoints = CabinetCalc.CabinetStructureToPoint(AllData);
        allPoints.Remove(data);
        AllData = CabinetCalc.BuildCabinetStructure(allPoints, await context.Db.Queryable<config_card_type_judge>().ToListAsync());
        await SaveAndUploadFileAsync();
    }
    [RelayCommand]
    private void Import() {
        navigation.NavigateWithHierarchy(typeof(ImportPage));
    }
    [RelayCommand]
    private async Task Refresh() {
        model.Status.Busy("正在刷新……");
        await ReloadAllData();
        model.Status.Reset();
    }
    private bool EditData(Xt2Point data, string title) {
        var builder = data.CreateEditorBuilder();
        builder.WithTitle(title);
        foreach (var property in typeof(Xt2Point).GetProperties()) {
            var porpDisplay = property.GetCustomAttribute<DisplayAttribute>()!;
            if (!porpDisplay.GetAutoGenerateField().GetValueOrDefault(true)) { continue; }
            var propDisplayName = porpDisplay.Name!;
            if (Filters.SingleOrDefault(x => x.Title == propDisplayName) is { Option: not "全部" } filter) {
                property.SetValue(data, filter.Option);
            }
            if (property.PropertyType == typeof(string)) {
                builder.AddProperty<string>(property.Name).WithHeader(propDisplayName).WithPlaceHoplder($"请输入{propDisplayName}");
            } else if (property.PropertyType == typeof(float)) {
                builder.AddProperty<float>(property.Name).WithHeader(propDisplayName).EditAsDouble().ConvertFromProperty(x => (double)x).ConvertToProperty(x => (float)x);
            } else if (property.PropertyType == typeof(int)) {
                builder.AddProperty<int>(property.Name).WithHeader(propDisplayName).EditAsInt();
            } else if (property.PropertyType == typeof(int?)) {
                builder.AddProperty<int?>(property.Name).WithHeader(propDisplayName).EditAsInt().ConvertFromProperty(x => x ?? default);
            } else if (property.PropertyType == typeof(DateTime?)) {
                builder.AddProperty<DateTime?>(property.Name).WithHeader(propDisplayName).EditAsDateTime().ConvertFromProperty(x => x ?? new()).ConvertToProperty(x => x == default ? null : x);
            } else {
                Debugger.Break();
            }
        }
        return builder.Build().EditWithWpfUI();
    }
}
using System.IO;
using System.Reactive.Linq;
using System.Text.Json;
using IODataPlatform.Models;
using IODataPlatform.Models.DBModels;
using IODataPlatform.Models.ExcelModels;
using IODataPlatform.Services;
using IODataPlatform.Utilities;
using IODataPlatform.Views.SubPages.Common;
using IODataPlatform.Views.SubPages.XT2;
using LYSoft.Libs.ServiceInterfaces;
using SqlSugar;
namespace IODataPlatform.Views.Pages;
public partial class DepXT2ViewModel(SqlSugarContext context, ConfigTableViewModel configvm, INavigationService navigation,
    GlobalModel model, IMessageService message, IContentDialogService dialog, StorageService storage,
    ExcelService excel, IPickerService picker, PublishViewModel publishvm) : ObservableObject, INavigationAware {
    private bool isInit = false;
    public void OnNavigatedFrom() {
    }
    public async void OnNavigatedTo() {
        if (!model.User.Check(Department.系统二室, null)) {
            model.Status.Error("您无权访问此页面/使用此功能"); 
            await message.ErrorAsync("您无权访问此页面/使用此功能");
            await Task.Delay(200);
            navigation.Navigate(typeof(LoginPage));
        }
        if (!isInit) {
            await RefreshProjects();
            isInit = true;
        } else {
            FilterAndSort();
        }
    }
    [ObservableProperty]
    private ObservableCollection<Xt2Cabinet>? allData;       
    public async Task SaveAndUploadFileAsync(int? versionId = null) {
        _ = Project?.Id ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        var subProjectId = SubProject?.Id ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        var allData = AllData ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        var relativePath = storage.GetRealtimeIoFileRelativePath(subProjectId);
        var absolutePath = storage.GetWebFileLocalAbsolutePath(relativePath);
        await File.WriteAllTextAsync(absolutePath, JsonSerializer.Serialize(allData));
        await storage.UploadRealtimeIoFileAsync(subProjectId);
        if (versionId == null) { return; }
        await storage.WebCopyFilesAsync([(relativePath, storage.GetPublishIoFileRelativePath(subProjectId, versionId.Value))]);
    }
    public async Task ReloadAllData() {
        AllData = null;
        _ = Project?.Id ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        var subProjectId = SubProject?.Id ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        try {
            var file = await storage.DownloadRealtimeIoFileAsync(subProjectId);
            var list = JsonSerializer.Deserialize<List<Xt2Cabinet>>(await File.ReadAllTextAsync(file));
            AllData = [.. list];
        } catch {
            AllData = [];
        }
    }
    [ObservableProperty]
    private bool isCabinetSummaryFlyoutOpen = false;
    [ObservableProperty]
    private bool isTotalSummaryFlyoutOpen = false;
    [ObservableProperty]
    private Xt2TotalSummaryInfo? totalSummaryInfo;
    [ObservableProperty]
    private int redundancyRate = 20;
    [RelayCommand]
    private void GetTotalSummaryInfo() {
        TotalSummaryInfo = CabinetCalc.GetTotalSummaryInfo(AllData ?? throw new());
        IsTotalSummaryFlyoutOpen = true;
    }
    [RelayCommand]
    private void ExtractPdfData() {
        navigation.NavigateWithHierarchy(typeof(ExtractPdfPage));
    }
    [RelayCommand]
    private void ImportExcelData() {
        navigation.NavigateWithHierarchy(typeof(UploadExcelDataPage));
    }
    [RelayCommand]
    private async Task AddTag(Xt2PointType type)
    {
        _ = AllData ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        if (type == Xt2PointType.Alarm)
        {
            var configs = await context.Db.Queryable<config_card_type_judge>().ToListAsync();
            var configDI211 = configs.FirstOrDefault(c => c.IoCardType == "DI211");
            var configDO211 = configs.FirstOrDefault(c => c.IoCardType == "DO211");
            if (configDI211 == null) throw new Exception("未找到卡件DI211的数量");
            if (configDO211 == null) throw new Exception("未找到卡件DO211的数量");
            model.Status.Busy($"正在添加报警点……");
            foreach (var cabinet in AllData)
            {
                var hasAlarmPoint = cabinet.Cages
                 .SelectMany(cage => cage.Slots)         
                 .SelectMany(slot => slot.Board?.Channels ?? Enumerable.Empty<Xt2Channel>())  
                 .Any(channel => channel.Point?.PointType == Xt2PointType.Alarm);
                if (hasAlarmPoint) continue;
                AddAlarmPoints(cabinet, configDI211);
                AddControlAlarmPoint(cabinet, configDO211);
            }
            model.Status.Busy($"添加报警点完毕……");
        }
        else if (type==Xt2PointType.BackUp)
        {
            model.Status.Busy($"正在添加备用点……");
            foreach (var cabinet in AllData)
            {
                foreach (var cage in cabinet.Cages)
                {
                    foreach (var slot in cage.Slots)
                    {
                        var cardType = slot.Board?.Type;
                        if (cardType == null || cardType.Contains("DP") || cardType.Contains("FF")) continue;
                        for (int i = 0; i < slot.Board!.Channels.Count; i++)
                        {
                            if (slot.Board.Channels[i].Point == null)
                            {
                                var lastTag = slot.Board.Channels.FirstOrDefault(c => c.Point != null)?.Point;
                                if (lastTag == null) continue;
                                slot.Board.Channels[i].Point = new Xt2Point()
                                {
                                    CabinetNumber = cabinet.Name,
                                    SignalPositionNumber = $"{cabinet.Name}{cage.Index}{slot.Index.ToString("00")}{cardType.Substring(0, 2)}CH{i.ToString("00")}",
                                    SystemCode = "BEIYONG",
                                    Cage = cage.Index,
                                    Slot = slot.Index,
                                    CardType = cardType,
                                    Description = "备用",
                                    Channel = i,
                                    IoType = lastTag.IoType,
                                    PowerType = lastTag.PowerType,
                                    ElectricalCharacteristics = lastTag.ElectricalCharacteristics,
                                    SignalEffectiveMode = lastTag.SignalEffectiveMode,
                                    PointType = Xt2PointType.BackUp,
                                    Version = "A",
                                    ModificationDate = DateTime.Now
                                };
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
            model.Status.Busy($"添加备用点完毕……");
        }
        void AddAlarmPoints(Xt2Cabinet cabinet, config_card_type_judge config)
        {
            var alarmDescriptions = new[] { "电源A故障报警", "电源B故障报警", "机柜门开", "温度高报警", "风扇故障", "网络故障" };
            var extensionCodes = new[] { "PWFA", "PWFB", "DROP", "TEPH", "FAN", "SWF" };
            for (int i = 0; i < 6; i++)
            {
                var point = new Xt2Point
                {
                    CabinetNumber = cabinet.Name,
                    PointType = Xt2PointType.Alarm,
                    SignalPositionNumber = cabinet.Name,
                    Cage = 0,
                    Slot = 0,
                    Channel = 0,
                    IoType = "DI",
                    PowerType = "DI1",
                    ElectricalCharacteristics = "无源常开",
                    SignalEffectiveMode = "NO",
                    SystemCode = "JIGUIBAOJING",
                    ExtensionCode = extensionCodes[i],
                    Description = $"控制柜{cabinet.Name}机柜{alarmDescriptions[i]}"
                };
                cabinet.UnsetPoints.Add(point);
            }
        }
        void AddControlAlarmPoint(Xt2Cabinet cabinet, config_card_type_judge config)
        {
            var point = new Xt2Point
            {
                CabinetNumber = cabinet.Name,
                PointType = Xt2PointType.Alarm,
                Cage = 0,
                Slot = 0,
                Channel = 0,
                SignalPositionNumber = cabinet.Name,
                SystemCode = "JIGUIBAOJING",
                ExtensionCode = "ALM",
                Description = $"控制柜{cabinet.Name}机柜报警灯",
                IoType = "DO",
                PowerType = "DO2",
                ElectricalCharacteristics = "有源常闭",
                SignalEffectiveMode = "NO"
            };
            cabinet.UnsetPoints.Add(point);
        }
        AllData = [.. AllData];
        await Recalc();
        await SaveAndUploadFileAsync();
        model.Status.Reset();
    }
    [RelayCommand]
    private async Task DeleteTag(Xt2PointType type) {
        _ = AllData ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        _ = AllPoints ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        model.Status.Busy($"正在删除点……");
        AllPoints.RemoveWhere(x => x.PointType == type);
        AllData = CabinetCalc.BuildCabinetStructure([.. AllPoints], await context.Db.Queryable<config_card_type_judge>().ToListAsync());
        await SaveAndUploadFileAsync();
        model.Status.Reset();
    }
    [RelayCommand]
    private void EditConfigurationTable(string param) {
        configvm.Title = param;
        configvm.DataType = param switch {
            "IO卡型号配置表" => typeof(config_card_type_judge),
            "TB型号配置表" => typeof(config_terminalboard_type_judge),
            "接线点配置表" => typeof(config_connection_points),
            "供电方式配置表" => typeof(config_power_supply_method),
            "OF显示格式值配置表" => typeof(config_output_format_values),
            _ => throw new NotImplementedException(),
        };
        navigation.NavigateWithHierarchy(typeof(ConfigTablePage));
    }
    [RelayCommand]
    private async Task AllocateIO() {
        _ = AllData ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        model.Status.Busy($"正在分配……");
        var formularHelper = new FormularHelper();
        List<config_card_type_judge> config_Card_Type_Judges = await context.Db.Queryable<config_card_type_judge>().ToListAsync();
        AllData = [.. formularHelper.AutoAllocateIO([.. AllData], config_Card_Type_Judges, RedundancyRate / 100.0)];
        await SaveAndUploadFileAsync();
        model.Status.Success($"分配完毕！");
    }
    [RelayCommand]
    private void PreviewAllocateIO() {
        navigation.NavigateWithHierarchy(typeof(CabinetAllocatedPage));
    }
}
using Aspose.Pdf;
using Aspose.Pdf.Operators;
using IODataPlatform.Models.DBModels;
using IODataPlatform.Models.ExcelModels;
using IODataPlatform.Utilities;
using Microsoft.CodeAnalysis.CSharp.Scripting;
using System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations;
using System.Linq.Expressions;
using System.Reflection;
using System.Threading.Channels;
using Expression = System.Linq.Expressions.Expression;
namespace IODataPlatform.Views.Pages;
partial class DepXT2ViewModel
{
    [ObservableProperty]
    private bool useFormula = false;
    [RelayCommand]
    public async Task Recalc()
    {
        model.Status.Busy($"正在重新计算……");
        List<Formula> formulars = UseFormula ? [] : context.Db.Queryable<Formula>().ToList();
        List<FormulaIndex> formularIndexes = UseFormula ? [] : context.Db.Queryable<FormulaIndex>().ToList();
        List<FormulaIndexCondition> conditions = UseFormula ? [] : context.Db.Queryable<FormulaIndexCondition>().ToList();
        var fm = new FormulaBuilder();
        DisplayInfo displayInfo = DisplayAttributeHelper.GetDisplayInfo<Xt2Point>();
        var p = new Xt2Point();
        string cardType = displayInfo.FieldDisplayNames[nameof(p.CardType)];
        string powerSupplyMethod = displayInfo.FieldDisplayNames[nameof(p.PowerSupplyMethod)];
        string terminalBoardModel = displayInfo.FieldDisplayNames[nameof(p.TerminalBoardModel)];
        string signalPlus = displayInfo.FieldDisplayNames[nameof(p.SignalPlus)];
        string signalMinus = displayInfo.FieldDisplayNames[nameof(p.SignalMinus)];
        string rTDCompensationC = displayInfo.FieldDisplayNames[nameof(p.RTDCompensationC)];
        string rTDCompensationE = displayInfo.FieldDisplayNames[nameof(p.RTDCompensationE)];       
        string signalEffectiveMode = displayInfo.FieldDisplayNames[nameof(p.SignalEffectiveMode)];
        Parallel.ForEach(AllData, cabinet =>
        {
            foreach (var cage in cabinet.Cages)
            {
                foreach (var slot in cage.Slots)
                {
                    if (slot.Board != null)
                    {
                        foreach (var channel in slot.Board.Channels)
                        {
                            var point = channel.Point;
                            if (point != null)
                            {
                                point.SignalEffectiveMode = fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpressionNew(point, displayInfo.ClassName, signalEffectiveMode, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                                point.OFDisplayFormat = GetOfDisplayFormat(point.RangeUpperLimit, point.RangeLowerLimit);
                                point.TagName = GetTagName(point.SignalPositionNumber, point.ExtensionCode);
                                point.CardType = UseFormula ? GetIoCardTypeFormula(point) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpression(point, displayInfo.ClassName, cardType, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                                point.PowerSupplyMethod = UseFormula ? GetPowerSupplyMethodFormula(point) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpression(point, displayInfo.ClassName, powerSupplyMethod, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                                point.TerminalBoardModel = UseFormula ? GetTerminalBoxTypeFormula(point.CardType,point.PowerSupplyMethod,point.ElectricalCharacteristics) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpression(point, displayInfo.ClassName, terminalBoardModel, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                                point.CardNumberInCabinet = GetCardInCabinetNumber(cage.Index, slot.Index, point.CardType);
                                point.CardNumber = cabinet.Name + point.CardNumberInCabinet;
                                point.TerminalBoardNumber = GetTerminalBoardNumber(point.TerminalBoardModel, point.CardType, cage.Index, slot.Index, point.NetType);
                                point.CardAddress = GetCardAddress(cage.Index, slot.Index);
                                point.SignalPlus = UseFormula ? GetSingalPlusFormula(point) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpressionNew(point, displayInfo.ClassName, signalPlus, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                                point.SignalMinus = UseFormula ? GetSingalMinusFormula(point) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpressionNew(point, displayInfo.ClassName, signalMinus, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                                point.RTDCompensationC = UseFormula ? GetRTDCompensationEndC(point.SensorType, point.Channel) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpressionNew(point, displayInfo.ClassName, rTDCompensationC, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                                point.RTDCompensationE = UseFormula ? GetRTDCompensationEndD(point.SensorType, point.Channel) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpressionNew(point, displayInfo.ClassName, rTDCompensationE, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
            foreach (var board in cabinet.UnsetBoards)
            {
                foreach (var channel in board.Channels)
                {
                    var point = channel.Point;
                    if (point != null)
                    {
                        point.Cage = 0;
                        point.Slot = 0;
                        point.Channel = channel.Index;
                        point.SignalEffectiveMode = fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpressionNew(point, displayInfo.ClassName, signalEffectiveMode, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                        point.OFDisplayFormat = GetOfDisplayFormat(point.RangeUpperLimit, point.RangeLowerLimit);
                        point.TagName = GetTagName(point.SignalPositionNumber, point.ExtensionCode);
                        point.CardType = UseFormula ? GetIoCardTypeFormula(point) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpression(point, displayInfo.ClassName, cardType, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                        point.PowerSupplyMethod = UseFormula ? GetPowerSupplyMethodFormula(point) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpression(point, displayInfo.ClassName, powerSupplyMethod, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                        point.TerminalBoardModel = UseFormula ? GetTerminalBoxTypeFormula(point.CardType, point.PowerSupplyMethod, point.ElectricalCharacteristics) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpression(point, displayInfo.ClassName, terminalBoardModel, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                        point.CardNumberInCabinet = GetCardInCabinetNumber(0, 0, point.CardType);
                        point.CardNumber = cabinet.Name + point.CardNumberInCabinet;
                        point.TerminalBoardNumber = GetTerminalBoardNumber(point.TerminalBoardModel, point.CardType, 0, 0, point.NetType);
                        point.CardAddress = GetCardAddress(0, 0);
                        point.SignalPlus = UseFormula ? GetSingalPlusFormula(point) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpressionNew(point, displayInfo.ClassName, signalPlus, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                        point.SignalMinus = UseFormula ? GetSingalMinusFormula(point) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpressionNew(point, displayInfo.ClassName, signalMinus, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                        point.RTDCompensationC = UseFormula ? GetRTDCompensationEndC(point.SensorType, point.Channel) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpressionNew(point, displayInfo.ClassName, rTDCompensationC, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                        point.RTDCompensationE = UseFormula ? GetRTDCompensationEndD(point.SensorType, point.Channel) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpressionNew(point, displayInfo.ClassName, rTDCompensationE, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                    }
                }
            }
            foreach (var point in cabinet.UnsetPoints)
            {
                point.Cage = 0;
                point.Slot = 0;
                point.Channel = 0;
                point.SignalEffectiveMode = fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpressionNew(point, displayInfo.ClassName, signalEffectiveMode, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                point.OFDisplayFormat = GetOfDisplayFormat(point.RangeUpperLimit, point.RangeLowerLimit);
                point.TagName = GetTagName(point.SignalPositionNumber, point.ExtensionCode);
                point.CardType = UseFormula ? GetIoCardTypeFormula(point) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpression(point, displayInfo.ClassName, cardType, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                point.PowerSupplyMethod = UseFormula ? GetPowerSupplyMethodFormula(point) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpression(point, displayInfo.ClassName, powerSupplyMethod, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                point.TerminalBoardModel = UseFormula ? GetTerminalBoxTypeFormula(point.CardType, point.PowerSupplyMethod, point.ElectricalCharacteristics) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpression(point, displayInfo.ClassName, terminalBoardModel, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                point.CardNumberInCabinet = GetCardInCabinetNumber(0, 0, point.CardType);
                point.CardNumber = cabinet.Name + point.CardNumberInCabinet;
                point.TerminalBoardNumber = GetTerminalBoardNumber(point.TerminalBoardModel, point.CardType, 0, 0, point.NetType);
                point.CardAddress = GetCardAddress(0, 0);
                point.SignalPlus = UseFormula ? GetSingalPlusFormula(point) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpressionNew(point, displayInfo.ClassName, signalPlus, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                point.SignalMinus = UseFormula ? GetSingalMinusFormula(point) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpressionNew(point, displayInfo.ClassName, signalMinus, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                point.RTDCompensationC = UseFormula ? GetRTDCompensationEndC(point.SensorType, point.Channel) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpressionNew(point, displayInfo.ClassName, rTDCompensationC, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                point.RTDCompensationE = UseFormula ? GetRTDCompensationEndD(point.SensorType, point.Channel) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpressionNew(point, displayInfo.ClassName, rTDCompensationE, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
            }
        });
        await SaveAndUploadFileAsync();
        AllData = [.. AllData];
        model.Status.Success("重新计算完毕");
    }
    public async Task Recalc(string cabinetName)
    {
        model.Status.Busy($"正在重新计算……");
        List<Formula> formulars = UseFormula ? [] : context.Db.Queryable<Formula>().ToList();
        List<FormulaIndex> formularIndexes = UseFormula ? [] : context.Db.Queryable<FormulaIndex>().ToList();
        List<FormulaIndexCondition> conditions = UseFormula ? [] : context.Db.Queryable<FormulaIndexCondition>().ToList();
        var fm = new FormulaBuilder();
        DisplayInfo displayInfo = DisplayAttributeHelper.GetDisplayInfo<Xt2Point>();
        var p = new Xt2Point();
        string cardType = displayInfo.FieldDisplayNames[nameof(p.CardType)];
        string powerSupplyMethod = displayInfo.FieldDisplayNames[nameof(p.PowerSupplyMethod)];
        string terminalBoardModel = displayInfo.FieldDisplayNames[nameof(p.TerminalBoardModel)];
        string signalPlus = displayInfo.FieldDisplayNames[nameof(p.SignalPlus)];
        string signalMinus = displayInfo.FieldDisplayNames[nameof(p.SignalMinus)];
        string rTDCompensationC = displayInfo.FieldDisplayNames[nameof(p.RTDCompensationC)];
        string rTDCompensationE = displayInfo.FieldDisplayNames[nameof(p.RTDCompensationE)];
        string signalEffectiveMode = displayInfo.FieldDisplayNames[nameof(p.SignalEffectiveMode)];
        var cabinet = AllData.FirstOrDefault(a => a.Name == cabinetName);        
        foreach (var cage in cabinet.Cages)
        {
            foreach (var slot in cage.Slots)
            {
                if (slot.Board != null)
                {
                    foreach (var channel in slot.Board.Channels)
                    {
                        var point = channel.Point;
                        if (point != null)
                        {
                            point.SignalEffectiveMode = fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpressionNew(point, displayInfo.ClassName, signalEffectiveMode, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                            point.OFDisplayFormat = GetOfDisplayFormat(point.RangeUpperLimit, point.RangeLowerLimit);
                            point.TagName = GetTagName(point.SignalPositionNumber, point.ExtensionCode);
                            point.CardType = UseFormula ? GetIoCardTypeFormula(point) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpression(point, displayInfo.ClassName, cardType, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                            point.PowerSupplyMethod = UseFormula ? GetPowerSupplyMethodFormula(point) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpression(point, displayInfo.ClassName, powerSupplyMethod, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                            point.TerminalBoardModel = UseFormula ? GetTerminalBoxTypeFormula(point.CardType, point.PowerSupplyMethod, point.ElectricalCharacteristics) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpression(point, displayInfo.ClassName, terminalBoardModel, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                            point.CardNumberInCabinet = GetCardInCabinetNumber(cage.Index, slot.Index, point.CardType);
                            point.CardNumber = cabinet.Name + point.CardNumberInCabinet;
                            point.TerminalBoardNumber = GetTerminalBoardNumber(point.TerminalBoardModel, point.CardType, cage.Index, slot.Index, point.NetType);
                            point.CardAddress = GetCardAddress(cage.Index, slot.Index);
                            point.SignalPlus = UseFormula ? GetSingalPlusFormula(point) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpressionNew(point, displayInfo.ClassName, signalPlus, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                            point.SignalMinus = UseFormula ? GetSingalMinusFormula(point) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpressionNew(point, displayInfo.ClassName, signalMinus, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                            point.RTDCompensationC = UseFormula ? GetRTDCompensationEndC(point.SensorType, point.Channel) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpressionNew(point, displayInfo.ClassName, rTDCompensationC, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                            point.RTDCompensationE = UseFormula ? GetRTDCompensationEndD(point.SensorType, point.Channel) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpressionNew(point, displayInfo.ClassName, rTDCompensationE, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
        foreach (var board in cabinet.UnsetBoards)
        {
            foreach (var channel in board.Channels)
            {
                var point = channel.Point;
                if (point != null)
                {
                    point.Cage = 0;
                    point.Slot = 0;
                    point.Channel = channel.Index;
                    point.SignalEffectiveMode = fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpressionNew(point, displayInfo.ClassName, signalEffectiveMode, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                    point.OFDisplayFormat = GetOfDisplayFormat(point.RangeUpperLimit, point.RangeLowerLimit);
                    point.TagName = GetTagName(point.SignalPositionNumber, point.ExtensionCode);
                    point.CardType = UseFormula ? GetIoCardTypeFormula(point) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpression(point, displayInfo.ClassName, cardType, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                    point.PowerSupplyMethod = UseFormula ? GetPowerSupplyMethodFormula(point) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpression(point, displayInfo.ClassName, powerSupplyMethod, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                    point.TerminalBoardModel = UseFormula ? GetTerminalBoxTypeFormula(point.CardType, point.PowerSupplyMethod, point.ElectricalCharacteristics) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpression(point, displayInfo.ClassName, terminalBoardModel, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                    point.CardNumberInCabinet = GetCardInCabinetNumber(0, 0, point.CardType);
                    point.CardNumber = cabinet.Name + point.CardNumberInCabinet;
                    point.TerminalBoardNumber = GetTerminalBoardNumber(point.TerminalBoardModel, point.CardType, 0, 0, point.NetType);
                    point.CardAddress = GetCardAddress(0, 0);
                    point.SignalPlus = UseFormula ? GetSingalPlusFormula(point) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpressionNew(point, displayInfo.ClassName, signalPlus, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                    point.SignalMinus = UseFormula ? GetSingalMinusFormula(point) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpressionNew(point, displayInfo.ClassName, signalMinus, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                    point.RTDCompensationC = UseFormula ? GetRTDCompensationEndC(point.SensorType, point.Channel) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpressionNew(point, displayInfo.ClassName, rTDCompensationC, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                    point.RTDCompensationE = UseFormula ? GetRTDCompensationEndD(point.SensorType, point.Channel) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpressionNew(point, displayInfo.ClassName, rTDCompensationE, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
                }
            }
        }
        foreach (var point in cabinet.UnsetPoints)
        {
            point.Cage = 0;
            point.Slot = 0;
            point.Channel = 0;
            point.SignalEffectiveMode = fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpressionNew(point, displayInfo.ClassName, signalEffectiveMode, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);  
            point.OFDisplayFormat = GetOfDisplayFormat(point.RangeUpperLimit, point.RangeLowerLimit);
            point.TagName = GetTagName(point.SignalPositionNumber, point.ExtensionCode);
            point.CardType = UseFormula ? GetIoCardTypeFormula(point) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpression(point, displayInfo.ClassName, cardType, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
            point.PowerSupplyMethod = UseFormula ? GetPowerSupplyMethodFormula(point) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpression(point, displayInfo.ClassName, powerSupplyMethod, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
            point.TerminalBoardModel = UseFormula ? GetTerminalBoxTypeFormula(point.CardType, point.PowerSupplyMethod, point.ElectricalCharacteristics) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpression(point, displayInfo.ClassName, terminalBoardModel, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
            point.CardNumberInCabinet = GetCardInCabinetNumber(0, 0, point.CardType);
            point.CardNumber = cabinet.Name + point.CardNumberInCabinet;
            point.TerminalBoardNumber = GetTerminalBoardNumber(point.TerminalBoardModel, point.CardType, 0, 0, point.NetType);
            point.CardAddress = GetCardAddress(0, 0);
            point.SignalPlus = UseFormula ? GetSingalPlusFormula(point) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpressionNew(point, displayInfo.ClassName, signalPlus, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
            point.SignalMinus = UseFormula ? GetSingalMinusFormula(point) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpressionNew(point, displayInfo.ClassName, signalMinus, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
            point.RTDCompensationC = UseFormula ? GetRTDCompensationEndC(point.SensorType, point.Channel) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpressionNew(point, displayInfo.ClassName, rTDCompensationC, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
            point.RTDCompensationE = UseFormula ? GetRTDCompensationEndD(point.SensorType, point.Channel) : fm.FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpressionNew(point, displayInfo.ClassName, rTDCompensationE, formulars, formularIndexes, conditions);
        }
        AllData = [.. AllData];
        model.Status.Success("重新计算完毕");
    }
    public static string GetFieldDisplayName<T>(string fieldName)
    {
        Type type = typeof(T);
        var propertyInfo = type.GetProperty(fieldName);
        if (propertyInfo != null)
        {
            var displayAttribute = propertyInfo.GetCustomAttribute<DisplayAttribute>();
            if (displayAttribute != null)
            {
                return displayAttribute.Name;
            }
        }
        return fieldName; 
    }
    public string GetPowerSupplyMethodFormula(Xt2Point x)
    {
        try
        {
            if (x.CardType == "MD211" || x.CardType == "MD212" || x.CardType == "MD216")
            {
                return "--";
            }
            string powerType = x.PowerType ?? "";  
            char typeIndicator = powerType.Length > 0 ? powerType[0] : ' ';
            string typeDetail = powerType.Length >= 2 ? powerType.Last().ToString() : "";
            if (x.IoType.Contains("PROFIBUS") && string.IsNullOrEmpty(x.PowerType))
            {
                return "--";
            }
            switch (typeIndicator)
            {
                case 'A':
                    if (powerType.StartsWith("AI"))
                    {
                        switch (typeDetail)
                        {
                            case "1": return "DCS";
                            case "2": return "USER(提供24VDC)";
                            case "3": return "USER(提供220VAC)";
                            case "4":
                            case "5":
                            case "6":
                            case "7":
                            case "8":
                            case "9":
                                return "USER";
                            default:
                                return "DCS";
                        }
                    }
                    if (powerType.StartsWith("AO"))
                    {
                        string sensorType = x.SensorType ?? "";
                        if (!sensorType.Contains("24V") && !sensorType.Contains("220V"))
                        {
                            return "DCS";
                        }
                        else if (sensorType.Contains("24V"))
                        {
                            return "DCS(提供24VDC)";
                        }
                        else if (sensorType.Contains("220V"))
                        {
                            return "DCS(提供220VAC)";
                        }
                    }
                    break;
                case 'P':
                    switch (typeDetail)
                    {
                        case "1": return "DCS(提供24VDC)";
                        case "2": return "DCS(提供220VAC)";
                        case "3": return "USER";
                        default:
                            return "DCS";
                    }
                case 'F':
                    if (powerType.StartsWith("FF"))
                    {
                        switch (typeDetail)
                        {
                            case "1": return "DCS";
                            case "2": return "DCS(提供24VDC)";
                            case "3": return "DCS(提供220VAC)";
                            case "4":
                            case "5":
                                return "USER";
                            case "6":
                            case "7":
                            case "8":
                            case "9":
                                return "DCS";
                            default:
                                return "DCS";
                        }
                    }
                    break;
                case 'D':
                    if (powerType.StartsWith("DP"))
                    {
                        switch (typeDetail)
                        {
                            case "1": return "DCS";
                            case "2": return "DCS(提供220VAC)";
                            default:
                                return "Err";
                        }
                    }
                    if (powerType.StartsWith("DI"))
                    {
                        switch (typeDetail)
                        {
                            case "1": return "DCS";
                            case "2": return "DCS(提供独立24VDC)";
                            case "3": return "DCS(提供独立220VAC)";
                            case "4": return "USER(提供中间继电器线圈侧24VDC)";
                            case "5": return "USER(提供中间继电线圈侧220VAC)";
                            default:
                                return "DCS";
                        }
                    }
                    if (powerType.StartsWith("DO"))
                    {
                        switch (typeDetail)
                        {
                            case "1": return "DCS";
                            case "2": return "DCS(DCS提供独立24VDC)";
                            case "3": return "USER(DCS提供独立220VAC)";
                            case "4": return "USER";
                            case "5": return "USER(提供中间继电线圈侧220VAC)";
                            default:
                                return "DCS";
                        }
                    }
                    break;
                default:
                    return "ERR";
            }
            return "ERR";
        }
        catch (Exception ex)
        {
            var a = x.PowerType;
            throw new Exception("机柜供电计算错误，供电类型出错");
        }
    }
    public string GetTerminalBoxTypeFormula(string boardType, string powerSupply, string electricalCharacteristics)
    {              
        if (boardType == "DO211")
        {
            if (powerSupply.StartsWith("USER"))
            {
                return "TB231";
            }
            else if (powerSupply.StartsWith("DCS"))
            {
                return "TB233";
            }
        }
        if (boardType == "DI211")
        {
            if (powerSupply.StartsWith("DCS"))
            {
                return "TB222";
            }
            else if (powerSupply.StartsWith("USER"))
            {
                return "TB221";
            }
        }
        if (boardType == "FF211" && powerSupply.StartsWith("DCS"))
        {
            return "TB271";
        }
        else if (boardType == "DP211")
        {
            return "TB272";
        }
        else if (boardType == "AI216" && (electricalCharacteristics == "4~20mA") || (electricalCharacteristics == "4-20mA"))
        {
            return "TB241";
        }
        else if (boardType == "AI232")
        {
            return "TB246";
        }
        else if (boardType == "AO211")
        {
            return "TB251";
        }
        else if (boardType == "PI211" || boardType == "AO215")
        {
            return "TB244";
        }
        else if (boardType == "AI212")
        {
            return "TB241";
        }
        else if (boardType == "AI221")
        {
            return "TB242";
        }
        else if (boardType == "MD211")
        {
            return "TB244";
        }
        else if (boardType == "MD216")
        {
            return "--";
        }
        else
        {
            return "ERR";
        }
    }
    public string GetIoCardTypeFormula(Xt2Point data)
    {
        if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(data.ElectricalCharacteristics))
        {
            if (data.ElectricalCharacteristics.Contains("MODBUS") && data.ElectricalCharacteristics.Contains("TCP"))
            {
                return "MD216";
            }
            if (data.ElectricalCharacteristics.Contains("MODBUS") && data.ElectricalCharacteristics.Contains("RTU"))
            {
                return "MD211";
            }
            if (data.ElectricalCharacteristics.Contains("FF"))
            {
                return "FF211";
            }
            if (data.ElectricalCharacteristics.Contains("DP"))
            {
                return "DP211";
            }
        }
        if (data.IoType.Contains("FF"))
        {
            return "FF211";
        }
        if (data.IoType.Contains("PROFIBUS"))
        {
            return "DP211";
        }
        if (data.IoType.ToUpper().Contains("MODBUS") && data.IoType.ToUpper().Contains("TCP"))
        {
            return "MD216";
        }
        else if (data.IoType.ToUpper().Contains("MODBUS") && data.IoType.ToUpper().Contains("RTU"))
        {
            return "MD211";
        }
        if (data.Description.Contains("计量泵"))
        {
            if (data.IoType == "AI")
            {
                return "AI212";
            }
            else if (data.IoType == "AO")
            {
                return "AO211";
            }
        }
        switch (data.IoType.Trim())
        {
            case "AI":
                if ((data.ElectricalCharacteristics.Contains('4') && data.ElectricalCharacteristics.ToUpper().Contains(("20mA").ToUpper())))
                {
                    return "AI216";
                }
                if (data.ElectricalCharacteristics.Contains("TC"))
                {
                    return "AI221";
                }
                if (data.ElectricalCharacteristics.Contains("PT100"))
                {
                    return "AI232";
                }
                if (data.PowerType == ("AI8") || data.PowerType.Contains("AI7") || data.PowerType.Contains("AI9"))
                {
                    return "AI232";
                }
                return "未知AI板卡";
            case "DI":
                return "DI211";
            case "AO":
                return "AO215";
            case "DO":
                return "DO211";
            case "P":
            case "PI":
                return "PI211";
        }
        switch (data.PowerType.Trim())
        {
            case "AO1":
                return "AO211";
            case "AOH":
                return "AO215";
        }
        return "未知板卡";
    }
    public string GetOfDisplayFormat(string upperLimitStr, string lowerLimitStr)
    {
        if (double.TryParse(upperLimitStr, out double upperLimit) && double.TryParse(lowerLimitStr, out double lowerLimit))
        {
            double range = upperLimit - lowerLimit;
            string result;
            if (range <= 10)
            {
                result = "3"; 
            }
            else if (range <= 100)
            {
                result = "2"; 
            }
            else if (range <= 1000)
            {
                result = "1"; 
            }
            else if (range <= 100000)
            {
                result = "1"; 
            }
            else if (range > 1000000 || range < 0.0001)
            {
                if (range > 1000000)
                {
                    result = range.ToString("E1"); 
                }
                else 
                {
                    result = range.ToString("E3"); 
                }
            }
            else
            {
                result = "0"; 
            }
            return result;
        }
        else
        {
            return "";
        }
    }
    public string GetOfDisplayFormat(List<config_output_format_values> query, Xt2Point data)
    {
        _ = int.TryParse(data.RangeLowerLimit, out int low);
        _ = int.TryParse(data.RangeUpperLimit, out int high);
        if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(data.EngineeringUnit))
        {
            query = query.Where(r => r.RangeUnit == "").ToList();
        }
        else
        {
            query = query.Where(r => r.RangeUnit == data.EngineeringUnit).ToList();
        }
        if (query != null)
        {
            query = query.Where(f => f.RangeLow < low).ToList();
        }
        if (query != null)
        {
            query = query.Where(f => f.RangeHigh >= high).ToList();
        }
        if (query != null && query.Count == 1)
        {
            var formatValue = query.ToList().FirstOrDefault();
            return formatValue?.DecimalPlaces ?? "";
        }
        return "";
    }
    public string GetIoCardType(List<config_card_type_judge> list, Xt2Point data)
    {
        return list.Where(x => string.IsNullOrEmpty(x.IoType) || x.IoType == data.IoType)
            .Where(x => string.IsNullOrEmpty(x.SignalSpec) || x.SignalSpec.Split(";").Contains(data.ElectricalCharacteristics))
            .Where(x => string.IsNullOrEmpty(x.PowerType) || x.PowerType == data.PowerType)
            .FirstOrDefault()?.IoCardType ?? "未知板卡";
    }
    public string GetTerminalBoxType(List<config_terminalboard_type_judge> list, Xt2Point data)
    {
        return list.Where(x => string.IsNullOrEmpty(x.CardType) || x.CardType == data.CardType)
            .Where(x => string.IsNullOrEmpty(x.SignalType) || data.PowerSupplyMethod.StartsWith(x.SignalType))
            .Where(x => string.IsNullOrEmpty(x.SignalSpec) || data.ElectricalCharacteristics == x.SignalSpec)
            .FirstOrDefault()?.TerminalBlock ?? "ERR";
    }
    public string GetPowerSupplyMethod(List<config_power_supply_method> list, Xt2Point data)
    {
        return list.Where(x => string.IsNullOrEmpty(x.SupplyType) || x.SupplyType == data.PowerSupplyMethod)
            .Where(x => string.IsNullOrEmpty(x.CardType) || data.CardType == data.CardType)
            .Where(x => string.IsNullOrEmpty(x.SensorType) || data.SensorType == x.SensorType)
            .FirstOrDefault()?.SupplyModel ?? "ERR";
    }
    public string GetSignalPositionNumber(string SignalPositionNumber)
    {
        if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(SignalPositionNumber))
        {
            return "";
        }
        return SignalPositionNumber.Replace("-", "");
    }
    public string GetTagName(string oldVarName, string oldExtCode)
    {
        string processedText = "R" + oldVarName.Trim().Replace("-", "");
        if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(oldExtCode))
        {
            processedText += "_" + oldExtCode;
        }
        return processedText;
    }
    public string GetCardInCabinetNumber(int cage, int slot, string IOCardType)
    {
        if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(IOCardType)) return "";
        var formatted = $"{slot:00}";
        var typeStr = (IOCardType == "AI232" || IOCardType == "AI221") ? "TC" : IOCardType[..2];
        var result = $"{cage}{formatted}{typeStr}";
        return result;
    }
    public string GetTerminalBoardNumber(string terminalBoardModel, string cardType, int cage, int slot, string net)
    {
        if (terminalBoardModel == "--")
        {
            return "--";
        }
        else if (cardType == "FF211")
        {
            int netAddress = net == Xt2NetType.Net1.ToString() ? 1 : 2;
            return cage + slot.ToString("00") + "_" + netAddress + "FI";
        }
        else
        {
            return cage + slot.ToString("00") + "BN";
        }
    }
    public int GetCardAddress(int cage, int slot)
    {
        return (cage - 1) * 10 + slot;
    }
    public string GetSingalPlusFormula(Xt2Point data)
    {
        int channel;
        switch (data.TerminalBoardModel)
        {
            case "TB244":
                return data.IoType == "PI" ? ((data.Channel - 1) * 4 + 2).ToString() : (data.Channel * 2 + 22).ToString();
            case "TB271":
                var signalRightThree = data.TerminalBoardNumber.Length >= 3 ?
                                       data.TerminalBoardNumber.Substring(data.TerminalBoardNumber.Length - 3) : "";
                if (data.TerminalBoardNumber.EndsWith("FI") && data.NetType == Xt2NetType.Net1.ToString())
                {
                    return "FA+";
                }
                if (data.TerminalBoardNumber.EndsWith("FI") && data.NetType == Xt2NetType.Net2.ToString())
                {
                    return "FB+";
                }
                return "--";
            case "TB231":
            case "TB232":
            case "TB233":
                channel = data.Channel;
                return data.SignalEffectiveMode == "NC" ? $"{channel}A" : $"{channel}B";
            case "TB241":
                string powerSupplyStartFour_AB2 = data.PowerSupplyMethod.Length >= 4 ?
                                                  data.PowerSupplyMethod.Substring(0, 4) : "";
                channel = data.Channel;
                return powerSupplyStartFour_AB2 == "USER" ? $"{channel}A" :
                       data.PowerSupplyMethod.StartsWith("DCS") ? $"{channel}B" : "Err";
            case "TB222":
            case "TB221":
            case "TB246":
            case "TB243":
            case "TB242":
                channel = data.Channel;
                return $"{channel}A";
            case "TB272":
                channel = data.Channel;
                return $"{channel}--";
            case "TB251":
                string powerSupplyStartFourOrThree_AB2 = data.PowerSupplyMethod.Length >= 4 ?
                                                        data.PowerSupplyMethod.Substring(0, 4) : "";
                channel = data.Channel;
                if (powerSupplyStartFourOrThree_AB2 == "USER")
                {
                    return $"{channel}C";
                }
                else if (data.PowerSupplyMethod.StartsWith("DCS"))
                {
                    return $"{channel}B";
                }
                return $"{channel}Err";
            case "--":
                return "--";
            default:
                return "Err";
        }
    }
    public string GetSingalMinusFormula(Xt2Point data)
    {
        switch (data.TerminalBoardModel)
        {
            case "TB244":
                return data.IoType == "PI" ? (data.Channel * 4).ToString() : (data.Channel * 2 + 19).ToString();
            case "TB271":
                if (data.TerminalBoardNumber.EndsWith("FI") && data.NetType == Xt2NetType.Net1.ToString())
                {
                    return "FA-";
                }
                if (data.TerminalBoardNumber.EndsWith("FI") && data.NetType == Xt2NetType.Net2.ToString())
                {
                    return "FB-";
                }
                return data.Channel + "--"; 
            case "TB231":
            case "TB232":
            case "TB233":
                return data.Channel + "C";
            case "TB241":
                if (data.PowerSupplyMethod.StartsWith("USER"))
                {
                    return data.Channel + "C";
                }
                if (data.PowerSupplyMethod.StartsWith("DCS"))
                {
                    return data.Channel + "A";
                }
                break; 
            case "TB272":
                return data.Channel + "--";
            case "TB222":
            case "TB221":
            case "TB246":
            case "TB243":
            case "TB242":
                return data.Channel + "B";
            case "TB251":
                if (data.PowerSupplyMethod.StartsWith("DCS"))
                {
                    return data.Channel + "C";
                }
                if (data.PowerSupplyMethod.StartsWith("USER"))
                {
                    return data.Channel + "A";
                }
                break; 
            case "--":
                return "--";
            default:
                return "Err";
        }
        return "Err";
    }
    public async Task<string> GetSingalPlusAsync(List<config_connection_points> configs, Xt2Point data)
    {
        var config = configs
            .Where(x => string.IsNullOrEmpty(x.TerminalBoardModel) || x.TerminalBoardModel == data.TerminalBoardModel)
            .Where(x => string.IsNullOrEmpty(x.IoType) || x.IoType == data.IoType)
            .Where(x => string.IsNullOrEmpty(x.TerminalBoardNumber) || data.TerminalBoardNumber.EndsWith(x.TerminalBoardNumber))
            .Where(x => $"{x.SignalEffectiveMode}" == data.SignalEffectiveMode)
            .Where(x => string.IsNullOrEmpty(x.PowerSupply) || data.TerminalBoardNumber.StartsWith(x.PowerSupply))
            .SingleOrDefault()?.SignalPlus ?? "ERR";
        if (config == "ERR")
        {
            return "ERR";
        }
        var result = await CSharpScript.EvaluateAsync(config.Replace("CH", $"{data.Channel}"));
        return $"{result}";
    }
    public async Task<string> GetSignalMinusAsync(List<config_connection_points> configs, Xt2Point data)
    {
        var config = configs
            .Where(x => string.IsNullOrEmpty(x.TerminalBoardModel) || x.TerminalBoardModel == data.TerminalBoardModel)
            .Where(x => string.IsNullOrEmpty(x.IoType) || x.IoType == data.IoType)
            .Where(x => string.IsNullOrEmpty(x.TerminalBoardNumber) || data.TerminalBoardNumber.EndsWith(x.TerminalBoardNumber))
            .Where(x => $"{x.SignalEffectiveMode}" == data.SignalEffectiveMode)
            .Where(x => string.IsNullOrEmpty(x.PowerSupply) || data.TerminalBoardNumber.StartsWith(x.PowerSupply))
            .SingleOrDefault()?.SignalMinus ?? "ERR";
        if (config == "ERR")
        {
            return "ERR";
        }
        var result = await CSharpScript.EvaluateAsync(config.Replace("CH", $"{data.Channel}"));
        return $"{result}";
    }
    public string GetRTDCompensationEndC(string sensorType, int channel)
    {
        return sensorType.Contains("PT100") ? $"{channel}C" : "--";
    }
    public string GetRTDCompensationEndD(string sensorType, int channel)
    {
        return sensorType.Contains("四线制PT100") ? $"{channel}D" : "--";
    }
    public void test()
    {
    }
}
using System.Globalization;
using System.Windows.Data;
using System.Windows.Media;
namespace IODataPlatform.Views.Pages;
public class BoolToBrushConverter : IValueConverter {
    public object Convert(object value, Type targetType, object parameter, CultureInfo culture) {
        if ((bool)value) {
            return Application.Current.Resources["TextFillColorPrimaryBrush"];
        } else {
            return Brushes.Red;
        }
    }
    public object ConvertBack(object value, Type targetType, object parameter, CultureInfo culture) {
        throw new NotSupportedException();
    }
}
public class RateToBrushConverter : IMultiValueConverter {
    public object Convert(object[] values, Type targetType, object parameter, CultureInfo culture) {
        var rate = (int)(double)values[0];
        var comparisonValue = (int)values[1];
        if (rate >= comparisonValue) {
            return (Brush)Application.Current.Resources["TextFillColorPrimaryBrush"];
        } else {
            return Brushes.Red;
        }
    }
    public object[] ConvertBack(object value, Type[] targetTypes, object parameter, CultureInfo culture) {
        throw new NotSupportedException();
    }
}
using System.Reactive.Linq;
using System.Windows.Controls;
namespace IODataPlatform.Views.Pages;
public partial class DepXT1Page : INavigableView<DepXT1ViewModel> {
    public DepXT1ViewModel ViewModel { get; set; }
    public DepXT1Page(DepXT1ViewModel viewModel) {
        ViewModel = viewModel;
        DataContext = this;
        InitializeComponent();
        Loaded += DepXT1Page_Loaded;
    }
    private void DepXT1Page_Loaded(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e) {
        ColumnsVisibilityPanel.Children.Clear();
        var checkAll = new CheckBox() { Content = "全选", IsChecked = false };
        checkAll.Checked += (_, _) => ColumnsVisibilityPanel.Children.Cast<CheckBox>().AllDo(x => x.IsChecked = true);
        checkAll.Unchecked += (_, _) => ColumnsVisibilityPanel.Children.Cast<CheckBox>().AllDo(x => x.IsChecked = false);
        ColumnsVisibilityPanel.Children.Add(checkAll);
        var columnsInit = new List<string> { "房间号", "标签名", "盘箱柜号" };
        grid.Columns.ToObservable().Subscribe(x => {
            var check = new CheckBox() { Content = x.Header, IsChecked = columnsInit.Contains($"{x.Header}") };
            x.Visibility = check.IsChecked.GetValueOrDefault(false) ? Visibility.Visible : Visibility.Collapsed;
            check.Checked += (_, _) => x.Visibility = Visibility.Visible;
            check.Unchecked += (_, _) => x.Visibility = Visibility.Collapsed;
            ColumnsVisibilityPanel.Children.Add(check);
        });
    }
}
