using IODataPlatform.Models;
using IODataPlatform.Models.DBModels;
using IODataPlatform.Views.SubPages.Common;
using Microsoft.Extensions.DependencyInjection;
using Wpf.Ui.Extensions;
namespace IODataPlatform.Views.Pages;
partial class DepXT1ViewModel {
    [RelayCommand]
    private async Task Publish() {
        var projectId = Project?.Id ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        var subProjectId = SubProject?.Id ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        var allData = AllData ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        publishvm.Title = "系统一室IO发布";
        publishvm.SubProjectId = subProjectId;      
        publishvm.saveAction = SaveAndUploadFileAsync;
        publishvm.downloadAndCoverAction = DownloadAndCover;
        navigation.NavigateWithHierarchy(typeof(CommonPublishPage));              
    }
    private async Task DownloadAndCover(int subProjectId,int versionId)
    {
        var relativePath = storage.GetRealtimeIoFileRelativePath(subProjectId);
        await storage.WebCopyFilesAsync([(storage.GetPublishIoFileRelativePath(subProjectId, versionId), relativePath)]);
    }
}
using IODataPlatform.Models;
using IODataPlatform.Models.DBModels;
using Wpf.Ui.Extensions;
namespace IODataPlatform.Views.Pages
{
    partial class DepXT1ViewModel
    {
        [ObservableProperty]
        private ObservableCollection<Project>? projects;
        [ObservableProperty]
        private ObservableCollection<config_project_major>? majors;
        [ObservableProperty]
        private ObservableCollection<SubProject>? subProjects;
        [ObservableProperty]
        private Project? project;
        [ObservableProperty]
        private config_project_major? major;
        [ObservableProperty]
        private SubProject? subProject;
        [RelayCommand]
        private async Task AddSubProject()
        {
            var projectId = Project?.Id ?? throw new("请先选择项目");
            var majorId = Major?.Id ?? throw new("请选择专业");
            var textbox = new TextBox() { VerticalAlignment = VerticalAlignment.Center, PlaceholderText = "请输入子项名", Width = 180 };
            var result = await dialog.ShowSimpleDialogAsync(
                new SimpleContentDialogCreateOptions()
                {
                    Title = "添加子项",
                    Content = textbox,
                    PrimaryButtonText = "确定",
                    CloseButtonText = "取消",
                }
            );
            if (result != ContentDialogResult.Primary) { return; }
            if (string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(textbox.Text)) { throw new("请输入子项名"); }
            var subProjectName = textbox.Text;
            await context.Db.Insertable(new SubProject() { Name = subProjectName, ProjectId = projectId, MajorId = majorId }).ExecuteCommandIdentityIntoEntityAsync();
            SubProjects = new(await Task.Run(() => context.Db.Queryable<SubProject>().Where(x => x.ProjectId == projectId&&x.MajorId==majorId).ToList()));
            SubProject = SubProjects.Where(x => x.Name == subProjectName).SingleOrDefault();
        }
        [RelayCommand]
        private async Task DeleteSubProject()
        {
            var projectId = Project?.Id ?? throw new("请先选择要删除的子项");
            var subProjectId = SubProject?.Id ?? throw new("请先选择要删除的子项");
            if (!await message.ConfirmAsync("是否删除子项")) { return; }
            await context.Db.Deleteable<IoPublish>().Where(x => x.SubProjectId == subProjectId).ExecuteCommandAsync();
            await context.Db.Deleteable<SubProject>().Where(x => x.Id == subProjectId).ExecuteCommandAsync();
            await storage.DeleteSubprojectFolderAsync(subProjectId);
            await RefreshProjects();
        }
        private async Task RefreshProjects()
        {
            Projects = null;
            Projects = new(await context.Db.Queryable<Project>().ToListAsync());
        }
        async partial void OnProjectChanged(Project? value)
        {
            Major = null;
            if (value is null) { return; }
            Majors = new(await context.Db.Queryable<config_project_major>().Where(x => x.Department == Department.系统一室).Where(x => x.ProjectId == value.Id).ToListAsync());
            if (Majors.Count == 1) { Major = Majors[0]; }
        }
        async partial void OnMajorChanged(config_project_major? value)
        {
            SubProjects = null;
            if (value is null) { return; }
            SubProjects = new(await context.Db.Queryable<SubProject>().Where(x => x.MajorId == value.Id).ToListAsync());
            if (SubProjects.Count == 1) { SubProject = SubProjects[0]; }
        }
        async partial void OnSubProjectChanged(SubProject? value)
        {
            AllData = null;
            if (value is null) { return; }
            model.Status.Busy("正在获取数据……");
            await ReloadAllData();
            model.Status.Reset();
        }
        [RelayCommand]
        private async Task RefreshAll()
        {
            if (!await message.ConfirmAsync("是否全部刷新")) { return; }
            await RefreshProjects();
        }
    }
}
using IODataPlatform.Models.ExcelModels;
using IODataPlatform.Utilities;
using System;
using System.Collections.Generic;
using System.Collections.Immutable;
using System.Linq;
using System.Text;
using System.Threading.Tasks;
namespace IODataPlatform.Views.Pages
{
    partial class DepXT1ViewModel
    {
        [ObservableProperty]
        private ObservableCollection<IoData>? displayPoints;
        [ObservableProperty]
        private int displayPointCount;
        [ObservableProperty]
        private int allDataCount;
        [ObservableProperty]
        private bool isAscending = true; 
        private bool isRefreshingOptions = false; 
        partial void OnDisplayPointsChanged(ObservableCollection<IoData>? value)
        {
            DisplayPointCount = value?.Count ?? 0; 
        }
        partial void OnAllDataChanged(ObservableCollection<IoData>? value)
        {         
            AllDataCount = value?.Count ?? 0;           
            DisplayPoints = null;           
            RefreshFilterOptions();
            FilterAndSort();
        }
        public ImmutableList<CommonFilter> Filters { get; } = [
            new("机柜号"), new("IO类型"),
    ];
        [RelayCommand]
        private async Task ClearAllFilterOptions()
        {
            if (!await message.ConfirmAsync("确认重置全部筛选条件")) { return; }
            isRefreshingOptions = true;
            Filters.AllDo(x => x.Option = "全部");
            isRefreshingOptions = false;
            FilterAndSort();
        }
        partial void OnIsAscendingChanged(bool value)
        {
            FilterAndSort();
        }
        private void RefreshFilterOptions()
        {
            isRefreshingOptions = true;
            if (AllData == null)
            {
                Filters.ForEach(x => x.ClearAll());
            }
            else
            {              
                var filterDic = Filters.ToDictionary(x => x.Title);
                filterDic["机柜号"].SetOptions(AllData.Select(x => x.Cabinet));             
                filterDic["IO类型"].SetOptions(AllData.Select(x => x.IoType));              
            }
            isRefreshingOptions = false;
        }
        [RelayCommand]
        private void FilterAndSort()
        {
            if (isRefreshingOptions) { return; }
            if (AllData is null) { return; }
            var filterDic = Filters.ToDictionary(x => x.Title);
            var data = AllData
                .WhereIf(x => x.Cabinet == filterDic["机柜号"].Option, filterDic["机柜号"].Option != "全部")
                .WhereIf(x => x.IoType == filterDic["IO类型"].Option, filterDic["IO类型"].Option != "全部");
            DisplayPoints = [..data];
        }
    }
}
using System.Data;
using System.IO;
using IODataPlatform.Models.DBModels;
using IODataPlatform.Models.ExcelModels;
using IODataPlatform.Utilities;
using Microsoft.Xaml.Behaviors.Layout;
namespace IODataPlatform.Views.Pages
{
    partial class DepXT1ViewModel
    {
        [RelayCommand]
        private async Task Export(string param)
        {
            if (AllData == null) { throw new("没有可导出的数据"); }
            if (picker.SaveFile("Excel 文件(*.xlsx)|*.xlsx", param) is not string file) { return; }
            if (File.Exists(file)) { File.Delete(file); }
            model.Status.Busy($"正在{param}数据……");
            if (param == "导出IO点表")
            {
                var data = AllData.Reset(AllData).ToList();
                await ExportIOSubStation(data, file);
            }           
            model.Status.Success($"已成功{param}数据：{file}");
        }
        private async Task ExportIOSubStation(List<IoData> data, string filePath)
        {          
            using var dataTable = await data.ToTableByDisplayAttributeAsync();
            await excel.FastExportSheetAsync(dataTable, filePath, "系统一室IO表");
        }
    }
}
using System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations;
using System.Diagnostics;
using System.Reflection;
using IODataPlatform.Models.ExcelModels;
using IODataPlatform.Utilities;
using IODataPlatform.Views.SubPages.XT1;
using LYSoft.Libs.Editor;
using LYSoft.Libs.Wpf.WpfUI;
namespace IODataPlatform.Views.Pages
{
    partial class DepXT1ViewModel
    {
        [RelayCommand]
        private async Task Add()
        {
            if (SubProject is null) { return; }
            if (AllData is null) { return; }
            var data = new IoData();
            if (!EditData(data, "添加")) { return; }
            AllData.Add(data);
            await SaveAndUploadFileAsync();
        }
        [RelayCommand]
        private async Task Clear()
        {
            if (!await message.ConfirmAsync("确认清空")) { return; }
            AllData = [];
            await SaveAndUploadFileAsync();
        }
        [RelayCommand]
        private async Task Edit(IoData data)
        {
            var objToEdit = new IoData().CopyPropertiesFrom(data);
            if (!EditData(objToEdit, "编辑")) { return; }
            data.CopyPropertiesFrom(objToEdit);
            await SaveAndUploadFileAsync();
            await ReloadAllData();
        }
        [RelayCommand]
        private async Task Delete(IoData data)
        {
            _ = AllData ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
            if (!await message.ConfirmAsync("是否删除")) { return; }
            AllData.Remove(data);
            await SaveAndUploadFileAsync();
        }
        [RelayCommand]
        private async Task Import()
        {
            navigation.NavigateWithHierarchy(typeof(ImportPage));
        }
        [RelayCommand]
        private async Task Refresh()
        {
            model.Status.Busy("正在刷新……");
            await ReloadAllData();
            model.Status.Reset();
        }
        private bool EditData(IoData data, string title)
        {
            var builder = data.CreateEditorBuilder();
            builder.WithTitle(title);
            foreach (var property in typeof(IoData).GetProperties())
            {
                var propDisplayName = property.GetCustomAttribute<DisplayAttribute>()?.Name ?? property.Name;
                if (property.PropertyType == typeof(string))
                {
                    builder.AddProperty<string>(property.Name).WithHeader(propDisplayName).EditAsText();
                }
                else if (property.PropertyType == typeof(float))
                {
                    builder.AddProperty<float>(property.Name).WithHeader(propDisplayName).EditAsDouble().ConvertFromProperty(x => (double)x).ConvertToProperty(x => (float)x);
                }
                else if (property.PropertyType == typeof(int))
                {
                    builder.AddProperty<int>(property.Name).WithHeader(propDisplayName).EditAsInt();
                }
                else if (property.PropertyType == typeof(int?))
                {
                    builder.AddProperty<int?>(property.Name).WithHeader(propDisplayName).EditAsInt().ConvertFromProperty(x => x ?? default);
                }
                else if (property.PropertyType == typeof(DateTime?))
                {
                    builder.AddProperty<DateTime?>(property.Name).WithHeader(propDisplayName).EditAsDateTime().ConvertFromProperty(x => x ?? new()).ConvertToProperty(x => x == default ? null : x);
                }
                else
                {
                    Debugger.Break();
                }
            }
            return builder.Build().EditWithWpfUI();
        }
    }
}
using System.IO;
using IODataPlatform.Models;
using IODataPlatform.Models.DBModels;
using IODataPlatform.Models.ExcelModels;
using IODataPlatform.Models.ExtDBModels;
using IODataPlatform.Services;
using IODataPlatform.Utilities;
using IODataPlatform.Views.SubPages.Common;
using LYSoft.Libs.ServiceInterfaces;
using SqlSugar;
namespace IODataPlatform.Views.Pages;
public partial class DepXT1ViewModel(SqlSugarContext context, GlobalModel model, IMessageService message, IContentDialogService dialog, INavigationService navigation,
    StorageService storage, ExcelService excel, IPickerService picker, PublishViewModel publishvm) : ObservableObject, INavigationAware
{
    private bool isInit = false;
    [ObservableProperty]
    private ObservableCollection<IoData>? allData;       
    public void OnNavigatedFrom() {
    }
    public async void OnNavigatedTo() {
        if (!isInit) {
            await RefreshProjects();
            isInit = true;
        } else {
            try { await ReloadAllData(); } catch { }
        }
    }   
    private async Task ReloadAllData() {
        AllData = null;
        _ = Project?.Id ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        var subProjectId = SubProject?.Id ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        try {
            var file = await storage.DownloadRealtimeIoFileAsync(subProjectId);
            using var dataTable = await excel.GetDataTableAsStringAsync(file, true);
            var list = await Task.Run(() => new ObservableCollection<IoData>(dataTable.StringTableToIEnumerableByDiplay<IoData>()));
            AllData = list;
        } catch {
            AllData = [];
        }
    }
    [RelayCommand]
    private async Task ReadIODatabase() {
        if (picker.OpenFile("Access 文件(*.accdb)|*.accdb;") is not string file) { return; }
        model.Status.Busy("正在获取数据……");
        var result = new List<IoData>();
        var db = new SqlSugarScope(new ConnectionConfig()
        {
            ConnectionString = $"Provider=Microsoft.ACE.OLEDB.12.0;Data Source={file};Persist Security Info=False;",
            DbType = DbType.Access, 
            IsAutoCloseConnection = true,
            InitKeyType = InitKeyType.Attribute
        });
        var tblMasters = await db.Queryable<tbl_Master>().ToListAsync();
        var tblFCUS = await db.Queryable<tbl_FCU>().ToListAsync();
        var tblIOModules = await db.Queryable<tbl_IO_Module>().ToListAsync();
        var tblCabinets = await db.Queryable<tbl_Cabinet>().ToListAsync();
        model.Status.Busy("正在解析数据……");
        var datahelper = new FormularHelper();
        for (int i = 0; i < tblMasters.Count; i++) {
            var tag = tblMasters[i];
            var iOData = new IoData();
            iOData.TagName = tag.TagName;
            iOData.Prefix = datahelper.GetEx(tag.TagName);
            iOData.OldVarName = datahelper.GetTagNameSection(tag.TagName, 0);
            iOData.OldVarName = iOData.OldVarName[..^6];
            iOData.OldExtCode = datahelper.GetTagNameSection(tag.TagName, 1);
            iOData.ExtCode1 = datahelper.GetTagNameSection(tag.TagName, 2);
            iOData.ExtCode2 = datahelper.GetTagNameSection(tag.TagName, 3);
            iOData.Designation = tag.Designation;  
            var cabinet = string.IsNullOrEmpty(tag.IO_Module) ? "" : tag.IO_Module[..4];
            var currentFcu = tblFCUS.FirstOrDefault(t => t.Cabinet == cabinet);
            var currentCabinet = tblCabinets.FirstOrDefault(t => t.Cabinet == tag.Cabinet_No);
            var currentIOModule = tblIOModules.FirstOrDefault(t => t.IO_Module == tag.IO_Module);
            iOData.Unit = tag.Unit;
            iOData.Lot = currentFcu == null ? "" : currentFcu.FCU;
            iOData.SubItem = "无";
            iOData.FcuName = currentFcu == null ? "" : currentFcu.FCU_Name;
            iOData.Room = currentCabinet == null ? "" : currentCabinet.Room;
            iOData.Cabinet = tag.Cabinet_No;
            iOData.IoType = tag.IOType;
            iOData.Type = currentIOModule?.Type ?? string.Empty;
            iOData.IoCardNumber = datahelper.CalculateIoCardNumberAndBN(tag.IO_Module, "IO");
            iOData.Pin = tag.Pin;
            iOData.TAPartNumber = string.Empty;
            iOData.Component = datahelper.CalculateIoCardNumberAndBN(tag.IO_Module, "BN");
            iOData.SignalStart = "无";
            iOData.Destination = tag.Destination;
            iOData.PowerType = tag.PowerSupply;
            iOData.LoopVoltage = tag.LoopVoltage;
            iOData.ContactCapacity = tag.ContactCapacity;
            iOData.SignalSpec = tag.SignalSpec;
            iOData.Isolation = tag.Isolation;
            iOData.Ees = tag.EES;
            iOData.SensorType = tag.SensorType;
            iOData.TypicalLoopDrawing = "需要增加典回核查表";
            iOData.Sa = tag.SA;
            iOData.SoeTra = tag.SOETRA;
            iOData.IntExt = tag.INT_EXT;
            iOData.SafetyClassDivision = tag.SafetyClassDivision;
            iOData.FunctionalClass = tag.FunctionalClass;
            iOData.Seismic = tag.Seismic;
            iOData.System = tag.System;
            iOData.List = tag.List;
            iOData.DiagramNumber = tag.DiagramNumber;
            iOData.TransNo = tag.TransNo;
            result.Add(iOData);
        }
        AllData = [..result];
        model.Status.Busy("已完成");
        model.Status.Reset();
        await SaveAndUploadFileAsync();
    }
    public async Task SaveAndUploadFileAsync(int? versionId = null) {
        _ = Project?.Id ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        var subProjectId = SubProject?.Id ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        var allData = AllData ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        var relativePath = storage.GetRealtimeIoFileRelativePath(subProjectId);
        var absolutePath = storage.GetWebFileLocalAbsolutePath(relativePath);
        using var dataTable = await allData.ToTableByDisplayAttributeAsync();
        await excel.FastExportAsync(dataTable, absolutePath);
        await storage.UploadRealtimeIoFileAsync(subProjectId);
        if (versionId == null) { return; }
        await storage.WebCopyFilesAsync([(relativePath, storage.GetPublishIoFileRelativePath(subProjectId, versionId.Value))]);
    }
}
using IODataPlatform.Models.ExcelModels;
using System.Reflection;
using System.Windows.Controls;
using System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations;
namespace IODataPlatform.Views.Pages;
public partial class DepAQJPage : INavigableView<DepAQJViewModel> {
    public DepAQJViewModel ViewModel { get; }
    private List<Wpf.Ui.Controls.DataGrid> dataGrids = [];
    public DepAQJPage(DepAQJViewModel viewModel) {
        ViewModel = viewModel;
        DataContext = this;
        InitializeComponent();
        var columnsInit = new List<string> { "序号", "信号名称", "信号说明" };
        ColumnsVisibilityPanel.Children.Clear();
        var checkAll = new CheckBox() { Content = "全选", IsChecked = false };
        checkAll.Checked += (_, _) => ColumnsVisibilityPanel.Children.Cast<CheckBox>().AllDo(x => x.IsChecked = true);
        checkAll.Unchecked += (_, _) => ColumnsVisibilityPanel.Children.Cast<CheckBox>().AllDo(x => x.IsChecked = false);
        ColumnsVisibilityPanel.Children.Add(checkAll);
        typeof(AQJIoData).GetProperties().Select(x => x.GetCustomAttribute<DisplayAttribute>()?.Name ?? x.Name).AllDo(x => {
            var checkbox = new CheckBox() { Content = x, IsChecked = columnsInit.Contains(x) };
            checkbox.Checked += (_, _) => dataGrids.AllDo(d => d.Columns.Where(c => $"{c.Header}" == x).AllDo(c => c.Visibility = Visibility.Visible));
            checkbox.Unchecked += (_, _) => dataGrids.AllDo(d => d.Columns.Where(c => $"{c.Header}" == x).AllDo(c => c.Visibility = Visibility.Collapsed));
            ColumnsVisibilityPanel.Children.Add(checkbox);
        });
    }
    private void DataGrid_Loaded(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)
    {
        var dataGrid = sender.AsTrue<Wpf.Ui.Controls.DataGrid>();
        dataGrids.Add(dataGrid);
        var displayCols = ColumnsVisibilityPanel.Children.OfType<CheckBox>().Where(x => x.IsChecked == true).Select(x => $"{x.Content}");
        dataGrid.Columns.Skip(1).Where(x => !displayCols.Contains($"{x.Header}")).AllDo(x => x.Visibility = Visibility.Collapsed);
    }
    private void DataGrid_Unloaded(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)
    {
        dataGrids.Remove(sender.AsTrue<Wpf.Ui.Controls.DataGrid>());
    }
}

using IODataPlatform.Models;
using IODataPlatform.Models.DBModels;
using IODataPlatform.Views.SubPages.Common;
using Microsoft.Extensions.DependencyInjection;
using Wpf.Ui.Extensions;
namespace IODataPlatform.Views.Pages;
partial class DepAQJViewModel {
    [RelayCommand]
    private async Task Publish() {
        var projectId = Project?.Id ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        var subProjectId = SubProject?.Id ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        var allData = AllData ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        publishvm.Title = "安全级室IO发布";
        publishvm.SubProjectId = subProjectId;      
        publishvm.saveAction = SaveAndUploadFileAsync;
        publishvm.downloadAndCoverAction = DownloadAndCover;
        navigation.NavigateWithHierarchy(typeof(CommonPublishPage));              
    }
    private async Task DownloadAndCover(int subProjectId,int versionId)
    {
        var relativePath = storage.GetRealtimeIoFileRelativePath(subProjectId);
        await storage.WebCopyFilesAsync([(storage.GetPublishIoFileRelativePath(subProjectId, versionId), relativePath)]);
    }
}
using IODataPlatform.Models;
using IODataPlatform.Models.DBModels;
using Wpf.Ui.Extensions;
namespace IODataPlatform.Views.Pages;
partial class DepAQJViewModel
{
    [ObservableProperty]
    private ObservableCollection<Project>? projects;
    [ObservableProperty]
    private ObservableCollection<config_project_major>? majors;
    [ObservableProperty]
    private ObservableCollection<SubProject>? subProjects;
    [ObservableProperty]
    private Project? project;
    [ObservableProperty]
    private config_project_major? major;
    [ObservableProperty]
    private SubProject? subProject;
    [RelayCommand]
    private async Task AddSubProject()
    {
        var projectId = Project?.Id ?? throw new("请先选择项目");
        var majorId = Major?.Id ?? throw new("请选择专业");
        var textbox = new TextBox() { VerticalAlignment = VerticalAlignment.Center, PlaceholderText = "请输入子项名", Width = 180 };
        var result = await dialog.ShowSimpleDialogAsync(
            new SimpleContentDialogCreateOptions()
            {
                Title = "添加子项",
                Content = textbox,
                PrimaryButtonText = "确定",
                CloseButtonText = "取消",
            }
        );
        if (result != ContentDialogResult.Primary) { return; }
        if (string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(textbox.Text)) { throw new("请输入子项名"); }
        var subProjectName = textbox.Text;
        await context.Db.Insertable(new SubProject() { Name = subProjectName, ProjectId = projectId, MajorId = majorId }).ExecuteCommandIdentityIntoEntityAsync();
        SubProjects = new(await Task.Run(() => context.Db.Queryable<SubProject>().Where(x => x.ProjectId == projectId && x.MajorId == majorId).ToList()));
        SubProject = SubProjects.Where(x => x.Name == subProjectName).SingleOrDefault();
    }
    [RelayCommand]
    private async Task DeleteSubProject()
    {
        var projectId = Project?.Id ?? throw new("请先选择要删除的子项");
        var subProjectId = SubProject?.Id ?? throw new("请先选择要删除的子项");
        if (!await message.ConfirmAsync("是否删除子项")) { return; }
        await context.Db.Deleteable<IoPublish>().Where(x => x.SubProjectId == subProjectId).ExecuteCommandAsync();
        await context.Db.Deleteable<SubProject>().Where(x => x.Id == subProjectId).ExecuteCommandAsync();
        await storage.DeleteSubprojectFolderAsync(subProjectId);
        await RefreshProjects();
    }
    private async Task RefreshProjects()
    {
        Projects = null;
        Projects = new(await context.Db.Queryable<Project>().ToListAsync());
    }
    async partial void OnProjectChanged(Project? value)
    {
        Major = null;
        if(value is null) { return; }
        Majors = new(await context.Db.Queryable<config_project_major>().Where(x => x.Department == Department.安全级室).Where(x => x.ProjectId == value.Id).ToListAsync());
        if (Majors.Count == 1) { Major = Majors[0]; }
    }
    async partial void OnMajorChanged(config_project_major? value)
    {        
        SubProjects = null;
        if (value is null) { return; }
        SubProjects = new(await context.Db.Queryable<SubProject>().Where(x => x.MajorId == value.Id).ToListAsync());
        if (SubProjects.Count == 1) { SubProject = SubProjects[0]; }
    }
    async partial void OnSubProjectChanged(SubProject? value)
    {
        AllData = null;
        if (value is null) { return; }
        model.Status.Busy("正在获取数据……");
        await ReloadAllData();
        model.Status.Reset();
    }
    [RelayCommand]
    private async Task RefreshAll()
    {
        if (!await message.ConfirmAsync("是否全部刷新")) { return; }
        await RefreshProjects();
    }
}
using IODataPlatform.Models.ExcelModels;
using IODataPlatform.Utilities;
using System;
using System.Collections.Generic;
using System.Collections.Immutable;
using System.Linq;
using System.Text;
using System.Threading.Tasks;
namespace IODataPlatform.Views.Pages
{
    partial class DepAQJViewModel
    {
        [ObservableProperty]
        private ObservableCollection<AQJIoData>? displayPoints;
        [ObservableProperty]
        private int displayPointCount;
        [ObservableProperty]
        private int allDataCount;
        [ObservableProperty]
        private bool isAscending = true; 
        private bool isRefreshingOptions = false; 
        partial void OnDisplayPointsChanged(ObservableCollection<AQJIoData>? value)
        {
            DisplayPointCount = value?.Count ?? 0; 
        }
        partial void OnAllDataChanged(ObservableCollection<AQJIoData>? value)
        {         
            AllDataCount = value?.Count ?? 0;           
            DisplayPoints = null;           
            RefreshFilterOptions();
            FilterAndSort();
        }
        public ImmutableList<CommonFilter> Filters { get; } = [
            new("机柜号"), new("IO类型"),
    ];
        [RelayCommand]
        private async Task ClearAllFilterOptions()
        {
            if (!await message.ConfirmAsync("确认重置全部筛选条件")) { return; }
            isRefreshingOptions = true;
            Filters.AllDo(x => x.Option = "全部");
            isRefreshingOptions = false;
            FilterAndSort();
        }
        partial void OnIsAscendingChanged(bool value)
        {
            FilterAndSort();
        }
        private void RefreshFilterOptions()
        {
            isRefreshingOptions = true;
            if (AllData == null)
            {
                Filters.ForEach(x => x.ClearAll());
            }
            else
            {              
                var filterDic = Filters.ToDictionary(x => x.Title);
                filterDic["机柜号"].SetOptions(AllData.Select(x => x.机柜号));             
                filterDic["IO类型"].SetOptions(AllData.Select(x => x.IO类型));              
            }
            isRefreshingOptions = false;
        }
        [RelayCommand]
        private void FilterAndSort()
        {
            if (isRefreshingOptions) { return; }
            if (AllData is null) { return; }
            var filterDic = Filters.ToDictionary(x => x.Title);
            var data = AllData
                .WhereIf(x => x.机柜号 == filterDic["机柜号"].Option, filterDic["机柜号"].Option != "全部")
                .WhereIf(x => x.IO类型 == filterDic["IO类型"].Option, filterDic["IO类型"].Option != "全部");
            DisplayPoints = [..data];
        }
    }
}
using System.Data;
using System.IO;
using IODataPlatform.Models.DBModels;
using IODataPlatform.Models.ExcelModels;
using IODataPlatform.Utilities;
using Microsoft.Xaml.Behaviors.Layout;
namespace IODataPlatform.Views.Pages
{
    partial class DepAQJViewModel
    {
        [RelayCommand]
        private async Task Export(string param)
        {
            if (AllData == null) { throw new("没有可导出的数据"); }
            if (picker.SaveFile("Excel 文件(*.xlsx)|*.xlsx", param) is not string file) { return; }
            if (File.Exists(file)) { File.Delete(file); }
            model.Status.Busy($"正在{param}数据……");
            if (param == "导出IO清册")
            {
                var data = AllData.Reset(AllData).ToList();
                await ExportIOSubStation(data, file);
            }           
            model.Status.Success($"已成功{param}数据：{file}");
        }
        private async Task ExportIOSubStation(List<AQJIoData> data, string filePath)
        {          
            using var dataTable = await data.ToTableByDisplayAttributeAsync();
            await excel.FastExportSheetAsync(dataTable, filePath, "安全级IO清册");
        }
    }
}
using System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations;
using System.Diagnostics;
using System.Reflection;
using IODataPlatform.Models.ExcelModels;
using IODataPlatform.Utilities;
using IODataPlatform.Views.SubPages.AQJ;
using LYSoft.Libs.Editor;
using LYSoft.Libs.Wpf.WpfUI;
namespace IODataPlatform.Views.Pages;
partial class DepAQJViewModel {
    [RelayCommand]
    private async Task Add() {
        if (SubProject is null) { return; }
        if (AllData is null) { return; }
        var data = new AQJIoData();
        if (!EditData(data, "添加")) { return; }
        AllData.Add(data);
        await SaveAndUploadFileAsync();
    }
    [RelayCommand]
    private async Task Clear() {
        if (!await message.ConfirmAsync("确认清空")) { return; }
        AllData = [];
        await SaveAndUploadFileAsync();
    }
    [RelayCommand]
    private async Task Edit(AQJIoData data) {
        var objToEdit = new AQJIoData().CopyPropertiesFrom(data);
        if (!EditData(objToEdit, "编辑")) { return; }
        data.CopyPropertiesFrom(objToEdit);
        await SaveAndUploadFileAsync();
        await ReloadAllData();
    }
    [RelayCommand]
    private async Task Delete(AQJIoData data) {
        _ = AllData ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        if (!await message.ConfirmAsync("是否删除")) { return; }
        AllData.Remove(data);
        await SaveAndUploadFileAsync();
    }
    [RelayCommand]
    private async Task Import() {
        navigation.NavigateWithHierarchy(typeof(ImportPage));
    }
    [RelayCommand]
    private async Task Refresh() {
        model.Status.Busy("正在刷新……");
        await ReloadAllData();
        model.Status.Reset();
    }
    private bool EditData(AQJIoData data, string title) {
        var builder = data.CreateEditorBuilder();
        builder.WithTitle(title);
        foreach (var property in typeof(AQJIoData).GetProperties()) {
            var propDisplayName = property.GetCustomAttribute<DisplayAttribute>()?.Name ?? property.Name;
            if (property.PropertyType == typeof(string)) {
                builder.AddProperty<string>(property.Name).WithHeader(propDisplayName).EditAsText();
            } else if (property.PropertyType == typeof(float)) {
                builder.AddProperty<float>(property.Name).WithHeader(propDisplayName).EditAsDouble().ConvertFromProperty(x => (double)x).ConvertToProperty(x => (float)x);
            } else if (property.PropertyType == typeof(int)) {
                builder.AddProperty<int>(property.Name).WithHeader(propDisplayName).EditAsInt();
            } else if (property.PropertyType == typeof(int?)) {
                builder.AddProperty<int?>(property.Name).WithHeader(propDisplayName).EditAsInt().ConvertFromProperty(x => x ?? default);
            } else if (property.PropertyType == typeof(DateTime?)) {
                builder.AddProperty<DateTime?>(property.Name).WithHeader(propDisplayName).EditAsDateTime().ConvertFromProperty(x => x ?? new()).ConvertToProperty(x => x == default ? null : x);
            } else {
                Debugger.Break();
            }
        }
        return builder.Build().EditWithWpfUI();
    }
}
using IODataPlatform.Models;
using IODataPlatform.Models.ExcelModels;
using IODataPlatform.Services;
using IODataPlatform.Utilities;
using IODataPlatform.Views.SubPages.Common;
using LYSoft.Libs.ServiceInterfaces;
namespace IODataPlatform.Views.Pages;
public partial class DepAQJViewModel(SqlSugarContext context, GlobalModel model, IMessageService message, IContentDialogService dialog, INavigationService navigation,
    StorageService storage, ExcelService excel, IPickerService picker,PublishViewModel publishvm) : ObservableObject, INavigationAware {
    private bool isInit = false;
    public void OnNavigatedFrom() {
    }
    public async void OnNavigatedTo() {
        if (!isInit) {
            await RefreshProjects();
            isInit = true;
        } else {
            try { await ReloadAllData(); } catch { }
        }
    }
    [ObservableProperty]
    private ObservableCollection<AQJIoData>? allData;       
    public async Task SaveAndUploadFileAsync(int? versionId = null) {
        _ = Project?.Id ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        var subProjectId = SubProject?.Id ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        var allData = AllData ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        var relativePath = storage.GetRealtimeIoFileRelativePath(subProjectId);
        var absolutePath = storage.GetWebFileLocalAbsolutePath(relativePath);
        using var dataTable = await allData.ToTableByDisplayAttributeAsync();
        await excel.FastExportAsync(dataTable, absolutePath);
        await storage.UploadRealtimeIoFileAsync(subProjectId);
        if (versionId == null) { return; }
        await storage.WebCopyFilesAsync([(relativePath, storage.GetPublishIoFileRelativePath(subProjectId, versionId.Value))]);
    }
    private async Task ReloadAllData() {
        AllData = null;
        _ = Project?.Id ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        var subProjectId = SubProject?.Id ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        try {
            var file = await storage.DownloadRealtimeIoFileAsync(subProjectId);
            var data = await excel.GetDataTableAsStringAsync(file, true);
            var list = data.StringTableToIEnumerableByDiplay<AQJIoData>();
            AllData = [.. list];
        } catch {
            AllData = [];
        }
    }
}
using System.Data;
using System.IO;
using System.Windows.Controls;
using System.Windows.Controls.Primitives;
using System.Windows.Media;
using IODataPlatform.Models;
namespace IODataPlatform.Views.Pages;
public partial class DataComparePage : INavigableView<DataCompareViewModel> {
    private readonly ExcelService excel;
    public readonly GlobalModel model;
    public DataCompareViewModel ViewModel { get; }
    public DataComparePage(DataCompareViewModel viewModel, ExcelService excel, GlobalModel model) {
        ViewModel = viewModel;
        this.excel = excel;
        this.model = model;
        DataContext = this;
        InitializeComponent();
    }
    private async void Compare(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e) {
        if (!File.Exists(ViewModel.FilePath1)) { throw new("请选择Excel文件1"); }
        if (!File.Exists(ViewModel.FilePath2)) { throw new("请选择Excel文件2"); }
        if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(ViewModel.FieldName)) { throw new("请输入主键字段名"); }
        model.Status.Busy("正在比对数据");
        using var oldData1 = await excel.GetDataTableAsStringAsync(ViewModel.FilePath1, true);
        using var oldData2 = await excel.GetDataTableAsStringAsync(ViewModel.FilePath2, true);
        var newData1 = new DataTable();
        var newData2 = new DataTable();
        var fields = ValidateFieldsAndGetFields(oldData1, oldData2, newData1, newData2);
        var keys = ValidateKeyAndGetKeys(oldData1, oldData2);
        await SetData(oldData1, oldData2, newData1, newData2, fields, keys);
        SetColor(newData1, newData2);
        model.Status.Reset();
    }
    private void SetColor(DataTable data1, DataTable data2) {
        for (int row = 0; row < data1.Rows.Count; row++) {
            for (int col = 0; col < data1.Columns.Count; col++) {
                if ($"{data1.Rows[row][col]}" == $"{data2.Rows[row][col]}") { continue; }
                {
                    var dataGridRow = DataGrid1.ItemContainerGenerator.ContainerFromIndex(row) as DataGridRow;
                    if (dataGridRow != null) {
                        var presenter = FindVisualChild<DataGridCellsPresenter>(dataGridRow);
                        if (presenter != null) {
                            var dataGridCell = (DataGridCell)presenter.ItemContainerGenerator.ContainerFromIndex(col);
                            if (dataGridCell != null) {
                                dataGridCell.Background = new SolidColorBrush(Colors.Red);
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
                {
                    var dataGridRow = DataGrid2.ItemContainerGenerator.ContainerFromIndex(row) as DataGridRow;
                    if (dataGridRow != null) {
                        var presenter = FindVisualChild<DataGridCellsPresenter>(dataGridRow);
                        if (presenter != null) {
                            var dataGridCell = (DataGridCell)presenter.ItemContainerGenerator.ContainerFromIndex(col);
                            if (dataGridCell != null) {
                                dataGridCell.Background = new SolidColorBrush(Colors.Red);
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    }
    private static T FindVisualChild<T>(DependencyObject obj) where T : DependencyObject {
        for (int i = 0; i < VisualTreeHelper.GetChildrenCount(obj); i++) {
            DependencyObject child = VisualTreeHelper.GetChild(obj, i);
            if (child != null && child is T)
                return (T)child;
            else {
                T childOfChild = FindVisualChild<T>(child);
                if (childOfChild != null)
                    return childOfChild;
            }
        }
        return null;
    }
    private async Task SetData(DataTable oldData1, DataTable oldData2, DataTable newData1, DataTable newData2, string[] fields, string[] keys) {
        await Task.Run(() => {
            for (int row = 0; row < keys.Length; row++) {
                var key = keys[row];
                var obj1 = oldData1.Rows.Cast<DataRow>().SingleOrDefault(x => $"{x[ViewModel.FieldName]}" == key);
                var obj2 = oldData2.Rows.Cast<DataRow>().SingleOrDefault(x => $"{x[ViewModel.FieldName]}" == key);
                var row1 = newData1.NewRow();
                var row2 = newData2.NewRow();
                foreach (var field in fields) {
                    row1[field] = obj1?[field];
                    row2[field] = obj2?[field];
                }
                newData1.Rows.Add(row1);
                newData2.Rows.Add(row2);
            }
        });
        DataGrid1.ItemsSource = newData1.DefaultView;
        DataGrid2.ItemsSource = newData2.DefaultView;
    }
    private string[] ValidateKeyAndGetKeys(DataTable data1, DataTable data2) {
        var keys1 = data1.Rows.Cast<DataRow>().Select(x => $"{x[ViewModel.FieldName]}");
        var keys2 = data2.Rows.Cast<DataRow>().Select(x => $"{x[ViewModel.FieldName]}");
        if (keys1.Any(string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace)) { throw new("Excel文件1中主键有空白"); }
        if (keys2.Any(string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace)) { throw new("Excel文件2中主键有空白"); }
        if (keys1.Distinct().Count() != keys1.Count()) { throw new("Excel文件1中主键有重复数据"); }
        if (keys2.Distinct().Count() != keys2.Count()) { throw new("Excel文件2中主键有重复数据"); }
        return [.. keys1.Concat(keys2).Distinct().Order()];
    }
    private string[] ValidateFieldsAndGetFields(DataTable oldData1, DataTable oldData2, DataTable newData1, DataTable newData2) {
        var cols1 = oldData1.Columns.Cast<DataColumn>().Select(x => x.ColumnName).ToArray();
        var cols2 = oldData2.Columns.Cast<DataColumn>().Select(x => x.ColumnName).ToArray();
        if (cols1.Any(string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace)) { throw new("Excel文件1中有空白字段名"); }
        if (cols2.Any(string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace)) { throw new("Excel文件2中有空白字段名"); }
        if (cols1.Distinct().Count() != cols1.Length) { throw new("Excel文件1中有重复字段名"); }
        if (cols2.Distinct().Count() != cols1.Length) { throw new("Excel文件2中有重复字段名"); }
        if (!cols1.Order().SequenceEqual(cols2.Order())) { throw new("Excel文件1和Excel文件2中有不同字段名"); }
        if (!cols1.Contains(ViewModel.FieldName)) { throw new($"Excel文件中未找到字段：{ViewModel.FieldName}"); }
        var cols = cols1.Except([ViewModel.FieldName]).Prepend(ViewModel.FieldName);
        foreach (var col in cols) {
            newData1.Columns.Add(col);
            newData2.Columns.Add(col);
        }
        return [.. cols];
    }
    private void DataGrid1_LoadingRow(object sender, DataGridRowEventArgs e) {
    }
}

using LYSoft.Libs.ServiceInterfaces;
namespace IODataPlatform.Views.Pages;
public partial class DataCompareViewModel(IPickerService picker) : ObservableObject {
    [ObservableProperty]
    private string filePath1 = "请选择数据文件1";
    [ObservableProperty]
    private string filePath2 = "请选择数据文件2";
    [ObservableProperty]
    private string fieldName = string.Empty;
    [RelayCommand]
    private void PickFile(string param) {
        if (picker.OpenFile("Excel 文件(*.xls; *.xlsx)|*.xls; *.xlsx") is not string file) { return; }
        if (param == "1") { FilePath1 = file; } else {  FilePath2 = file; }
    }

using System.Reactive.Linq;
using System.Windows.Controls;
namespace IODataPlatform.Views.Pages;
public partial class DataAssetCenterPage : INavigableView<DataAssetCenterViewModel> {
    public DataAssetCenterViewModel ViewModel { get; }
    public DataAssetCenterPage(DataAssetCenterViewModel viewModel) {
        ViewModel = viewModel;
        DataContext = this;
        InitializeComponent();
        Loaded += DepXT2Page_Loaded;
    }
    private void DepXT2Page_Loaded(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e) {
        ColumnsVisibilityPanel.Children.Clear();
        var checkAll = new CheckBox() { Content = "全选", IsChecked = false };
        checkAll.Checked += (_, _) => ColumnsVisibilityPanel.Children.Cast<CheckBox>().AllDo(x => x.IsChecked = true);
        checkAll.Unchecked += (_, _) => ColumnsVisibilityPanel.Children.Cast<CheckBox>().AllDo(x => x.IsChecked = false);
        ColumnsVisibilityPanel.Children.Add(checkAll);
        var columnsInit = new List<string> { "版本", "机柜号", "点名" };
        Data.Columns.ToObservable().Subscribe(x =>{
            var check = new CheckBox() { Content = x.Header, IsChecked = columnsInit.Contains($"{x.Header}") };
            x.Visibility = check.IsChecked.GetValueOrDefault(false) ? Visibility.Visible : Visibility.Collapsed;
            check.Checked += (_, _) => x.Visibility = Visibility.Visible;
            check.Unchecked += (_, _) => x.Visibility = Visibility.Collapsed;
            ColumnsVisibilityPanel.Children.Add(check);
        });
    }
}

using IODataPlatform.Models;
using IODataPlatform.Models.DBModels;
using Microsoft.Extensions.DependencyInjection;
namespace IODataPlatform.Views.Pages;
partial class DataAssetCenterViewModel {
    [ObservableProperty]
    private ObservableCollection<Project>? projects;
    public ObservableCollection<Department> Departments { get; } = [.. Enum.GetValues<Department>()];
    [ObservableProperty]
    private ObservableCollection<SubProject>? subProjects;
    [ObservableProperty]
    private ObservableCollection<IoPublish>? publishVersions;
    [ObservableProperty]
    private Project? project;
    [ObservableProperty]
    private Department? department;
    [ObservableProperty]
    private SubProject? subProject;
    [ObservableProperty]
    private IoPublish? publishVersion;
    private async Task RefreshProjects() {
        Projects = null;
        Projects = new(await context.Db.Queryable<Project>().ToListAsync());
    }
    async partial void OnProjectChanged(Project? value) {
        await LoadSubProjects();
    }
    async partial void OnDepartmentChanged(Department? value) {
        await LoadSubProjects();
    }
    private async Task LoadSubProjects() {
        SubProjects = null;
        if (Project is null) { return; }
        if (Department is null) { return; }
        SubProjects = new(await context.Db.Queryable<SubProject>().Where(x => x.Department == Department).Where(x => x.ProjectId == Project.Id).ToListAsync());
        if (SubProjects.Count == 1) { SubProject = SubProjects[0]; }
    }
    async partial void OnSubProjectChanged(SubProject? value) {
        PublishVersions = null;
        if (SubProject is null) { return; }
        PublishVersions = new(await context.Db.Queryable<IoPublish>().Where(x => x.SubProjectId == SubProject.Id).ToListAsync());
        if (PublishVersions.Count == 1) { PublishVersion = PublishVersions[0]; }
    }
    async partial void OnPublishVersionChanged(IoPublish? value) {
        AllData = null;
        if (PublishVersion is null) { return; }
        model.Status.Busy("正在获取数据……");
        await ReloadAllData();
        model.Status.Reset();
    }
    [RelayCommand]
    private async Task RefreshAll() {
        if (!await message.ConfirmAsync("是否全部刷新")) { return; }
        Department = null;
        await RefreshProjects();
    }
}
using System.Collections.Immutable;
using IODataPlatform.Models.ExcelModels;
using IODataPlatform.Utilities;
namespace IODataPlatform.Views.Pages;
partial class DataAssetCenterViewModel {
    [ObservableProperty]
    private ObservableCollection<IoData>? displayData;
    [ObservableProperty]
    private int allDataCount;
    [ObservableProperty]
    private int displayDataCount;
    private bool isRefreshingOptions = false;
    public ImmutableList<CommonFilter> Filters { get; } = [new("版本"), new("机柜号"), new("点名")];
    [RelayCommand]
    private async Task ClearAllFilterOptions() {
        if (!await message.ConfirmAsync("确认重置全部筛选条件")) { return; }
        isRefreshingOptions = true;
        Filters.AllDo(x => x.Option = "全部");
        isRefreshingOptions = false;
        Filter();
    }
    private void RefreshFilterOptions() {
        isRefreshingOptions = true;
        if (AllData == null) {
            Filters.ForEach(x => x.ClearAll());
        } else {
            var filterDic = Filters.ToDictionary(x => x.Title);
            filterDic["版本"].SetOptions(AllData.Select(x => x.Version));
            filterDic["机柜号"].SetOptions(AllData.Select(x => x.Cabinet));
            filterDic["点名"].SetOptions(AllData.Select(x => x.TagName));
        }
        isRefreshingOptions = false;
    }
    [RelayCommand]
    private void Filter() {
        if (isRefreshingOptions) { return; }
        if (AllData is null) { return; }
        var filterDic = Filters.ToDictionary(x => x.Title);
        var data = AllData
            .WhereIf(x => x.Version == filterDic["版本"].Option, filterDic["版本"].Option != "全部")
            .WhereIf(x => x.Cabinet == filterDic["机柜号"].Option, filterDic["机柜号"].Option != "全部")
            .WhereIf(x => x.TagName == filterDic["点名"].Option, filterDic["点名"].Option != "全部");
        DisplayData = new(data);
    }
    partial void OnDisplayDataChanged(ObservableCollection<IoData>? value) {
        DisplayDataCount = DisplayData?.Count ?? 0;
    }
    partial void OnAllDataChanged(ObservableCollection<IoData>? value) {
        DisplayData = null;
        AllDataCount = AllData?.Count ?? 0;
        if (AllData is null) { return; }
        RefreshFilterOptions();
        Filter();
    }
}
#pragma warning disable CA1822 
using System.IO;
using IODataPlatform.Utilities;
namespace IODataPlatform.Views.Pages;
partial class DataAssetCenterViewModel {
    [RelayCommand]
    private async Task Export(string param) {
        if (AllData == null) { throw new("没有可导出的数据"); }
        if (picker.SaveFile("Excel 文件(*.xlsx)|*.xlsx", param) is not string file) { return; }
        if (File.Exists(file)) { File.Delete(file); }
        model.Status.Busy($"正在{param}数据……");
        if (param == "导出发布数据") {
            await ExportPublishData(file);
        } else if (param == "导出IoData") {
            await ExportIoData(file);
        } else {
            throw new("开发人员注意");
        }
        model.Status.Success($"已成功{param}数据：{file}");
    }
    private async Task ExportPublishData(string file) {
        var projectId = Project?.Id ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        var subProjectId = SubProject?.Id ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        var publishId = PublishVersion?.Id ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        await storage.DownloadPublishIoFileAsync(subProjectId, publishId);
        var localAbsolutePath = storage.GetWebFileLocalAbsolutePath(storage.GetPublishIoFileRelativePath(subProjectId, publishId));
        using var wb = excel.GetWorkbook(localAbsolutePath);
        wb.Save(file);
    }
    private async Task ExportIoData(string file) {
        if (AllData is null) { throw new("开发人员注意"); }
        await excel.FastExportAsync(await AllData.ToTableByDisplayAttributeAsync(), file);
    }
}
using IODataPlatform.Models;
using IODataPlatform.Models.ExcelModels;
using IODataPlatform.Services;
using IODataPlatform.Utilities;
using LYSoft.Libs.ServiceInterfaces;
namespace IODataPlatform.Views.Pages;
public partial class DataAssetCenterViewModel(SqlSugarContext context,
    GlobalModel model, IMessageService message, StorageService storage,
    ExcelService excel, IPickerService picker) : ObservableObject, INavigationAware {
    private bool isInit = false;
    public void OnNavigatedFrom() {
    }
    public async void OnNavigatedTo() {
        if (!isInit) {
            await RefreshProjects();
            isInit = true;    
        } else {
            try { await ReloadAllData(); } catch { }
        }
    }
    [ObservableProperty]
    private ObservableCollection<IoData>? allData;       
    private async Task ReloadAllData() {
        AllData = null;
        var projectId = Project?.Id ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        var department = Department ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        var subProjectId = SubProject?.Id ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        var publishId = PublishVersion?.Id ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        var file = await storage.DownloadPublishIoFileAsync(subProjectId, publishId);
        using var dataTable = await excel.GetDataTableAsStringAsync(file, true);
        if (Department == Models.Department.系统二室) {
            var list = await Task.Run(() => dataTable.StringTableToIEnumerableByDiplay<Xt2Point>().Select(x => x.ToIoData()));
            AllData = [.. list];
        }
    }
    [RelayCommand]
    private async Task Refresh() {
        model.Status.Busy("正在刷新……");
        await ReloadAllData();
        model.Status.Reset();
    }
}
using System.Reactive.Linq;
using System.Windows.Controls;
namespace IODataPlatform.Views.Pages;
public partial class CablePage : INavigableView<CableViewModel> {
    public CableViewModel ViewModel { get; }
    public CablePage(CableViewModel viewModel) {
        ViewModel = viewModel;
        DataContext = this;
        InitializeComponent();
        Loaded += DepXT2Page_Loaded;
    }
    private void DepXT2Page_Loaded(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e) {
        ColumnsVisibilityPanel.Children.Clear();
        var checkAll = new CheckBox() { Content = "全选", IsChecked = false };
        checkAll.Checked += (_, _) => ColumnsVisibilityPanel.Children.Cast<CheckBox>().AllDo(x => x.IsChecked = true);
        checkAll.Unchecked += (_, _) => ColumnsVisibilityPanel.Children.Cast<CheckBox>().AllDo(x => x.IsChecked = false);
        ColumnsVisibilityPanel.Children.Add(checkAll);
        var columnsInit = new List<string> { "机柜号", "点名" };
        Data.Columns.ToObservable().Subscribe(x =>{
            var check = new CheckBox() { Content = x.Header, IsChecked = columnsInit.Contains($"{x.Header}") };
            x.Visibility = check.IsChecked.GetValueOrDefault(false) ? Visibility.Visible : Visibility.Collapsed;
            check.Checked += (_, _) => x.Visibility = Visibility.Visible;
            check.Unchecked += (_, _) => x.Visibility = Visibility.Collapsed;
            ColumnsVisibilityPanel.Children.Add(check);
        });
    }
}

namespace IODataPlatform.Views.Pages;
partial class CableViewModel {
    [RelayCommand]
    private void Publish() {
        navigation.NavigateWithHierarchy(typeof(SubPages.Cable.PublishPage));
    }
}
using IODataPlatform.Models;
using IODataPlatform.Models.DBModels;
using Microsoft.Extensions.DependencyInjection;
using Wpf.Ui.Extensions;
namespace IODataPlatform.Views.Pages;
partial class CableViewModel {
    [ObservableProperty]
    private ObservableCollection<Project>? projects;
    [ObservableProperty]
    private ObservableCollection<config_project_major>? majors;
    [ObservableProperty]
    private ObservableCollection<SubProject>? subProjects1;
    [ObservableProperty]
    private ObservableCollection<SubProject>? subProjects2;
    [ObservableProperty]
    private ObservableCollection<TerminationPublish>? terminations1;
    [ObservableProperty]
    private ObservableCollection<TerminationPublish>? terminations2;
    [ObservableProperty]
    private Project? project;
    [ObservableProperty]
    private config_project_major? major1;
    [ObservableProperty]
    private config_project_major? major2;
    [ObservableProperty]
    private SubProject? subProject1;
    [ObservableProperty]
    private SubProject? subProject2;
    private async Task RefreshProjects() {
        Projects = null;
        Projects = new(await context.Db.Queryable<Project>().ToListAsync());
    }
    async partial void OnProjectChanged(Project? value) {
        Major1 = null;
        Major2 = null;
        if (value is null) { return; }
        Majors = new(await context.Db.Queryable<config_project_major>().Where(x => x.ProjectId == value.Id).ToListAsync());
        if (Majors.Count == 1) { Major1 = Majors[0]; Major2 = Majors[0]; }
    }
    async partial void OnMajor1Changed(config_project_major? value) {
        SubProjects1 = null;
        if (value is null) { return; }
        SubProjects1 = new(await context.Db.Queryable<SubProject>().Where(x => x.MajorId == value.Id).ToListAsync());
        if (SubProjects1.Count == 1) { SubProject1 = SubProjects1[0]; }
    }
    async partial void OnMajor2Changed(config_project_major? value) {
        SubProjects2 = null;
        if (value is null) { return; }
        SubProjects2 = new(await context.Db.Queryable<SubProject>().Where(x => x.MajorId == value.Id).ToListAsync());
        if (SubProjects2.Count == 1) { SubProject2 = SubProjects2[0]; }
    }
    async partial void OnSubProject1Changed(SubProject? value) {
        AllData = null;
        model.Status.Busy("正在获取数据……");
        await ReloadAllData();
        model.Status.Reset();
    }
    async partial void OnSubProject2Changed(SubProject? value) {
        AllData = null;
        if (value is null) { return; }
        model.Status.Busy("正在获取数据……");
        await ReloadAllData();
        model.Status.Reset();
    }
    [RelayCommand]
    private async Task RefreshAll() {
        if (!await message.ConfirmAsync("是否全部刷新")) { return; }
        await RefreshProjects();
    }
}
#pragma warning disable CA1822 
using System.IO;
using System.Security.Policy;
using System.Windows.Media;
using IODataPlatform.Models;
using IODataPlatform.Models.DBModels;
using IODataPlatform.Models.ExcelModels;
using IODataPlatform.Utilities;
using IODataPlatform.Views.SubPages.Cable;
using Microsoft.Extensions.DependencyInjection;
using Wpf.Ui.Extensions;
namespace IODataPlatform.Views.Pages;
partial class CableViewModel {
    [RelayCommand]
    private void Import(string param) {
        if (param == "导入发布端接数据") {
            ImportIoData();
        } else if (param == "导入数据") {
            ImportData();
        } else {
            throw new("开发人员注意");
        }
    }
    private void ImportIoData() {
        navigation.NavigateWithHierarchy(typeof(MatchPage));
    }
    private void ImportData() {
        navigation.NavigateWithHierarchy(typeof(SubPages.Termination.ImportPage));
    }
    [RelayCommand]
    private async Task Export(string param) {
        _ = AllData ?? throw new("没有可导出的数据");
        if (picker.SaveFile("Excel 文件(*.xlsx)|*.xlsx", param) is not string file) { return; }
        if (File.Exists(file)) { File.Delete(file); }
        model.Status.Busy($"正在{param}……");
        if (param == "导出全部数据") {
            await ExportAllData(file);
        } else if (param == "导出筛选数据") {
            await ExportFilterData(file);
        } else {
            throw new("开发人员注意");
        }
        model.Status.Success($"已成功{param}：{file}");
    }
    private async Task ExportAllData(string file) {
        if (AllData is null) { throw new("开发人员注意"); }
        await excel.FastExportAsync(await AllData.ToTableByDisplayAttributeAsync(), file);
    }
    private async Task ExportFilterData(string file) {
        if (DisplayData is null) { throw new("开发人员注意"); }
        await excel.FastExportAsync(await DisplayData.ToTableByDisplayAttributeAsync(), file);
    }
}
using System.Collections.Immutable;
using IODataPlatform.Models.ExcelModels;
using IODataPlatform.Utilities;
namespace IODataPlatform.Views.Pages;
partial class CableViewModel {
    [ObservableProperty]
    private ObservableCollection<CableData>? displayData;
    [ObservableProperty]
    private int allDataCount;
    [ObservableProperty]
    private int displayDataCount;
    private bool isRefreshingOptions = false;
    public ImmutableList<CommonFilter> Filters { get; } = [  ]; 
    [RelayCommand]
    private async Task ClearAllFilterOptions() {
        if (!await message.ConfirmAsync("确认重置全部筛选条件")) { return; }
        isRefreshingOptions = true;
        Filters.AllDo(x => x.Option = "全部");
        isRefreshingOptions = false;
        Filter();
    }
    private void RefreshFilterOptions() {
        isRefreshingOptions = true;
        if (AllData == null) {
            Filters.ForEach(x => x.ClearAll());
        } else {
            var filterDic = Filters.ToDictionary(x => x.Title);
        }
        isRefreshingOptions = false;
    }
    [RelayCommand]
    private void Filter() {
        if (isRefreshingOptions) { return; }
        if (AllData is null) { return; }
        var filterDic = Filters.ToDictionary(x => x.Title);
        var data = AllData
            ;
        DisplayData = new(data);
    }
    partial void OnDisplayDataChanged(ObservableCollection<CableData>? value) {
        DisplayDataCount = DisplayData?.Count ?? 0;
    }
    partial void OnAllDataChanged(ObservableCollection<CableData>? value) {
        DisplayData = null;
        AllDataCount = AllData?.Count ?? 0;
        if (AllData is null) { return; }
        RefreshFilterOptions();
        Filter();
    }
}
using System.IO;
using IODataPlatform.Models;
using IODataPlatform.Models.DBModels;
using IODataPlatform.Models.ExcelModels;
using IODataPlatform.Services;
using IODataPlatform.Utilities;
using IODataPlatform.Views.SubPages.Cable;
using IODataPlatform.Views.SubPages.Common;
using LYSoft.Libs.ServiceInterfaces;
namespace IODataPlatform.Views.Pages;
public partial class CableViewModel(SqlSugarContext context, INavigationService navigation, ConfigTableViewModel configvm,
    GlobalModel model, IMessageService message, IContentDialogService dialog, StorageService storage,
    ExcelService excel, IPickerService picker) : ObservableObject, INavigationAware {
    private bool isInit = false;
    public void OnNavigatedFrom() {
    }
    public async void OnNavigatedTo() {
        if (!isInit) {
            await RefreshProjects();
            isInit = true;
        } else {
            try { await ReloadAllData(); } catch { }
        }
    }
    [ObservableProperty]
    private ObservableCollection<CableData>? allData;       
    public async Task SaveAndUploadRealtimeFileAsync(int? versionId = null) {
        _ = Project?.Id ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        var subProjectId1 = SubProject1?.Id ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        var subProjectId2 = SubProject2?.Id ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        var allData = AllData ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        var relativePath = storage.GetRealtimeCableFileRelativePath(subProjectId1, subProjectId2);
        var absolutePath = storage.GetWebFileLocalAbsolutePath(relativePath);
        using var dataTable = await allData.ToTableByDisplayAttributeAsync();
        await excel.FastExportAsync(dataTable, absolutePath);
        await storage.UploadRealtimeCableFileAsync(subProjectId1, subProjectId2);
        if (versionId == null) { return; }
        var publishRelativePath = storage.GetPublishCableFileRelativePath(subProjectId1, subProjectId2, versionId.Value);
        var publishAbsolutePath = storage.GetWebFileLocalAbsolutePath(publishRelativePath);
        File.Copy(absolutePath, publishAbsolutePath, true);
        await storage.WebCopyFilesAsync([(relativePath, publishRelativePath)]);
    }
    public async Task ReloadAllData() {
        AllData = null;
        _ = Project?.Id ?? throw new("开发人员注意");
        var subProjectId1 = SubProject1?.Id;
        var subProjectId2 = SubProject2?.Id;
        if (subProjectId1 == null || subProjectId2 == null) { return; }
        try {
            var file = await storage.DownloadRealtimeCableFileAsync(subProjectId1.Value, subProjectId2.Value);
            using var dataTable = await excel.GetDataTableAsStringAsync(file, true);
            var list = await Task.Run(dataTable.StringTableToIEnumerableByDiplay<CableData>);
            AllData = [.. list];
        } catch {
            AllData = [];
        }
    }
    [RelayCommand]
    private async Task Refresh() {
        model.Status.Busy("正在刷新……");
        await ReloadAllData();
        model.Status.Reset();
    }
    [RelayCommand]
    private async Task GoToMatchPage()
    {
        await Task.Delay(1);
        navigation.NavigateWithHierarchy(typeof(MatchPage));
    }
    [RelayCommand]
    private void EditConfigurationTable(string param)
    {
        configvm.Title = param;
        configvm.DataType = param switch
        {
            "配置线缆列别及色标" => typeof(config_cable_categoryAndColor),
            "配置电缆特性代码" => typeof(config_cable_spec),
            "配置电缆的起始流水号" => typeof(config_cable_startNumber),
            "配置电缆的系统号" => typeof(config_cable_systemNumber),            
            _ => throw new NotImplementedException(),
        };
        navigation.NavigateWithHierarchy(typeof(ConfigTablePage));
    }
}

using System.Globalization;
using System.Text;
using System.Text.RegularExpressions;
namespace IODataPlatform.Utilities;
public partial class RegexDao {
    private RegexDao() { }
    private static RegexDao? instance = null;
    public static RegexDao GetInstance() {
        return instance ??= new();
    }
    public static bool IsChineseCh(string input) {
        return IsMatch(@"^[\u4e00-\u9fa5]+$", input);
    }
    public static bool IsPhone(string input) {
        string pattern = "^\\(0\\d{2}\\)[- ]?\\d{8}$|^0\\d{2}[- ]?\\d{8}$|^\\(0\\d{3}\\)[- ]?\\d{7}$|^0\\d{3}[- ]?\\d{7}$";
        return IsMatch(pattern, input);
    }
    public static bool IsMobilePhone(string input) {
        return IsMatch(@"^13\\d{9}$", input);
    }
    public static bool IsNumber(string input) {
        string pattern = "^-?\\d+$|^(-?\\d+)(\\.\\d+)?$";
        return IsMatch(pattern, input);
    }
    public static bool IsNotNagtive(string input) {
        return IsMatch(@"^\d+$", input);
    }
    public static bool IsUint(string input) {
        return IsMatch(@"^[0-9]*[1-9][0-9]*$", input);
    }
    public static bool IsEnglisCh(string input) {
        return IsMatch(@"^[A-Za-z]+$", input);
    }
    public static bool IsEmail(string input) {
        string pattern = @"^([\w-\.]+)@((\[[0-9]{1,3}\.[0-9]{1,3}\.[0-9]{1,3}\.)|(([\w-]+\.)+))([a-zA-Z]{2,4}|[0-9]{1,3})(\]?)$";
        return IsMatch(pattern, input);
    }
    public static bool IsNumAndEnCh(string input) {
        return IsMatch(@"^[A-Za-z0-9]+$", input);
    }
    public static bool IsURL(string input) {
        string pattern = @"^[a-zA-Z]+:
        return IsMatch(pattern, input);
    }
    public static float GetDigitsAsFloat(string str) {
        var sb = new StringBuilder();
        var dotEncountered = false;
        foreach (char c in str) {
            if (char.IsDigit(c)) {
                sb.Append(c);
            } else if (c == '.' && !dotEncountered) {
                sb.Append(c);
                dotEncountered = true;
            }
        }
        return float.Parse(sb.ToString(), CultureInfo.InvariantCulture);
    }
    public static bool IsIPv4(string input) {
        string[] IPs = input.Split('.');
        for (int i = 0; i < IPs.Length; i++) {
            if (!IsMatch(@"^\d+$", IPs[i])) {
                return false;
            }
            if (Convert.ToUInt16(IPs[i]) > 255) {
                return false;
            }
        }
        return true;
    }
    public static bool IsIPV6(string input) {
        var temp = input;
        var strs = temp.Split(':');
        if (strs.Length > 8) {
            return false;
        }
        int count = GetStringCount(input, "::");
        if (count > 1) {
            return false;
        } else if (count == 0) {
            return IsMatch(@"^([\da-f]{1,4}:){7}[\da-f]{1,4}$", input);
        } else {
            return IsMatch(@"^([\da-f]{1,4}:){0,5}::([\da-f]{1,4}:){0,5}[\da-f]{1,4}$", input);
        }
    }
    #region 正则的通用方法
    public static int GetCount(string input) {
        return ChineseRegex().Replace(input, "aa").Length;
    }
    public static bool IsMatch(string pattern, string input) {
        if (input == null || input == "") return false;
        var regex = new Regex(pattern);
        return regex.IsMatch(input);
    }
    public static string Replace(string pattern, string input, string replacement) {
        var regex = new Regex(pattern);
        return regex.Replace(input, replacement);
    }
    public static string[] Split(string pattern, string input) {
        var regex = new Regex(pattern);
        return regex.Split(input);
    }
    private static int GetStringCount(string input, string compare) {
        int index = input.IndexOf(compare);
        if (index != -1) {
            return 1 + GetStringCount(input[(index + compare.Length)..], compare);
        } else {
            return 0;
        }
    }
    [GeneratedRegex(@"[\u4e00-\u9fa5/g]")]
    private static partial Regex ChineseRegex();
    #endregion
}

}

        {

        public string CalculateIoCardNumberAndBN(string ioModule, string lastfix)
        {
            if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(ioModule) || ioModule.Length < 7)
            {
                return ioModule + lastfix;
            }
            string rightThreeDigits = ioModule.Substring(ioModule.Length - 3, 3);
            if (ioModule[6] == '1')
            {
                int number = int.Parse(rightThreeDigits) + 2;
                return number.ToString("D3") + lastfix; 
            }
            else
            {
                return rightThreeDigits + lastfix;
            }
        }
        public string GetTagNameSection(string tagName, int index)
        {
            if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(tagName)) return "";
            if (GetEx(tagName) != "")
            {
                tagName = tagName.Remove(0, 2);
            }
            var tagArr = tagName.Split('_');
            if (tagArr != null && tagArr.Length > 0 && tagArr.Length <= 4)
            {
                var middle = -1;
                for (int i = 0; i < tagArr.Length; i++)
                {
                    if (tagArr[i] == "H" || tagArr[i] == "HO" || tagArr[i] == "HC" || tagArr[i] == "SA" || tagArr[i] == "DH")
                    {
                        middle = i;
                    }
                }
                switch (index)
                {
                    case 0:
                        if (middle == -1)
                        {
                            if (tagArr.Length > 2)
                            {
                                return "";
                            }
                            else
                            {
                                return tagArr[0];
                            }
                        }
                        return tagArr[0];
                    case 1:
                        string str = "";
                        if (middle == -1)
                        {
                            if (tagArr.Length == 2)
                            {
                                return tagArr[1];
                            }
                            return str;
                        }
                        for (int i = 1; i < middle; i++)
                        {
                            str += i == middle - 1 ? tagArr[i] : tagArr[i] + "_";
                        }
                        return str;
                    case 2:
                        if (middle == -1)
                        {
                            return "";
                        }
                        return tagArr[middle];
                    case 3:
                        string str1 = "";
                        if (middle == -1)
                        {
                            return str1;
                        }
                        for (int i = middle + 1; i < tagArr.Length; i++)
                        {
                            str1 += i == tagArr.Length - 1 ? tagArr[i] : tagArr[i] + "_";
                        }
                        return str1;
                    default:
                        break;
                }
            }
            return "";
        }
        public string GetEx(string tagName)
        {
            if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(tagName) || tagName.Length < 2)
            {
                return "";
            }
            var firstChar = tagName[0];
            var secondChar = tagName[1];
            if (RegexDao.IsEnglisCh(firstChar.ToString()) && RegexDao.IsNumber(secondChar.ToString()))
            {
                return tagName.Substring(0, 2);
            }
            return "";
        }
        public int CountCharacterOccurrences(string str, char character)
        {
            int count = 0;
            foreach (char c in str)
            {
                if (c == character)
                {
                    count++;
                }
            }
            return count;
        }
        public bool JudgeIsSame(string 信号位号, string 仪表功能号)
        {
            try
            {
                if (信号位号[..2] != 仪表功能号[..2]) { return false; }
                return 信号位号.Split("-").Last() == 仪表功能号.Split("-").Last();
            }
            catch (Exception)
            {
                return false;
            }
        }
        public static float GetDigitsAsFloat(string str)
        {
            var sb = new StringBuilder();
            bool dotEncountered = false;
            foreach (char c in str)
            {
                if (char.IsDigit(c))
                {
                    sb.Append(c);
                }
                else if (c == '.' && !dotEncountered)
                {
                    sb.Append(c);
                    dotEncountered = true;
                }
            }
            return float.Parse(sb.ToString(), CultureInfo.InvariantCulture);
        }
