        #region 自动IO分配
        public List<Xt2Cabinet> AutoAllocateIO(List<Xt2Cabinet> cabinetInfos, List<config_card_type_judge> configs, double rate)
        {
            foreach (Xt2Cabinet cabinet in cabinetInfos)
            {
                AutoAllocateIO(cabinet, configs, rate);
            }
            return cabinetInfos;
        }
        public Xt2Cabinet AutoAllocateIO(Xt2Cabinet cabinet, List<config_card_type_judge> configs, double rate)
        {
            var allpoints = cabinet.ToPoint().Where(c => c.PowerType != null).Select(t => t.PowerType).Distinct();
            foreach (var tag in allpoints) 
            {                
                if (!powerSupplyGrouping.ContainsKey(tag))
                {
                    powerSupplyGrouping.Add(tag, tag);
                }
            }
            ClearPointsAndAddToUnset(cabinet);
            var unsetTags = cabinet.UnsetPoints.Where(u => u.PointType == Xt2PointType.Normal).ToList();
            var alarmTags = cabinet.UnsetPoints.Where(u => u.PointType == Xt2PointType.Alarm).ToList();
            var lff = unsetTags.Where(c => c.IoType.ToUpper().Contains("FF")).ToList();
            var lboxB = unsetTags.Where(c => c.IoType.ToUpper().Contains("PROFIBUS")).ToList();
            var lleft = unsetTags.Except(lff).Except(lboxB).ToList();
            var lnormal = lleft.Where(l => string.IsNullOrEmpty(l.LocalBoxNumber));
            var lboxA = lleft.Where(l => !string.IsNullOrEmpty(l.LocalBoxNumber));
            cabinet.UnsetPoints.Clear();
            #region 硬接点
            var orderedIOTypes = lnormal.GroupBy(t => t.IoType).OrderBy(g => GetIOTypeOrder(g.Key));
            foreach (var ioType in orderedIOTypes)
            {
                var cardGroups = ioType.GroupBy(i => i.CardType);
                foreach (var card in cardGroups)
                {
                    var powerTypeGroups = card.GroupBy(tag => GetGroupName(tag.PowerType));
                    var config = configs.FirstOrDefault(c => c.IoCardType == card.Key);
                    if (config == null) throw new Exception($"IO分配遇到问题，未在配置表中找到{card.Key}，请手动添加后再进行分配");
                    foreach (var powerTypeGroup in powerTypeGroups)
                    {
                        AllocateTagToSameTypeCard(cabinet, card.Key, powerTypeGroup.Key, [.. powerTypeGroup], config, rate);
                    }
                }
            }
            #endregion
            #region A类阀箱
            var orderedIOTypes2 = lboxA.GroupBy(t => t.IoType).OrderBy(g => GetIOTypeOrder(g.Key));
            foreach (var item in orderedIOTypes2)
            {
                var boxGroups = item.GroupBy(i => i.LocalBoxNumber);
                foreach (var box in boxGroups)
                {
                    string cardType = box.ToList().FirstOrDefault().CardType;
                    var config = configs.FirstOrDefault(c => c.IoCardType == cardType);
                    if (config == null) throw new Exception($"IO分配遇到问题，未在配置表中找到{cardType}，请手动添加后再进行分配");
                    AllocateToCardForBoxA(cabinet, cardType, box.ToList(), box.Key, config, rate);
                }
            }
            #endregion
            #region B类阀箱
            var boxes = lboxB.GroupBy(f => f.LocalBoxNumber);
            foreach (var box in boxes)
            {
                string cardType = box.ToList().FirstOrDefault().CardType;
                var config = configs.FirstOrDefault(c => c.IoCardType == cardType);
                if (config == null) throw new Exception($"IO分配遇到问题，未在配置表中找到{cardType}，请手动添加后再进行分配");
                AllocateToCard(cabinet, cardType, box.ToList(), box.Key, config, rate);
            }
            #endregion
            #region FF总线箱
            var ffStations = lff.GroupBy(f => f.LocalBoxNumber);
            List<List<Xt2Point>> xt2IoSubstations = new List<List<Xt2Point>>();
            foreach (var ffStation in ffStations)
            {
                string cardType = ffStation.ToList().FirstOrDefault().CardType;
                var config = configs.FirstOrDefault(c => c.IoCardType == cardType);
                if (config == null) throw new Exception($"IO分配遇到问题，未在配置表中找到{cardType}，请手动添加后再进行分配");
                var list = ffStation.ToList();
                AllocateToCardFF(cabinet, cardType, ffStation.ToList(), ffStation.Key, config, rate);
            }
            #endregion
            #region 最后分报警点
            if (alarmTags != null && alarmTags.Count > 0)
            {
                var groupAlarm = alarmTags.GroupBy(a => a.CardType);
                foreach (var card in groupAlarm)
                {
                    bool hasEmptySlot = cabinet.Cages.Any(cage => cage.Slots.Any(slot => slot.Board == null));
                    var firstSpareSlot = cabinet.Cages.SelectMany(cage => cage.Slots.Select(slot => slot.Board)).Where(b => b == null);
                    if (hasEmptySlot)
                    {
                        var config = configs.FirstOrDefault(c => c.IoCardType == card.Key);
                        var newCard = Xt2Board.Create(config);
                        SetBoard(cabinet, newCard);
                        foreach (var tag in card.ToList())
                        {
                            var channel = newCard.Channels.FirstOrDefault(c => c.Point == null);
                            if (channel != null) channel.Point = tag;
                            else { cabinet.UnsetPoints.Add(tag); }
                        }
                    }
                    else
                    {
                        string powerTypeGroup = GetGroupName(card.FirstOrDefault().PowerType);
                        var config = configs.FirstOrDefault(c => c.IoCardType == card.Key);
                        if (config == null) throw new Exception($"IO分配遇到问题，未在配置表中找到{card.Key}，请手动添加后再进行分配");
                        AllocateTagToSameTypeCard(cabinet, card.Key, powerTypeGroup, card.ToList(), config, rate);
                    }
                }
            }
            #endregion
            return cabinet;
        }
        public void ReassignPoints(IEnumerable<Xt2Board> boards)
        {
            if (boards == null || boards.Count() == 0) return;
            foreach (var board in boards)
            {
                var net1Points = board.Channels
                    .Where(c => c.Point != null && c.Point.NetType == Xt2NetType.Net1.ToString())                  
                    .Select(c => c.Point)
                    .ToList();
                var net2Points = board.Channels
                    .Where(c => c.Point != null && c.Point.NetType == Xt2NetType.Net2.ToString())
                    .Reverse()  
                    .Select(c => c.Point)
                    .ToList();
                var allPoints = net1Points.Concat(net2Points).ToList();
                int pointIndex = 0;
                foreach (var channel in board.Channels)
                {
                    if (pointIndex < allPoints.Count)
                    {
                        channel.Point = allPoints[pointIndex++];
                    }
                    else
                    {
                        channel.Point = null;  
                    }
                }
            }
        }
        private void AllocateTagToSameTypeCard(Xt2Cabinet xt2structure, string cardType,string powerTypeValue, List<Xt2Point> powerTypeTags, config_card_type_judge config, double rate)
        {
            foreach (var group in powerTypeTags.GroupBy(tag => tag.SignalPositionNumber))
            {
                List<Xt2Point> tags = group.ToList();
                bool isAllocated = false;
                var totalBoards = xt2structure.Cages.SelectMany(cage => cage.Slots.Select(slot => slot.Board))
                                                       .Where(board => board != null && board.Type == cardType).Union(xt2structure.UnsetBoards.Where(b => b != null && b.Type == cardType));
                foreach (var card in totalBoards)
                {
                    int availableChannels = card.Channels.Count - (int)Math.Ceiling(card.Channels.Count * rate) - card.Channels.Count(c => c.Point != null);
                    var pointsOnCard = card.Channels.Where(c => c.Point != null).Select(c => c.Point).ToList();
                    bool isSameGroup = true;
                    if (pointsOnCard.Any() && tags.Any())
                    {
                        string cardPowerType = pointsOnCard.First().PowerType;
                        string cardPower = powerSupplyGrouping.FirstOrDefault(x => x.Key == cardPowerType).Value;
                        isSameGroup = cardPower == powerTypeValue;
                    }
                    if (isSameGroup && availableChannels >= tags.Count)
                    {
                        foreach (var tag in group)
                        {
                            var channel = card.Channels.FirstOrDefault(c => c.Point == null);
                            if (channel != null) channel.Point = tag;
                        }
                        isAllocated = true;
                        break;
                    }
                }
                if (!isAllocated)
                {
                    var newCard = Xt2Board.Create(config);
                    SetBoard(xt2structure, newCard);
                    foreach (var tag in group)
                    {
                        var channel = newCard.Channels.FirstOrDefault(c => c.Point == null);
                        if (channel != null) channel.Point = tag;
                        else { PlacePointToUnset(xt2structure, tag, $"硬接点点数量超出{newCard.Channels.Count}"); }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
        private void AllocateToCardForBoxA(Xt2Cabinet xt2structure, string cardType, List<Xt2Point> stationTags, string stationNumber, config_card_type_judge config, double rate)
        {
            bool isAllocated = false;
            var totalBoards = xt2structure.Cages.SelectMany(cage => cage.Slots.Select(slot => slot.Board))
                                                    .Where(board => board != null && board.Type == cardType).Union(xt2structure.UnsetBoards.Where(b => b != null && b.Type == cardType));
            foreach (var card in totalBoards)
            {
                int availableChannels = card.Channels.Count - (int)Math.Ceiling(card.Channels.Count * rate) - card.Channels.Count(c => c.Point != null);
                var pointsOnCard = card.Channels.Where(c => c.Point != null).Select(c => c.Point).ToList();
                bool isSameGroup = true;
                if (pointsOnCard.Any() && stationTags.Any())
                {
                    string cardPowerType = pointsOnCard.First().PowerType;
                    string cardGroup = powerSupplyGrouping.FirstOrDefault(x => x.Key == cardPowerType).Value;
                    isSameGroup = stationTags.All(tag =>
                    {
                        string tagGroupKey = powerSupplyGrouping.FirstOrDefault(x => x.Key == tag.PowerType).Value;
                        return tagGroupKey == cardGroup;
                    });
                }
                if (isSameGroup && availableChannels >= stationTags.Count)
                {
                    foreach (var tag in stationTags)
                    {
                        var channel = card.Channels.FirstOrDefault(c => c.Point == null);
                        if (channel != null) channel.Point = tag;
                    }
                    isAllocated = true;
                    break; 
                }
            }
            if (!isAllocated)
            {
                var newCard = Xt2Board.Create(config);
                SetBoard(xt2structure, newCard);
                foreach (var tag in stationTags)
                {
                    var channel = newCard.Channels.FirstOrDefault(c => c.Point == null);
                    if (channel != null) channel.Point = tag;
                    else { PlacePointToUnset(xt2structure, tag, $"A类阀箱点数量超出{newCard.Channels.Count}"); }
                }
            }
        }
        private void AllocateToCard(Xt2Cabinet xt2structure, string cardType, List<Xt2Point> stationTags, string stationNumber, config_card_type_judge config, double rate)
        {
            bool isAllocated = false;
            var totalBoards = xt2structure.Cages.SelectMany(cage => cage.Slots.Select(slot => slot.Board))
                                                    .Where(board => board != null && board.Type == cardType).Union(xt2structure.UnsetBoards.Where(b => b != null && b.Type == cardType));
            foreach (var card in totalBoards)
            {
                int availableChannels = card.Channels.Count - (int)Math.Ceiling(card.Channels.Count * rate) - card.Channels.Count(c => c.Point != null);
                var pointsOnCard = card.Channels.Where(c => c.Point != null).Select(c => c.Point).ToList();
                bool isSeriesConnect = pointsOnCard.Any(p => p != null && !string.IsNullOrEmpty(p.Remarks) && (p.Remarks.Contains("串联") || p.Remarks.Contains(stationNumber)))
                    || stationTags.Any(tag => !string.IsNullOrEmpty(tag.Remarks) && (tag.Remarks.Contains("串联") || pointsOnCard.Any(p => p != null && tag.Remarks.Contains(p.StationNumber))));
                if (isSeriesConnect && availableChannels >= stationTags.Count)
                {
                    foreach (var tag in stationTags)
                    {
                        var channel = card.Channels.FirstOrDefault(c => c.Point == null);
                        if (channel != null) channel.Point = tag;                        
                    }
                    isAllocated = true;
                    break; 
                }
            }
            if (!isAllocated)
            {
                var newCard = Xt2Board.Create(config);
                SetBoard(xt2structure, newCard);
                foreach (var tag in stationTags)
                {
                    var channel = newCard.Channels.FirstOrDefault(c => c.Point == null);
                    if (channel != null) channel.Point = tag;
                    else { PlacePointToUnset(xt2structure, tag, $"B类阀箱点数量超出{newCard.Channels.Count}"); }
                }
            }
        }
        private void AllocateToCardFF(Xt2Cabinet xt2structure, string cardType, List<Xt2Point> stationTags, string stationNumber, config_card_type_judge config, double rate)
        {
            bool isAllocated = false;
            var totalBoards = xt2structure.Cages.SelectMany(cage => cage.Slots.Select(slot => slot.Board))
                                                    .Where(board => board != null && board.Type == cardType).Union(xt2structure.UnsetBoards.Where(b => b != null && b.Type == cardType));
            foreach (var card in totalBoards)
            {
                int  halfPointCount = card.Channels.Count / 2;  
                var frontChannels = card.Channels.Take(halfPointCount).ToList();
                var backChannels = card.Channels.Skip(halfPointCount).ToList();
                int availableChannels1 = frontChannels.Count - (int)Math.Ceiling(frontChannels.Count * rate) - frontChannels.Count(c => c.Point != null);
                int availableChannels2 = backChannels.Count - (int)Math.Ceiling(backChannels.Count * rate) - backChannels.Count(c => c.Point != null);
                var pointsOnCard1 = frontChannels.Where(c => c.Point != null).Select(c => c.Point).ToList();
                var pointsOnCard2 = backChannels.Where(c => c.Point != null).Select(c => c.Point).ToList();
                bool isSeriesConnectNet1 = pointsOnCard1.Any(p => p != null && p.NetType == Xt2NetType.Net1.ToString() &&
                                                   !string.IsNullOrEmpty(p.Remarks) && (p.Remarks.Contains("串联") || (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(stationNumber) && p.Remarks.Contains(stationNumber))));
                bool isSeriesConnectNet2 = pointsOnCard2.Any(p => p != null && p.NetType == Xt2NetType.Net2.ToString() &&
                                                                  !string.IsNullOrEmpty(p.Remarks) && (p.Remarks.Contains("串联") || (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(stationNumber) && p.Remarks.Contains(stationNumber))));
                if (isSeriesConnectNet1 && availableChannels1 >= stationTags.Count)
                {
                    foreach (var tag in stationTags)
                    {
                        tag.NetType = Xt2NetType.Net1.ToString();
                        var channel = frontChannels.FirstOrDefault(c => c.Point == null);
                        if (channel != null) channel.Point = tag;                     
                    }
                    isAllocated = true;break;
                }
                else if ((backChannels.All(p => p.Point == null)|| isSeriesConnectNet2 )&&
                         availableChannels2 >= stationTags.Count)
                {
                    foreach (var tag in stationTags)
                    {
                        tag.NetType = Xt2NetType.Net2.ToString();
                        var channel = backChannels.FirstOrDefault(c => c.Point == null);
                        if (channel != null) channel.Point = tag;                       
                    }
                    isAllocated = true;break;
                }
            }
            if (!isAllocated)
            {
                var newCard = Xt2Board.Create(config);
                SetBoard(xt2structure, newCard);
                foreach (var tag in stationTags)
                {
                    int halfPointCount = newCard.Channels.Count / 2;  
                    var frontChannels = newCard.Channels.Take(halfPointCount).ToList();
                    tag.NetType = Xt2NetType.Net1.ToString();
                    var channel = frontChannels.FirstOrDefault(c => c.Point == null);
                    if (channel != null) channel.Point = tag;
                    else { PlacePointToUnset(xt2structure, tag, $"网段1数量超出{halfPointCount}"); }
                }
            }            
        }
        public void ClearPointsAndAddToUnset(Xt2Cabinet cabinet)
        {
            foreach (var cage in cabinet.Cages)
            {
                foreach (var slot in cage.Slots)
                {
                    if (slot.Board != null)
                    {
                        foreach (var channel in slot.Board.Channels)
                        {
                            if (channel.Point != null)
                            {
                                cabinet.UnsetPoints.Add(channel.Point);
                                channel.Point = null;
                            }
                        }
                        slot.Board = null;
                    }
                }
            }
            foreach (var board in cabinet.UnsetBoards)
            {
                foreach (var channel in board.Channels)
                {
                    if (channel.Point != null)
                    {
                        cabinet.UnsetPoints.Add(channel.Point);
                        channel.Point = null;
                    }
                }               
            }
            cabinet.UnsetBoards.Clear();
        }
        public void PlacePointToUnset(Xt2Cabinet cabinet, Xt2Point tag,string reason)
        {
            tag.UnsetReason = reason;
            cabinet.UnsetPoints.Add(tag);
        }
        private void SetBoard(Xt2Cabinet cabinetInfo, Xt2Board board)
        {
            bool isFFType = board.Type.Contains("FF");
            for (int i = 0; i < cabinetInfo.Cages.Count; i++)
            {
                var cage = cabinetInfo.Cages[(currentCageIndex + i) % cabinetInfo.Cages.Count];
                foreach (var slot in cage.Slots)
                {
                    if (slot.Board != null) continue;
                    if (isFFType)
                    {
                        int nextSlotIndex = slot.Index + 1;
                        if (slot.Index % 2 == 1 && (cage.Slots.Count <= nextSlotIndex || cage.Slots[nextSlotIndex].Board == null))
                        {
                            slot.Board = board;
                            currentCageIndex = (currentCageIndex + i + 1) % cabinetInfo.Cages.Count; 
                            return;
                        }
                    }
                    else 
                    {
                        slot.Board = board;
                        currentCageIndex = (currentCageIndex + i + 1) % cabinetInfo.Cages.Count; 
                        return;
                    }
                }
            }
            cabinetInfo.UnsetBoards.Add(board);
        }
        private int GetIOTypeOrder(string ioType)
        {
            var order = new List<string> { "AI", "PI", "AO", "DI", "DO" };
            return order.IndexOf(ioType);
        }
        private string GetGroupName(string powerType)
        {
            if (powerSupplyGrouping.ContainsKey(powerType))
            {
                return powerSupplyGrouping[powerType];
            }
            else if (powerSupplyGrouping.Keys.Any(k => powerType.Contains(k)))
            {
                return powerSupplyGrouping[powerSupplyGrouping.Keys.FirstOrDefault(p => powerType.Contains(p))!];
            }
            return "GROUP0";
        }
        #endregion
    }
}
using System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations;
using System.Data;
using System.Linq.Expressions;
using System.Reflection;
using System.Text.RegularExpressions;
using IODataPlatform.Models.DBModels;
using IODataPlatform.Models.ExcelModels;
using Microsoft.CodeAnalysis.CSharp.Scripting;
using Expression = System.Linq.Expressions.Expression;
namespace IODataPlatform.Utilities;
public partial class FormulaBuilder {
    public string FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpression<T>(T targetTypeInstance,string classDisplayName, string fieldDisplayName, List<Formula> formulars, List<FormulaIndex> formularIndexes, List<FormulaIndexCondition> FormulaIndexConditions) where T : class
    {
        try
        {
            Type type = typeof(T);           
            var fieldIdToGet = formulars
                .Where(q => q.TargetType == classDisplayName && q.FieldName == fieldDisplayName)
                .FirstOrDefault()?.Id;
            if (fieldIdToGet == null) return "Err";
            var values = formularIndexes.Where(f => f.FormulaId == fieldIdToGet).OrderBy(x => x.Index).ToList(); 
            foreach (var value in values)
            {
                ParameterExpression paramTarget = System.Linq.Expressions.Expression.Parameter(typeof(T), "target");
                Expression finalExpression = null;
                var conditions = FormulaIndexConditions
                    .Where(f => f.IndexId == value.Id)
                    .OrderBy(c => c.Index)
                    .ToList();
                foreach (var condition in conditions)
                {
                    var propertyInfo = typeof(T).GetProperties().FirstOrDefault(a => a.Name == condition.PropertyName);
                    if (propertyInfo == null)
                    {
                        continue; 
                    }
                    var propertyValue = propertyInfo.GetValue(targetTypeInstance) ?? "";
                    ConstantExpression propertyConstantValue = Expression.Constant(propertyValue);
                    ConstantExpression constantValue = Expression.Constant(Convert.ChangeType(condition.FieldValue, propertyInfo.PropertyType), propertyInfo.PropertyType);
                    Expression conditionExpression = condition.FieldOperator switch
                    {
                        FieldOperator.等于 => Expression.Equal(propertyConstantValue, constantValue),
                        FieldOperator.不等于 => Expression.NotEqual(propertyConstantValue, constantValue),
                        FieldOperator.包含 when propertyInfo.PropertyType == typeof(string) =>
                            Expression.Call(propertyConstantValue, "Contains", null, constantValue),
                        FieldOperator.不包含 when propertyInfo.PropertyType == typeof(string) =>
                            Expression.Not(Expression.Call(propertyConstantValue, "Contains", null, constantValue)),
                        FieldOperator.起始于 when propertyInfo.PropertyType == typeof(string) =>
                            Expression.Call(propertyConstantValue, "StartsWith", null, constantValue),
                        FieldOperator.终止于 when propertyInfo.PropertyType == typeof(string) =>
                            Expression.Call(propertyConstantValue, "EndsWith", null, constantValue),
                        _ => throw new NotSupportedException($"不支持的运算符: {condition.FieldOperator}")
                    };
                    finalExpression = finalExpression == null
                        ? conditionExpression
                        : condition.ConditionOperator switch
                        {
                            ConditionOperator.并且 => Expression.AndAlso(finalExpression, conditionExpression),
                            ConditionOperator.或 => Expression.OrElse(finalExpression, conditionExpression),
                            ConditionOperator.无 => finalExpression,
                            _ => throw new NotSupportedException($"不支持的连接运算符: {condition.ConditionOperator}")
                        };
                }
                if (finalExpression != null)
                {
                    var conditionDelegate = Expression.Lambda<Func<T, bool>>(finalExpression, paramTarget).Compile();
                    if (conditionDelegate(targetTypeInstance))
                    {
                        return value.ReturnValue;
                    }
                }
            }
            return "Err";
        }
        catch (Exception ex)
        {        
            throw new Exception($"获取{fieldDisplayName}错误");
        }
    }
    public string? FindMatchingFormulaReturnValueAsyncByExpressionNew<T>(T targetTypeInstance, string classDisplayName, string fieldDisplayName, List<Formula> formulars, List<FormulaIndex> formularIndexes, List<FormulaIndexCondition> FormulaIndexConditions) where T : class
    {
        try
        {
            Type type = typeof(T);
            var fieldIdToGet = formulars.FirstOrDefault(q => q.TargetType == classDisplayName && q.FieldName == fieldDisplayName)?.Id;
            if (fieldIdToGet == null) return "Err";
            var values = formularIndexes.Where(f => f.FormulaId == fieldIdToGet).OrderBy(x => x.Index).ToList();
            foreach (FormulaIndex value in values)
            {
                if (IsConditionMatched(value.Id, targetTypeInstance, FormulaIndexConditions))
                {
                    if (value.ReturnValue.Contains("CH"))
                    {
                        var chValue = (int)type.GetProperty("Channel")?.GetValue(targetTypeInstance);
                        string replacedExpression = value.ReturnValue.Replace("CH", chValue.ToString());
                        var result = CalculateChExpression(replacedExpression, chValue);
                        return result.ToString();
                    }
                    return value.ReturnValue;
                }
            }
            return "Err";
        }
        catch (Exception ex)
        {
            throw new Exception($"获取{fieldDisplayName}错误");
        }      
    }
    public string CalculateChExpression(string expression, int channel)
    {
        if (expression.Contains("CH"))
        {
            expression = expression.Replace("CH", channel.ToString());
        }
        if (expression.Contains("+") || expression.Contains("*") || expression.Contains("-") || expression.Contains("\\"))
        {
            return CalculateExpression(expression).ToString();
        }       
        else
        {
            return expression;
        }
    }    
    private object CalculateExpression(string expressionString)
    {
         NCalc.Expression expression = new NCalc.Expression(expressionString);
        return expression.Evaluate();
    }
    private bool IsConditionMatched<T>(int indexId, T targetTypeInstance, List<FormulaIndexCondition> FormulaIndexConditions) where T : class
    {
        ParameterExpression paramTarget = Expression.Parameter(typeof(T), "target");
        Expression finalExpression = null;
        var conditions = FormulaIndexConditions.Where(f => f.IndexId == indexId).OrderBy(c => c.Index).ToList();
        foreach (var condition in conditions)
        {
            var propertyInfo = typeof(T).GetProperties().FirstOrDefault(a => a.Name == condition.PropertyName);
            if (propertyInfo == null)
            {
                continue; 
            }
            var propertyValue = propertyInfo.GetValue(targetTypeInstance) ?? "";
            ConstantExpression propertyConstantValue = Expression.Constant(propertyValue);
            ConstantExpression constantValue = Expression.Constant(Convert.ChangeType(condition.FieldValue, propertyInfo.PropertyType), propertyInfo.PropertyType);
            Expression conditionExpression = condition.FieldOperator switch
            {
                FieldOperator.等于 => Expression.Equal(propertyConstantValue, constantValue),
                FieldOperator.不等于 => Expression.NotEqual(propertyConstantValue, constantValue),
                FieldOperator.包含 when propertyInfo.PropertyType == typeof(string) => Expression.Call(propertyConstantValue, "Contains", null, constantValue),
                FieldOperator.不包含 when propertyInfo.PropertyType == typeof(string) => Expression.Not(Expression.Call(propertyConstantValue, "Contains", null, constantValue)),
                FieldOperator.起始于 when propertyInfo.PropertyType == typeof(string) => Expression.Call(propertyConstantValue, "StartsWith", null, constantValue),
                FieldOperator.终止于 when propertyInfo.PropertyType == typeof(string) => Expression.Call(propertyConstantValue, "EndsWith", null, constantValue),
                _ => throw new NotSupportedException($"Unsupported operator: {condition.FieldOperator}")
            };
            finalExpression = finalExpression == null
                ? conditionExpression
                : condition.ConditionOperator switch
                {
                    ConditionOperator.并且 => Expression.AndAlso(finalExpression, conditionExpression),
                    ConditionOperator.或 => Expression.OrElse(finalExpression, conditionExpression),
                    ConditionOperator.无 => finalExpression,
                    _ => throw new NotSupportedException($"Unsupported conjunction operator: {condition.ConditionOperator}")
                };
        }
        if (finalExpression != null)
        {
            var conditionDelegate = Expression.Lambda<Func<T, bool>>(finalExpression, paramTarget).Compile();
            return conditionDelegate(targetTypeInstance);
        }
        return false;
    }
}
namespace IODataPlatform.Utilities;
public static partial class Extensions {
    public static object To(this string text, Type type) {
        var result = type switch {
            var t when t == typeof(string) => (object)text,
            var t when t == typeof(int) => text.ToInt32(),
            var t when t == typeof(int?) => text.ToNullableInt32(),
            var t when t == typeof(float) => text.ToSingle(),
            var t when t == typeof(float?) => text.ToNullableSingle(),
            var t when t == typeof(double) => text.ToDouble(),
            var t when t == typeof(double?) => text.ToNullableDouble(),
            var t when t == typeof(DateTime) => text.ToDateTime(),
            var t when t == typeof(DateTime?) => text.ToNullableDateTime(),
            _ => throw new("不支持的类型转换"),
        };
        return result!;
    }
    public static T To<T>(this string text) {
        return (T)text.To(typeof(T));
    }
    public static int ToInt32(this string text) {
        try { return int.Parse(text); } catch { return 0; }
    }
    public static int? ToNullableInt32(this string text) {
        try { return int.Parse(text); } catch { return null; }
    }
    public static float ToSingle(this string text) {
        try { return float.Parse(text); } catch { return 0; }
    }
    public static float? ToNullableSingle(this string text) {
        try { return float.Parse(text); } catch { return null; }
    }
    public static double ToDouble(this string text) {
        try { return double.Parse(text); } catch { return 0; }
    }
    public static double? ToNullableDouble(this string text) {
        try { return double.Parse(text); } catch { return null; }
    }
    public static DateTime ToDateTime(this string text) {
        try { return DateTime.Parse(text); } catch { return default; }
    }
    public static DateTime? ToNullableDateTime(this string text) {
        try { return DateTime.Parse(text); } catch { return null; }
    }
}
using IODataPlatform.Models;
using IODataPlatform.Models.ExcelModels;
using Microsoft.CodeAnalysis.CSharp.Syntax;
using System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations;
using System.Data;
using System.Reflection;
namespace IODataPlatform.Utilities;
public static partial class Extensions {
    public static IEnumerable<T> StringTableToIEnumerableByDiplay<T>(this DataTable table) where T : new() {
        var properties = typeof(T).GetProperties()
            .Where(x => x.CanWrite)
            .Select(x => new { Property = x, DisplayName = x.GetCustomAttribute<DisplayAttribute>()?.Name ?? x.Name })
            .Where(x => table.Columns.Contains(x.DisplayName))
            .ToList();
        return table.Rows.Cast<DataRow>().Select(row => {
            var result = new T();
            foreach (var property in properties) {
                try {
                    var value = $"{row[property.DisplayName]}";
                    if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(value))
                    {
                        if (property.Property.PropertyType == typeof(int) || property.Property.PropertyType == typeof(int?))
                        {
                            property.Property.SetValue(result, 0);
                        }
                        else
                        {
                            property.Property.SetValue(result, null);
                        }
                    }
                    else if (property.Property.PropertyType == typeof(string))
                    {
                        property.Property.SetValue(result, value);
                    }
                    else if (property.Property.PropertyType == typeof(bool))
                    {
                        try { property.Property.SetValue(result, bool.Parse(value)); } catch { property.Property.SetValue(result, false); }
                    }
                    else if (property.Property.PropertyType == typeof(int))
                    {
                        try { property.Property.SetValue(result, int.Parse(value)); } catch { property.Property.SetValue(result, 0); }
                    }
                    else if (property.Property.PropertyType == typeof(int?))
                    {
                        try { property.Property.SetValue(result, int.Parse(value)); } catch { property.Property.SetValue(result, null); }
                    }
                    else if (property.Property.PropertyType == typeof(float))
                    {
                        try { property.Property.SetValue(result, float.Parse(value)); } catch { property.Property.SetValue(result, 0); }
                    }
                    else if (property.Property.PropertyType == typeof(float?))
                    {
                        try { property.Property.SetValue(result, float.Parse(value)); } catch { property.Property.SetValue(result, null); }
                    }
                    else if (property.Property.PropertyType == typeof(decimal))
                    {
                        try { property.Property.SetValue(result, decimal.Parse(value)); } catch { property.Property.SetValue(result, 0); }
                    }
                    else if (property.Property.PropertyType == typeof(decimal?))
                    {
                        try { property.Property.SetValue(result, decimal.Parse(value)); } catch { property.Property.SetValue(result, null); }
                    }
                    else if (property.Property.PropertyType == typeof(double))
                    {
                        try { property.Property.SetValue(result, double.Parse(value)); } catch { property.Property.SetValue(result, 0); }
                    }
                    else if (property.Property.PropertyType == typeof(double?))
                    {
                        try { property.Property.SetValue(result, double.Parse(value)); } catch { property.Property.SetValue(result, null); }
                    }
                    else if (property.Property.PropertyType == typeof(DateTime?))
                    {
                        try { property.Property.SetValue(result, DateTime.Parse(value)); } catch { property.Property.SetValue(result, null); }
                    }
                    else if (property.Property.PropertyType == typeof(Xt2PointType))
                    {
                        property.Property.SetValue(result, value switch
                        {
                            "Normal" => Xt2PointType.Normal,
                            "Alarm" => Xt2PointType.Alarm,
                            "BackUp" => Xt2PointType.BackUp,
                            _ => Xt2PointType.Normal,
                        });
                    }
                    else if (property.Property.PropertyType == typeof(Xt2NetType))
                    {
                        property.Property.SetValue(result, value switch
                        {
                            "Net1" => Xt2NetType.Net1,
                            "Net2" => Xt2NetType.Net2,
                            _ => Xt2NetType.Net1,
                        });
                    }
                    else if (property.Property.PropertyType == typeof(盘箱柜类别))
                    {
                        property.Property.SetValue(result, value switch
                        {
                            "盘台" => 盘箱柜类别.盘台,
                            "阀箱" => 盘箱柜类别.阀箱,
                            "机柜" => 盘箱柜类别.机柜,
                            _ => throw new NotImplementedException(),
                        });
                    }
                    else
                    {
                        throw new NotImplementedException();
                    }
                } catch (NotImplementedException ex) {
                    throw new("开发人员注意：需要匹配更多类型");
                }
                catch (Exception ex)
                {
                }
            }
            return result;
        });
    }
    public static async Task<DataTable> ToTableByDisplayAttributeAsync<T>(this IEnumerable<T> data) {
        return await Task.Run(() => {
            var dataTable = new DataTable();
            var props = typeof(T).GetProperties().ToList();
            var mappingDic = props.ToDictionary(x => x.Name, x => x.GetCustomAttribute<DisplayAttribute>()?.Name ?? x.Name);
            props.ForEach(x => dataTable.Columns.Add(mappingDic[x.Name]));
            data.ToList().ForEach(x => {
                var row = dataTable.NewRow();
                props.ForEach(prop => row[mappingDic[prop.Name]] = prop.GetValue(x));
                dataTable.Rows.Add(row);
            });
            return dataTable;
        });
    }
    public static async Task<DataTable> ToTableByDisplayAttributeAsync<T>() {
        return await Enumerable.Empty<T>().ToTableByDisplayAttributeAsync();
    }
    public static async Task<DataTable> ToTableByPropertyNameAsync<T>(this IEnumerable<T> data) {
        return await Task.Run(() => {
            var dataTable = new DataTable();
            var props = typeof(T).GetProperties().ToList();
            props.ForEach(x => dataTable.Columns.Add(x.Name));
            data.ToList().ForEach(x => {
                var row = dataTable.NewRow();
                props.ForEach(prop => row[prop.Name] = prop.GetValue(x));
                dataTable.Rows.Add(row);
            });
            return dataTable;
        });
    }
    public static async Task<DataTable> ToTableByPropertyNameAsync<T>() {
        return await Enumerable.Empty<T>().ToTableByPropertyNameAsync();
    }
}
using System;
using System.Collections.Generic;
using System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations;
using System.Linq;
using System.Reflection;
using System.Text;
using System.Threading.Tasks;
namespace IODataPlatform.Utilities
{
    public class DisplayInfo
    {
        public string ClassName { get; set; }
        public Dictionary<string, string> FieldDisplayNames { get; set; }
    }
    public static class DisplayAttributeHelper
    {
        public static DisplayInfo GetDisplayInfo<T>()
        {
            Type type = typeof(T);
            DisplayInfo displayInfo = new DisplayInfo();
            displayInfo.FieldDisplayNames = new Dictionary<string, string>();
            DisplayAttribute classDisplayAttribute = type.GetCustomAttribute<DisplayAttribute>();
            displayInfo.ClassName = classDisplayAttribute?.Name ?? type.Name;
            foreach (PropertyInfo property in type.GetProperties())
            {
                DisplayAttribute displayAttribute = property.GetCustomAttribute<DisplayAttribute>();
                if (displayAttribute != null)
                {
                    displayInfo.FieldDisplayNames.Add(property.Name, displayAttribute.Name);
                }
            }
            return displayInfo;
        }
    }
}

    public static int ToInt(this string number)
    {
        _ = int.TryParse(number, out int pin);
        return pin;
    }

    public static CableData MatchCableData(TerminationData data1, TerminationData data2) {
        return new();
    }
    public static async Task<MatchCableDataResult> MatchCableData(SqlSugarContext context, IEnumerable<TerminationData> duanjieList1, IEnumerable<TerminationData> duanjieList2, string major1, string major2)
    {
        var systemNumberDtos = context.Db.Queryable<config_cable_systemNumber>().ToList();
        var cableFunctionDtos = context.Db.Queryable<config_cable_function>().ToList();
        var cableCategoryAndColorDtos = context.Db.Queryable<config_cable_categoryAndColor>().ToList();
        MatchCableDataResult result = new MatchCableDataResult();
        result.SuccessList = new List<CableData>();
        var l1 = duanjieList1.Where(d => d.MajorDest == major2).ToList();
        var l2 = duanjieList2.Where(d => d.MajorDest == major1).ToList();
        foreach (var d1 in l1)
        {
            foreach (var d2 in l2)
            {
                if (d1.IOPointName.Contains(d2.IOPointName) || d2.IOPointName.Contains(d1.IOPointName))
                {
                    string FindSystemNo(string firstSystem, string secondSystem)
                    {
                        return systemNumberDtos.FirstOrDefault(t =>
                            t.FirstSystem == firstSystem && t.SecondSystem == secondSystem)?.CableSystem ?? "";
                    }
                    string DetermineIOType(string firstIOType, string secondIOType)
                    {
                        var match = cableFunctionDtos.FirstOrDefault(c =>
                            c.FirstIOType == firstIOType && c.SecondIOType == secondIOType);
                        return match == null ? firstIOType : match.CableIOType;
                    }
                    config_cable_categoryAndColor CheckSafetyMatch(string firstSafetyGroup, string secondSafetyGroup)
                    {
                        return cableCategoryAndColorDtos.FirstOrDefault(t =>
                            t.FirstSafetyGroup == firstSafetyGroup && t.SecondSafetyGroup == secondSafetyGroup);
                    }
                    string firstSystem = "";
                    string secondSystem = "";
                    if (d1.CabinetNumber != null && d1.CabinetNumber.Length > 4)
                        firstSystem = d1.CabinetNumber.Substring(2, 3);
                    if (d2.CabinetNumber != null && d2.CabinetNumber.Length > 4)
                        secondSystem = d2.CabinetNumber.Substring(2, 3);
                    string systemNo = FindSystemNo(firstSystem, secondSystem);
                    string iotype = DetermineIOType(d1.IOType, d2.IOType);
                    var safetyMatched = CheckSafetyMatch(
                        d1.SafetyClassification_Grouping?.Replace("/", " "),
                        d2.SafetyClassification_Grouping?.Replace("/", " ")
                    );                  
                    result.SuccessList.Add(new CableData
                    {
                        线缆编号 = d1.UnitNumber + systemNo + iotype + "0001",
                        IO类型 = iotype??"DI",
                        线缆列别 = safetyMatched == null ? "" : safetyMatched.CableCategory,
                        色标 = safetyMatched == null ? "" : safetyMatched.Color,
                        起点信号位号 = d1.IOPointName,
                        起点房间号 = d1.RoomNumber,                        
                        起点盘柜名称 = d1.CabinetNumber,
                        起点设备名称 = d1.TerminalBoardNumber,
                        起点接线点1 = d1.ConnectionPoint1,
                        起点接线点2 = d1.ConnectionPoint2,
                        起点接线点3 = d1.ConnectionPoint3,
                        起点接线点4 = d1.ConnectionPoint4,
                        供货方 = "CNCS",
                        终点信号位号 = d2.IOPointName,
                        终点房间号 = d2.RoomNumber,
                        终点盘柜名称 = d2.CabinetNumber,
                        终点设备名称 = d2.TerminalBoardNumber,
                        终点接线点1 = d2.ConnectionPoint1,
                        终点接线点2 = d2.ConnectionPoint2,
                        终点接线点3 = d2.ConnectionPoint3,
                        终点接线点4 = d2.ConnectionPoint4,
                        SystemNo=systemNo,
                    });                                                         
                    d1.IsMatched = true;
                    d2.IsMatched = true;
                }
            }
        }
        result.FailList1 = new List<MatchCableDataFail>();
        result.FailList2 = new List<MatchCableDataFail>();
        foreach (var item in l1.Where(l => !l.IsMatched))
        {
            MatchCableDataFail match = new MatchCableDataFail { Data = item, Reason = "找不到IO点" };
            result.FailList1.Add(match);
        }
        foreach (var item in l2.Where(l => !l.IsMatched))
        {
            MatchCableDataFail match = new MatchCableDataFail { Data = item, Reason = "找不到IO点" };
            result.FailList2.Add(match);
        }
        return result;
    }
    public static async Task<Tuple<TerminationData, TerminationData>> UnMatchCableData(CableData cableData)
    {
        TerminationData t1 = new TerminationData
        {
            IOPointName = cableData.起点信号位号,
            RoomNumber = cableData.起点房间号,
            CabinetNumber = cableData.起点盘柜名称,
            TerminalBoardModel = cableData.起点设备名称,
            ConnectionPoint1 = cableData.起点接线点1,
            ConnectionPoint2 = cableData.起点接线点2,
            ConnectionPoint3 = cableData.起点接线点3,
            ConnectionPoint4 = cableData.起点接线点4,
            MajorDest = cableData.终点信号位号 
        };
        TerminationData t2 = new TerminationData
        {
            IOPointName = cableData.终点信号位号,
            RoomNumber = cableData.终点房间号,
            CabinetNumber = cableData.终点盘柜名称,
            TerminalBoardModel = cableData.终点设备名称,
            ConnectionPoint1 = cableData.终点接线点1,
            ConnectionPoint2 = cableData.终点接线点2,
            ConnectionPoint3 = cableData.终点接线点3,
            ConnectionPoint4 = cableData.终点接线点4,
            MajorDest = cableData.起点信号位号 
        };
        return Tuple.Create(t1, t2);
    }
    public static async Task<List<CableData>> MatchCableData(this SqlSugarContext context, IEnumerable<TerminationData> duanjieList1, IEnumerable<TerminationData> duanjieList2) {
        var systemNumberDtos = context.Db.Queryable<config_cable_systemNumber>().ToList();
        var cableFunctionDtos = context.Db.Queryable<config_cable_function>().ToList();
        var cableCategoryAndColorDtos = context.Db.Queryable<config_cable_categoryAndColor>().ToList();
        List<CableData> processedCables = new List<CableData>();
        var index = 0;
        foreach (var item in duanjieList1) {
            index++;
            var cable = new CableData();
            processedCables.Add(cable);
            cable.序号 = index.ToString();
            cable.起点房间号 = item.RoomNumber;
            cable.起点盘柜名称 = item.CabinetNumber;
            cable.起点设备名称 = item.TerminalBoardModel;
            cable.起点接线点1 = item.ConnectionPoint1;
            cable.起点接线点2 = item.ConnectionPoint2;
            cable.起点接线点3 = item.ConnectionPoint3;
            cable.起点接线点4 = item.ConnectionPoint4;
            cable.起点信号位号 = item.IOPointName;
            cable.供货方 = "CNCS";
            if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(item.OriginalVariableName)) {
                cable.匹配情况 = "【单独点】原变量名为空";
                continue;
            }
            var sameOnes1 = duanjieList2.Where(f => f.OriginalVariableName == item.OriginalVariableName && f.OriginalExtensionCode == item.OriginalExtensionCode).ToList();
            if (sameOnes1 != null && sameOnes1.Count == 1) {
                string systemNo = systemNumberDtos.FirstOrDefault(t => t.FirstSystem == item.CabinetNumber.Substring(1, 3) && t.SecondSystem == sameOnes1[0].CabinetNumber.Substring(1, 3)) == null ? "" : systemNumberDtos.FirstOrDefault(t => t.FirstSystem == item.CabinetNumber.Substring(1, 3) && t.SecondSystem == sameOnes1[0].CabinetNumber.Substring(1, 3)).CableSystem;
                string iotype = cableFunctionDtos.FirstOrDefault(c => c.FirstIOType == item.IOType && c.SecondIOType == sameOnes1[0].IOType) == null ? item.IOType : cableFunctionDtos.FirstOrDefault(c => c.FirstIOType == item.IOType && c.SecondIOType == sameOnes1[0].IOType).CableIOType;
                var safetyMatched = cableCategoryAndColorDtos.FirstOrDefault(t => t.FirstSafetyGroup == item.SafetyClassification_Grouping.Replace("/", " ") && t.SecondSafetyGroup == sameOnes1[0].IOType.Replace("/", " "));
                cable.线缆编号 = item.UnitNumber + systemNo + iotype + "0001";
                cable.IO类型 = iotype;
                cable.线缆列别 = safetyMatched == null ? "" : safetyMatched.CableCategory;
                cable.色标 = safetyMatched == null ? "" : safetyMatched.Color;
                cable.终点房间号 = sameOnes1[0].RoomNumber;
                cable.终点盘柜名称 = sameOnes1[0].CabinetNumber;
                cable.终点设备名称 = sameOnes1[0].TerminalBoardModel;
                cable.终点接线点1 = sameOnes1[0].ConnectionPoint1;
                cable.终点接线点2 = sameOnes1[0].ConnectionPoint2;
                cable.终点接线点3 = sameOnes1[0].ConnectionPoint3;
                cable.终点接线点4 = sameOnes1[0].ConnectionPoint4;
                cable.终点信号位号 = sameOnes1[0].IOPointName;
                cable.SystemNo = systemNo;
                cable.匹配情况 = "【成对点】匹配成功！";
                sameOnes1[0].IsMatched = true;
            }
            else if (sameOnes1 != null && sameOnes1.Count > 1) {
                cable.匹配情况 = $"【人工处理点】原变量名+原扩展码  匹配到{sameOnes1.Count}个元素";
                sameOnes1.ForEach(s => s.IsMatched = false);
            } else {
                var sameOnes2 = duanjieList2.Where(f => f.OriginalVariableName == item.OriginalVariableName && f.SignalDescription == item.SignalDescription).ToList();
                if (sameOnes2.Count > 0) {
                    cable.匹配情况 = $"【疑似成对点】匹配到{sameOnes2.Count}个疑似点！";
                    sameOnes2.ForEach(s => s.IsMatched = false);
                } else {
                    cable.匹配情况 = $"【无法匹配】";
                    sameOnes2.ForEach(s => s.IsMatched = false);
                }
            }
        }
        foreach (var item in duanjieList2.Where(d => d.IsMatched == false)) {
            index++;
            var checkDto = new CableData();
            processedCables.Add(checkDto);
            checkDto.序号 = index.ToString();
            checkDto.终点房间号 = item.RoomNumber;
            checkDto.终点盘柜名称 = item.CabinetNumber;
            checkDto.终点设备名称 = item.TerminalBoardModel;
            checkDto.终点接线点1 = item.ConnectionPoint1;
            checkDto.终点接线点2 = item.ConnectionPoint2;
            checkDto.终点接线点3 = item.ConnectionPoint3;
            checkDto.终点接线点4 = item.ConnectionPoint4;
            checkDto.终点信号位号 = item.IOPointName;
            checkDto.供货方 = "CNCS";
            if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(item.OriginalVariableName)) {
                checkDto.匹配情况 = "【单独点】原变量名为空";
                continue;
            }
            var sameOnes1 = duanjieList1.Where(f => f.OriginalVariableName == item.OriginalVariableName && f.OriginalExtensionCode == item.OriginalExtensionCode).ToList();
            if (sameOnes1 != null && sameOnes1.Count == 1) {
                string systemNo = systemNumberDtos.FirstOrDefault(t => t.FirstSystem == item.CabinetNumber && t.SecondSystem == sameOnes1[0].CabinetNumber) == null ? "" : systemNumberDtos.FirstOrDefault(t => t.FirstSystem == item.CabinetNumber && t.SecondSystem == sameOnes1[0].CabinetNumber).SecondSystem;
                string iotype = cableFunctionDtos.FirstOrDefault(c => c.FirstIOType == item.IOType && c.SecondIOType == sameOnes1[0].IOType) == null ? item.IOType : cableFunctionDtos.FirstOrDefault(c => c.FirstIOType == item.IOType && c.SecondIOType == sameOnes1[0].IOType).CableIOType;
                var safetyMatched = cableCategoryAndColorDtos.FirstOrDefault(t => t.FirstSafetyGroup == item.SafetyClassification_Grouping.Replace("/", " ") && t.SecondSafetyGroup == sameOnes1[0].SafetyClassification_Grouping.Replace("/", " "));
                checkDto.线缆编号 = item.UnitNumber + systemNo + iotype + "0001";
                checkDto.IO类型 = iotype;
                checkDto.线缆列别 = safetyMatched == null ? "" : safetyMatched.CableCategory;
                checkDto.色标 = safetyMatched == null ? "" : safetyMatched.Color;
                checkDto.起点房间号 = sameOnes1[0].RoomNumber;
                checkDto.起点盘柜名称 = sameOnes1[0].CabinetNumber;
                checkDto.起点设备名称 = sameOnes1[0].TerminalBoardModel;
                checkDto.起点接线点1 = sameOnes1[0].ConnectionPoint1;
                checkDto.起点接线点2 = sameOnes1[0].ConnectionPoint2;
                checkDto.起点接线点3 = sameOnes1[0].ConnectionPoint3;
                checkDto.起点接线点4 = sameOnes1[0].ConnectionPoint4;
                checkDto.起点信号位号 = sameOnes1[0].IOPointName;
                checkDto.SystemNo = systemNo;
                checkDto.匹配情况 = "匹配成功！";
                sameOnes1[0].IsMatched = true;
            } else if (sameOnes1 != null && sameOnes1.Count > 1) {
                checkDto.匹配情况 = $"【人工处理点】原变量名+原扩展码  匹配到{sameOnes1.Count}个元素";
                sameOnes1.ForEach(s => s.IsMatched = false);
            } else {
                var sameOnes2 = duanjieList1.Where(f => f.OriginalVariableName == item.OriginalVariableName && f.SignalDescription == item.SignalDescription).ToList();
                if (sameOnes2.Count > 0) {
                    checkDto.匹配情况 = $"【疑似成对点】匹配到{sameOnes2.Count}个疑似点！";
                    sameOnes2.ForEach(s => s.IsMatched = false);
                } else {
                    checkDto.匹配情况 = $"【人工处理点】无法匹配";
                    sameOnes2.ForEach(s => s.IsMatched = false);
                }
            }
        }
        var unmatched = processedCables.Where(r => r.IO类型 == null).ToList();
        var matched = await NumberMatchCable(processedCables.Where(r => r.IO类型 != null).ToList(), context);
        var final = unmatched.Union(matched).ToList();
        return final;
    }
    public static async Task<List<CableData>> NumberMatchCable(List<CableData> excelData, SqlSugarContext context) {
        var processedCables = new List<CableData>();
        var cableStartNumbers = await context.Db.Queryable<config_cable_startNumber>().ToListAsync();
        var cableSpecifications = await context.Db.Queryable<config_cable_spec>().ToListAsync();
        var ioTypeGroups = excelData.GroupBy(r => r.IO类型[..1]);
        foreach (var signalList in ioTypeGroups)
        {
            try {
                var isControlCable = signalList.Key.Contains('D'); 
                int maxSignalSupport = GetMaxSignalSupport(isControlCable, cableSpecifications); 
                var equipmentGroups = signalList.GroupBy(s => s.起点设备名称); 
                foreach (var equipmentList in equipmentGroups)
                {
                    var equipmentName = equipmentList.Key; 
                    var terminalCabinetGroups = equipmentList.GroupBy(e => e.终点盘柜名称); 
                    foreach (var terminalCabinetGroup in terminalCabinetGroups) {
                        var allSignalsInGroup = terminalCabinetGroup.OrderByDescending(s => terminalCabinetGroup.Count(l => l.起点信号位号.Split('_')[0] == s.起点信号位号.Split('_')[0])).ToList();
                        var (cableCount, cableLeft) = GetCableCountUsed(allSignalsInGroup, maxSignalSupport);
                        int totalUsedRow = 0;
                        for (int i = 0; i < cableCount; i++) {
                            int rowCount = GetSkipRowCount(allSignalsInGroup, maxSignalSupport, i);
                            int rowTakeCount = GetTakeRowCount(allSignalsInGroup, maxSignalSupport, i, rowCount);
                            totalUsedRow += rowTakeCount;
                            var li = allSignalsInGroup.Skip(rowCount).Take(rowTakeCount).ToList();
                            var sameNumber = cableStartNumbers.FirstOrDefault(s => s.StartCabinetNo == li.FirstOrDefault().起点盘柜名称.Substring(4, 3) && s.Sequence == li.FirstOrDefault().线缆列别)?.StartNumber;
                            var sameXulies = cableStartNumbers.Where(s => s.StartCabinetNo == li.FirstOrDefault().起点盘柜名称.Substring(4, 3) && s.StartNumber == sameNumber).Select(s => s.Sequence).ToList();
                            var find1 = processedCables.Where(r => r.起点盘柜名称 == li.FirstOrDefault().起点盘柜名称.Substring(4, 3) && sameXulies.Contains(r.线缆列别) && r.IO类型.Substring(0, 1) == li.FirstOrDefault().IO类型.Substring(0, 1)).ToList();
                            var currentStartNumber1 = 0;
                            if (find1 == null || find1.Count == 0) {
                                var a = cableStartNumbers.FirstOrDefault(s => s.StartCabinetNo == li.FirstOrDefault().起点盘柜名称.Substring(4, 3) && s.Sequence == li.FirstOrDefault().线缆列别); ;
                                if (a != null) {
                                    currentStartNumber1 = a.StartNumber;
                                }
                            } else {
                                currentStartNumber1 = find1.Max(f => f.StartNumber) + 1;
                            }
                            for (int j = 0; j < li.Count; j++) {
                                CableData cableDataTemp = new CableData();
                                cableDataTemp.起点盘柜名称 = li[j].起点盘柜名称.Substring(4, 3);
                                cableDataTemp.StartNumber = currentStartNumber1;
                                cableDataTemp.线缆编号 = isControlCable ? cableDataTemp.SystemNo + "C" + currentStartNumber1 : cableDataTemp.SystemNo + "M" + currentStartNumber1;
                                cableDataTemp.线缆列别 = li[j].线缆列别;
                                cableDataTemp.色标 = li[j].色标;
                                cableDataTemp.特性代码 = isControlCable ? cableSpecifications.Where(c => c.CableType == "控制电缆").MaxBy(c => c.SignalCount).FeatureCode : cableSpecifications.Where(c => c.CableType == "测量电缆").MaxBy(c => c.SignalCount).FeatureCode;
                                int startDuiShuNum = 0;
                                var sameGroupfind = processedCables.Where(r => r.IO类型.Substring(0, 1) == li[j].IO类型.Substring(0, 1) && r.起点设备名称 == li[j].起点设备名称 && r.终点盘柜名称 == li[j].终点盘柜名称);
                                if (sameGroupfind == null || sameGroupfind.Count() == 0) {
                                    startDuiShuNum = 1;
                                    if (isControlCable) {
                                        cableDataTemp.芯线号 = li[j].起点接线点1 == @"/" || li[j].起点接线点2 == @"/" ? $"{startDuiShuNum}" : $"{startDuiShuNum}&{startDuiShuNum + 1}";
                                    } else {
                                        cableDataTemp.芯线号 = "1";
                                    }
                                } else {
                                    var list = sameGroupfind.Select(s => s.芯线号.Contains("&") ? s.芯线号.Split('&').Last() : s.芯线号).ToList();
                                    if (isControlCable) {
                                        if (list.Select(s => int.Parse(s)).Last() == cableSpecifications.Where(c => c.CableType == "控制电缆").Max(c => c.SignalCount)) {
                                            startDuiShuNum = 1;
                                        } else if (list.Select(s => int.Parse(s)).Last() == cableSpecifications.Where(c => c.CableType == "控制电缆").Max(c => c.SignalCount) - 1 && !(li[j].起点接线点1 == @"/" || li[j].起点接线点2 == @"/")) {
                                            startDuiShuNum = 1;
                                        } else {
                                            startDuiShuNum = list.Select(s => int.Parse(s)).Last() + 1;
                                        }
                                        cableDataTemp.芯线号 = li[j].起点接线点1 == @"/" || li[j].起点接线点2 == @"/" ? $"{startDuiShuNum}" : $"{startDuiShuNum}&{startDuiShuNum + 1}";
                                    } else {
                                        if (2 * j == cableSpecifications.Where(c => c.CableType == "测量电缆").Max(c => c.SignalCount)) {
                                            cableDataTemp.芯线号 = "1";
                                        } else {
                                            cableDataTemp.芯线号 = (j + 1).ToString();
                                        }
                                    }
                                }
                                cableDataTemp.芯线号 = li[j].起点接线点1 == @"/" || li[j].起点接线点2 == @"/" ? $"{startDuiShuNum}" : $"{startDuiShuNum}&{startDuiShuNum + 1}";
                                if (isControlCable == false) {
                                    cableDataTemp.芯线号 = (j + 1).ToString();
                                }
                                cableDataTemp.芯线对数号 = isControlCable ? "" : "R&IY";
                                cableDataTemp.IO类型 = li[j].IO类型;
                                cableDataTemp.起点房间号 = li[j].起点房间号;
                                cableDataTemp.起点盘柜名称 = li[j].起点盘柜名称;
                                cableDataTemp.起点设备名称 = li[j].起点设备名称;
                                cableDataTemp.起点接线点1 = li[j].起点接线点1;
                                cableDataTemp.起点接线点2 = li[j].起点接线点2;
                                cableDataTemp.起点屏蔽端 = li[j].起点屏蔽端;
                                cableDataTemp.起点信号位号 = li[j].起点信号位号;
                                cableDataTemp.电缆长度 = li[j].电缆长度;
                                cableDataTemp.终点房间号 = li[j].终点房间号;
                                cableDataTemp.终点盘柜名称 = li[j].终点盘柜名称;
                                cableDataTemp.终点设备名称 = li[j].终点设备名称;
                                cableDataTemp.终点接线点1 = li[j].终点接线点1;
                                cableDataTemp.终点接线点2 = li[j].终点接线点2;
                                cableDataTemp.终点屏蔽端 = li[j].终点屏蔽端;
                                cableDataTemp.终点信号位号 = li[j].终点信号位号;
                                cableDataTemp.供货方 = li[j].供货方;
                                cableDataTemp.版本 = li[j].版本;
                                cableDataTemp.备注 = li[j].备注;
                                processedCables.Add(cableDataTemp);
                            }
                        }
                        int leftNum = 0;
                        for (int i = 0; i < allSignalsInGroup.Skip(totalUsedRow).ToList().Count; i++) {
                            leftNum += allSignalsInGroup.Skip(totalUsedRow).ToList()[i].起点接线点1 != @"/" ? 1 : 0;
                            leftNum += allSignalsInGroup.Skip(totalUsedRow).ToList()[i].起点接线点2 != @"/" ? 1 : 0;
                        }
                        var ListLeft = cableCount > 0 ? allSignalsInGroup.Skip(totalUsedRow).ToList() : allSignalsInGroup;
                        if (ListLeft == null || ListLeft.Count == 0) {
                            continue;
                        }
                        var sameNumber1 = cableStartNumbers.FirstOrDefault(s => s.StartCabinetNo == ListLeft.FirstOrDefault().起点盘柜名称.Substring(4, 3) && s.Sequence == ListLeft.FirstOrDefault().线缆列别)?.StartNumber;
                        var sameXulies1 = cableStartNumbers.Where(s => s.StartCabinetNo == ListLeft.FirstOrDefault().起点盘柜名称.Substring(4, 3) && s.StartNumber == sameNumber1).Select(s => s.Sequence).ToList();
                        var find2 = processedCables.Where(r => r.起点盘柜名称 == ListLeft.FirstOrDefault().起点盘柜名称.Substring(4, 3) && sameXulies1.Contains(r.线缆列别) && r.IO类型.Substring(0, 1) == ListLeft.FirstOrDefault().IO类型.Substring(0, 1)).ToList();
                        var currentStartNumber = 0;
                        if (find2 == null || find2.Count == 0) {
                            var a = cableStartNumbers.FirstOrDefault(s => s.StartCabinetNo == ListLeft.FirstOrDefault().起点盘柜名称.Substring(4, 3) && s.Sequence == ListLeft.FirstOrDefault().线缆列别); 
                            if (a != null) {
                                currentStartNumber = a.StartNumber;
                            }
                        } else {
                            currentStartNumber = find2.Max(f => f.StartNumber) + 1;
                        }
                        for (int n = 0; n < ListLeft.Count; n++) {
                            CableData cableDataTempLeft = new CableData();
                            cableDataTempLeft.起点盘柜名称 = ListLeft[n].起点盘柜名称.Substring(4, 3);
                            cableDataTempLeft.StartNumber = currentStartNumber;
                            cableDataTempLeft.线缆编号 = isControlCable ? cableDataTempLeft.SystemNo + "C" + currentStartNumber : cableDataTempLeft.SystemNo + "M" + currentStartNumber;
                            cableDataTempLeft.线缆列别 = ListLeft[n].线缆列别;
                            cableDataTempLeft.色标 = ListLeft[n].色标;
                            if (isControlCable) {
                                cableDataTempLeft.特性代码 = cableSpecifications.FirstOrDefault(c => c.CableType == "控制电缆" && leftNum == c.SignalCount)?.FeatureCode;
                            } else {
                                cableDataTempLeft.特性代码 = cableSpecifications.FirstOrDefault(c => c.CableType == "测量电缆" && 2 * ListLeft.Count == c.SignalCount)?.FeatureCode;
                            }
                            int startDuiShuNum = 0;
                            var sameGroupfind = processedCables.Where(r => r.IO类型.Substring(0, 1) == ListLeft[n].IO类型.Substring(0, 1) && r.起点设备名称 == ListLeft[n].起点设备名称 && r.终点盘柜名称 == ListLeft[n].终点盘柜名称).ToList();
                            if (sameGroupfind == null || sameGroupfind.Count() == 0) {
                                startDuiShuNum = 1;
                                if (isControlCable) {
                                    cableDataTempLeft.芯线号 = ListLeft[n].起点接线点1 == @"/" || ListLeft[n].起点接线点2 == @"/" ? $"{startDuiShuNum}" : $"{startDuiShuNum}&{startDuiShuNum + 1}";
                                } else {
                                    cableDataTempLeft.芯线号 = "1";
                                }
                            } else {
                                var list = sameGroupfind.Select(s => s.芯线号.Contains("&") ? s.芯线号.Split('&').Last() : s.芯线号).ToList();
                                if (isControlCable) {
                                    if (list.Select(s => int.Parse(s)).Last() == cableSpecifications.Where(c => c.CableType == "控制电缆").Max(c => c.SignalCount) || list.Select(s => int.Parse(s)).Last() == cableSpecifications.Where(c => c.CableType == "控制电缆").Max(c => c.SignalCount) - 1) {
                                        startDuiShuNum = 1;
                                    } else {
                                        startDuiShuNum = list.Select(s => int.Parse(s)).Last() + 1;
                                    }
                                    cableDataTempLeft.芯线号 = ListLeft[n].起点接线点1 == @"/" || ListLeft[n].起点接线点2 == @"/" ? $"{startDuiShuNum}" : $"{startDuiShuNum}&{startDuiShuNum + 1}";
                                } else {
                                    if (2 * n == cableSpecifications.Where(c => c.CableType == "测量电缆").Max(c => c.SignalCount)) {
                                        cableDataTempLeft.芯线号 = "1";
                                    } else {
                                        cableDataTempLeft.芯线号 = (n + 1).ToString();
                                    }
                                }
                            }
                            cableDataTempLeft.芯线对数号 = isControlCable ? "" : "R&IY";
                            cableDataTempLeft.IO类型 = ListLeft[n].IO类型;
                            cableDataTempLeft.起点房间号 = ListLeft[n].起点房间号;
                            cableDataTempLeft.起点盘柜名称 = ListLeft[n].起点盘柜名称;
                            cableDataTempLeft.起点设备名称 = ListLeft[n].起点设备名称;
                            cableDataTempLeft.起点接线点1 = ListLeft[n].起点接线点1;
                            cableDataTempLeft.起点接线点2 = ListLeft[n].起点接线点2;
                            cableDataTempLeft.起点屏蔽端 = ListLeft[n].起点屏蔽端;
                            cableDataTempLeft.起点信号位号 = ListLeft[n].起点信号位号;
                            cableDataTempLeft.电缆长度 = ListLeft[n].电缆长度;
                            cableDataTempLeft.终点房间号 = ListLeft[n].终点房间号;
                            cableDataTempLeft.终点盘柜名称 = ListLeft[n].终点盘柜名称;
                            cableDataTempLeft.终点设备名称 = ListLeft[n].终点设备名称;
                            cableDataTempLeft.终点接线点1 = ListLeft[n].终点接线点1;
                            cableDataTempLeft.终点接线点2 = ListLeft[n].终点接线点2;
                            cableDataTempLeft.终点屏蔽端 = ListLeft[n].终点屏蔽端;
                            cableDataTempLeft.终点信号位号 = ListLeft[n].终点信号位号;
                            cableDataTempLeft.供货方 = ListLeft[n].供货方;
                            cableDataTempLeft.版本 = ListLeft[n].版本;
                            cableDataTempLeft.备注 = ListLeft[n].备注;
                            processedCables.Add(cableDataTempLeft);
                        }
                    }
                }
            } catch (Exception ex) {
            }
        }
        SwapCablePropertiesForTypeA(processedCables);
        AssignSerialNumbers(processedCables);
        #region 核查
        #endregion
        return processedCables;
    }
    private static int GetMaxSignalSupport(bool DorA, List<config_cable_spec> cableSpecifications) {
        return DorA
            ? cableSpecifications.Where(c => c.CableType == "控制电缆").Max(c => c.SignalCount)
            : cableSpecifications.Where(c => c.CableType == "测量电缆").Max(c => c.SignalCount);
    }
    private static void AssignSerialNumbers(List<CableData> cables) {
        for (int i = 0; i < cables.Count; i++) {
            cables[i].序号 = (i + 1).ToString();
        }
    }
    private static void SwapCablePropertiesForTypeA(List<CableData> cables) {
        foreach (var item in cables.Where(r => r.IO类型.StartsWith("A"))) {
            (item.芯线号, item.芯线对数号) = (item.芯线对数号, item.芯线号);
        }
    }
    public static Tuple<int, int> GetCableCountUsed(List<CableData> allSignals, int maxSignalSupport) {
        int needCableCount = 0;
        int tempNum = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < allSignals.Count; i++) {
            if (tempNum == maxSignalSupport) {
                needCableCount += 1;
                tempNum = 0;
            }
            if (tempNum > maxSignalSupport) {
                needCableCount += 1;
                if (i > 0) {
                    tempNum = 0;
                    tempNum += allSignals[i - 1].起点接线点1 != @"/" ? 1 : 0;
                    tempNum += allSignals[i - 1].起点接线点2 != @"/" ? 1 : 0;
                }
            }
            tempNum += allSignals[i].起点接线点1 != @"/" ? 1 : 0;
            tempNum += allSignals[i].起点接线点2 != @"/" ? 1 : 0;
        }
        return new Tuple<int, int>(needCableCount, tempNum);
    }
    public static int GetSkipRowCount(List<CableData> allSignals, int maxSignalSupport, int i) {
        int skipNum = 0;
        int rowCount = 0;
        for (int c = 0; c < allSignals.Count; c++) {
            if (skipNum == maxSignalSupport * i) {
                break;
            }
            if (skipNum > maxSignalSupport * i) {
                rowCount -= 1;
                break;
            }
            skipNum += allSignals[c].起点接线点1 != @"/" ? 1 : 0;
            skipNum += allSignals[c].起点接线点2 != @"/" ? 1 : 0;
            rowCount += 1;
        }
        return rowCount;
    }
    public static int GetTakeRowCount(List<CableData> allSignals, int maxSignalSupport, int i, int rowCount) {
        int skipNum1 = 0;
        int rowTakeCount = 0;
        for (int c = 0; c < allSignals.Skip(rowCount).ToList().Count; c++) {
            if (skipNum1 == maxSignalSupport) {
                break;
            }
            if (skipNum1 > maxSignalSupport) {
                rowTakeCount -= 1;
                break;
            }
            skipNum1 += allSignals.Skip(rowCount).ToList()[c].起点接线点1 != @"/" ? 1 : 0;
            skipNum1 += allSignals.Skip(rowCount).ToList()[c].起点接线点2 != @"/" ? 1 : 0;
            rowTakeCount += 1;
        }
        return rowTakeCount;
    }
}
public class MatchCableDataResult {
    public List<CableData> SuccessList { get; set; }
    public List<MatchCableDataFail> FailList1 { get; set; }
    public List<MatchCableDataFail> FailList2 { get; set; }
}
public class MatchCableDataFail {
    public required TerminationData Data { get; set; }
    public required string Reason { get; set; }
    public bool IsChecked { get; set; } = false;
}
using System.ComponentModel.DataAnnotations;
using System.Diagnostics;
using System.Reflection;
namespace IODataPlatform.Utilities;
public class DataComparator {
    public static async Task<List<DifferentObject<TKey>>> ComparerAsync<T, TKey>(IEnumerable<T> newData, IEnumerable<T> oldData, Func<T, TKey> keySelector) where T : class {
        return await Task.Run(() => {
            if (oldData.Select(keySelector).Distinct().Count() != oldData.Count()) { throw new("原始数据主键不唯一,无法对比，但仍然可以导入！"); }
            if (newData.Select(keySelector).Distinct().Count() != newData.Count()) { throw new("导入数据主键不唯一,无法对比，但仍然可以导入！"); }
            var props = typeof(T).GetProperties().Select(x => new { Prop = x, Name = x.GetCustomAttribute<DisplayAttribute>()?.Name ?? x.Name });
            var diffList = new List<DifferentObject<TKey>>();
            var sw = Stopwatch.StartNew();
            var newList = newData.ExceptBy(oldData.Select(keySelector), keySelector).ToList();
            var a = sw.Elapsed;
            sw = Stopwatch.StartNew();
            foreach (var item in newList) {
                var diffObject = new DifferentObject<TKey>() { Key = keySelector(item), Type = DifferentType.新增 };
                diffObject.DiffProps.Reset(props.Select(prop => new DifferentProperty() { OldValue = null, NewValue = prop.Prop.GetValue(item), PropName = prop.Name }).Where(x => !string.IsNullOrEmpty($"{x.NewValue}")));
                diffList.Add(diffObject);
            }
            a = sw.Elapsed;
            sw = Stopwatch.StartNew();
            var oldList = oldData.ExceptBy(newData.Select(keySelector), keySelector).ToList();
            a = sw.Elapsed;
            sw = Stopwatch.StartNew();
            foreach (var item in oldList) {
                var diffObject = new DifferentObject<TKey>() { Key = keySelector(item), Type = DifferentType.移除 };
                diffObject.DiffProps.Reset(props.Select(prop => new DifferentProperty() { NewValue = null, OldValue = prop.Prop.GetValue(item), PropName = prop.Name }).Where(x => !string.IsNullOrEmpty($"{x.OldValue}")));
                diffList.Add(diffObject);
            }
            a = sw.Elapsed;
            sw = Stopwatch.StartNew();
            var sameList = oldData
                .Select(oldItem => new { OldItem = oldItem, NewItem = newData.SingleOrDefault(newItem => Equals(keySelector(newItem), keySelector(oldItem))) })
                .Where(x => x.NewItem is not null).ToList();
            a = sw.Elapsed;
            sw = Stopwatch.StartNew();
            foreach (var item in sameList) {
                var diffObject = new DifferentObject<TKey>() { Key = keySelector(item.OldItem), Type = DifferentType.覆盖 };
                diffObject.DiffProps.Reset(props.Select(prop => new DifferentProperty() { NewValue = prop.Prop.GetValue(item.NewItem), OldValue = prop.Prop.GetValue(item.OldItem), PropName = prop.Name }).Where(x => $"{x.OldValue}" != $"{x.NewValue}"));
                if (diffObject.DiffProps.Count != 0) { diffList.Add(diffObject); }
            }
            a = sw.Elapsed;
            return diffList;
        });
    }
}
public class DifferentObject<T> {
    public required T Key { get; set; }
    public required DifferentType Type { get; set; }
    public List<DifferentProperty> DiffProps { get; } = [];
}
public enum DifferentType {
    新增 = 1,
    移除 = 2,
    覆盖 = 4,
}
public class DifferentProperty {
    public required string PropName { get; set; }
    public required object? OldValue { get; set; }
    public required object? NewValue { get; set; }
}
namespace IODataPlatform.Utilities;
public partial class CommonFilter(string title) : ObservableObject {
    public string Title { get; } = title;
    public ObservableCollection<string> Options { get; } = ["全部"];
    [ObservableProperty]
    private string option = "全部";
    public void ClearAll() {
        Option = "全部";
        Options.Reset(["全部"]);
    }
    public void SetOptions(IEnumerable<string> newOptions) {
        var options = newOptions.Distinct().Where(x => !string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(x)).Prepend("全部");
        var option = options.Contains(Option) ? Option : "全部";
        Options.Reset(options);
        Option = option;
    }
}

global using System;
